title: Pawmates: The Dog Meetup App
description:
Featured on 50+ news and media channels including BlogTO, Narcity, Newsweek, CTV, City News, Global News, Curiocity, and many more

Downloaded more than 50,000 times in 20+ countries

Pawmates is your friendly neighbourhood dog meetup app! Match, chat, and meet with dogs and their owners near you!

Find your pack! Looking to meet with like minded people who love their pets like you do? Look no further! Our matching works just like your favourite meetup apps. Swipe right on pups you like, left on those you don’t. Once you’ve matched with them, you can chat freely as much as you want, for free. We do NOT believe in pay to message (who wants to do that?)

Our features include:

CREATE YOUR CUSTOM PROFILE
Post photos of your pup, add details about them including their personality, age, breed, and more!

MATCH WITH PUPS
Unlimited free browsing of the cutest dogs in your area! Change your settings to specify the types of dogs and people you want to meet! Find your gang!

CHAT AND MEET
Pawmates matches show up on your custom wheel! Swipe through your match wheel and start chatting with people and their pups!
Connect with pups near you by organizing meet ups!

OUR PET BUSINESS MAP

Looking for the top rated vets, pet food stores, walkers, or anything else related to your pup like the best park in your area? Hop on over to our Pawmates Map and check out every animal business in your area!

Pawmates is here not only to help you meet your new dogpack, but to help with every other need of pet owners and we're growing daily! We want to build the biggest community of dog lovers around the world. So come join our family today!

CONTACT US!
Have questions, problems, or feedback? Feel free to contact us @ Pawmatesapp@gmail.com Or visit us at our Instagram and Facebook pages to win amazing prizes and giveaways!

YOUR PRIVACY IS IMPORTANT TO US
Please read the terms and policies of Pawmates, as well as the privacy policy carefully. All data is handled under the terms and policies of Pawmates privacy policy. More details can be found here: https://pawmatesapp.com/terms-of-service/

comments: ['Great app and presents well visually but always fails to send Notifications when receiving chat messages forcing you to manually check in on conversations.', 'Decent app, but would be more effective with more members- obviously not the fault of the developer, but still a shortcoming. Adding the option to delete chats would be good.', "12 people are within my 50 mile radius. 7 of those people want to breed their dogs. 2 of those people want to date. And another 1 just wants a pet sitter. This app isnt regulated Edit: I did attempt to report these profiles. There wasn't a report option. Or it's incredibly difficult to find. Either or.", "Won't use proper location. Locks when I try to update the location. Won't let me delete account.", 'Fantastic app loved all the people', 'Very user friendly app. A lot of great matches for my little Barky. Me and 🐕 really loving this app.', "I love pawmates but they are the same dog s and no one manage me back but it's still a good app", 'This is a great way to meet other pets. 5/5!!', 'Great app my dog loves it']

title: DogDater
description:
Few animals are as social as our dog friends, yet no social App is devoted to THEIR needs for daily quality interactions until now! DogDater is an app created by dog lovers for dog lovers to help your dog flourish and find new friends. It allows you to follow and meet other dogs around the world regardless of where they are and based on your personal preferences such as breed, characteristics, and gender. 
The App includes lots of functions that will make your and your dog’s life happier: The yard allows you to stay up to date on what your favorite dogs are doing. You can also showcase your dog's life and news about it. You can create and join groups in your area or based on your dog's interests. This is a great way to connect with more dogs and to share tips and thoughts about your and others' dogs. You can also send direct messages to other dog owners and meet up, or recommend nice dog places, exciting parks, or any favorite dog accessories your dog might want to share with their friends. The App also makes it easy for you to keep track of your dog's family history, and find your dog's long-lost brothers and sisters.
We have just launched the App and are planning to add lots of exciting functions very soon, such as a marketplace, online courses, dog psychology, dog walking, dog sitting, parking, mating, and pedigrees for breeding all over the world. Welcome to DogDater The world's best community for dogs!
summary: The App for all dog lovers. Find dogs around the world & around the corner.

I'm not gonna commute with my two dogs, one of them with arthritis, to meet another dog. I understand it might work for other people, but it is a very simple feature to add an address to the account information and be able to search based on that. You basically already have that with the city...", 'Fantastic app. Really been waiting for an app like this. Thank you for making it happen!']

title: Fetchadate
description:
FetchaDate is Where Pet Lovers Meet! The place to connect for friends, pet playdates, and especially a date for you!

DATING, FRIENDS, PET PLAYDATES
What we do at FetchaDate is eliminate the hurdle to who you’re looking for. We are the dating app where singles meet over what they already love: dogs, cats, and maybe even exotic pets.

Those who trust FetchaDate are people who treat their pets as family so you don’t have to worry about them not being a “pet person”. Now, we can’t guarantee every person on here loves animals, but chances are they wouldn’t be here if they didn’t.

NO PET, NO PROBLEM
We understand people may be between pets at the moment so ‘No Pet, No Problem!’ Choose from a variety of virtual pets that represent your lifestyle like a bird, fish, turtle, horse, pig, or even a snake!

HERE’S HOW IT WORKS - YOU GET A WINGPET!
You can tell a lot about a person through their pet and that helps make better matches. With FetchaDate, your “WingPet” starts things off making your introduction. Your pet’s picture is seen first, and your pet gives clues about your interests. Why is the pet seen first? We feel this leads to more success, because who wouldn’t swipe right on a cute pet? And, Fetchadate creates a better experience by bonding over common ground.

CHANGING THE RULES TO FIND YOUR MATCH
Searching offers a few options:

1. See a pet you like and swipe right. And, if their owner swipes right on you, find them in your “Matches” tab. Swiped right but not a match yet? They will appear in your “fav’d” tab.
OR
2. See a pet and scroll up to get clues about the owner before swiping left or right.
OR
3. Need to see the person before swiping? Tap on the ? to see who’s behind that pet and select a heart for yes or X to keep fetching.

PROFILES: FETCH - MATCH - DATE
In FetchaDate, it’s quick to create your free profile including your values, interests, and personality. A profile also consists of name, age, location, occupation, and motto. And, you get to make a profile for your real or virtual pet.

FREE TO USE PLUS UPGRADES
FetchaDate is free to download, and create a profile with a limit on swipes, and chat!
We offer optional in-app purchases of monthly, 6 months, and 1 year subscriptions with discounts available. Subscriptions offer boosts, extended swiping, chat, and additional pet profiles. Price chart is displayed in the app before making a purchase.

Any free trial period is for a limited time. Any unused portion of a free trial period is forfeited after purchasing a subscription.

Payment will be charged to your Google Play account after purchase confirmation. Your subscription will automatically renew for the same term and price. You may cancel your subscription up to 24 hours before the next billing cycle.

You can manage your subscription in your phone’s account settings.
If you don’t choose to purchase a subscription, you may continue fetching on FetchaDate for free with limitations.

FOUNDER
Sheryl Matthys is the bestselling author of Leashes and Lovers: What Your Dog Can Teach You About Love, Life, and Happiness. From the moment Sheryl got her first Greyhound, people on the streets of NYC started talking to her. Right then she knew the secret to dating, friendships, and love! Sheryl’s appeared on ABC World News, Animal Planet, BRAVO, E!, Fox & Friends, The New York Times and more.

TERMS AND PRIVACY
Fetch on FetchaDate worry free. Check out our terms and privacy policy.
Terms of Use: https://fetchadate.com/terms/
Privacy Policy: https://fetchadate.com/privacy-policy

If you're looking for someone, this would be a good place to find someone with similar interests.", 'This is a cute, easy to use app. I would definitely be using it if I were single, will refer my son to it.', "Great app...great idea....even linked up from Australia.....and it's inclusive of my three mates, my two staffies and my lorikeet", '"Unexpected error occurred" EVERY time I enter my phone number to open the app...🤨👎', "Doesn't work, after I type in my phone number press next. It will not complete the action.", "Can't even open app. Keeps shutting down.", "I thought this would be Great idea because I love dogs and would love to meet someone with the same passion, but it's not accepting my phone number. It doesn't let me go any further. Anyone that can help me?", 'I like the concept. But what about other pets besides Dogs and Cats? What about Birds and Reptiles lovers?', 'It is a very easy and useful app to use', "It's and interesting take on dating but truth is if my dog don't like ya I won't either", 'Pretty cute concept', 'Not many close options in Ct', "It doesn't work", 'Finally an app for me.', '𝓕𝓮𝓽𝓬𝓱𝓪𝓭𝓪𝓽𝓪 𝓘𝓼 𝓣𝓱𝓮 𝓑', 'Seems cool', 'Wow wow', 'Gg']

title: WooPlus - Dating App for Curvy
description:
WooPlus, the largest BBW online dating and chat app, is the cupid for plus-size singles and people who admire curvy singles.

❤️ Best Plus Size & BBW Dating App with 8M+ users, NO fat-shaming.

❤️ Featured on BBC, Forbes, Google Play & the App Store.️

Meet new people & date local plus-size ladies and chubby singles in New York, Los Angeles, Chicago, Las Vegas, San Antonio, Philadelphia, and other US cities, as well as the UK, Canada, Australia, Germany, and other parts of the world!  

Start Dating With:

EASY CHAT - "Say Hi" to your match & start chatting! FUN EXPERIENCE - The video feature shows charm & gets you more matches! REAL PEOPLE - All profiles are professionally checked to block bots and scammers. INCLUSIVE VIBES - Meet new people nearby, meet local curvy singles who love your full-figured body.  

Meet Your Love:

WooPlus is a free dating app for adults and people who like to meet & date curvy girls, super-size big beautiful women (SSBBW), and chubby guys, whether you're black, Latino, Asian, or interracial, or seeking mature dating and LGBTQ relationships (lesbian, gay or bisexual). But if you're just looking for a ONS, FWB, sugar baby seeking sugar daddy for arrangement, casual encounters dating, or threesome affairs, WooPlus may not be the dating site for you.  

Social Buzz:

🌟 “Plus-size dating app WooPlus will now ban ‘fat-shaming fools’” - YAHOO 🌟 “WooPlus, hailed as an answer to Tinder for the bigger and rounder female population.'' - MIRROR   -Connect with us on social: @wooplus_dating (Instagram, TikTok) -Terms of Service: https://www.wooplus.com/terms -Privacy Policy: https://www.wooplus.com/privacy -Dating Tips: https://www.wooplus.com/bbwdating

comments: ['Wooplus is a really good dating app, it performs as advertised, and give much more reasonable options for single parents than other apps. The algorhythm is far more forgiving than other apps, and I find matches much faster than its competitors, the premium is also very affordable. The only downside is that the app does not work on data, at 5G and full bars, the app as no connection or service, which makes forming a connection with someone quite hard within the app.', "I wish I had learned about WooPlus sooner. I had trouble locating people on other apps with whom I actually clicked. They just always seemed to fizzle out in conversation or fail miserably in real life. They just didn't feel right, and they were unable to explain why. I've only just started using this app, but it's clear that the people I'm corresponding with are much more compatible.", "Balanced experience at the moment. I'm trying to update a few things on my profile, and it keeps running an unsuccessful save after I've entered everything. (-1400) Not sure why this is happening as the app has just been updated.", 'This app is horrible! It allows users to list disgusting sexual requests. Yet my profile was deleted due to me letting those interested know what expectations I as for in a potential match. The potential matches are always too far. Very few are in your city. This app is a waste of time. I do not recommend.', 'Garbage app, pretty much everything paywall and the app is not great, looks just okay but no functionality like nowhere to delete messages and most ppl that message you there is no way to block them, that feature only shows for a few.', "I've never had luck with dating apps, but this app has a feature where you can chat with someone and only after a little while talking does it show each person what the other looks like. I gave it a shot on a whim one night. Call it thanks to either dumb luck, fate, or this app, but I met my first ever girlfriend on this app on my first attempt on the FlashChat feature and I'm meeting her family in a few days. I couldn't be happier 😁", 'App is very predatory, will actively search people interstate unless you pay for the "premium" service. Makes tinder look like a good app. Wooplus used to be a half decent app, but now it\'s just a cash grab.', "For the most part it seems like a great app that I'm getting pretty into! However the issue I have is a big one The thing is that it's very unclear of the sexualities of other people. Often I find myself scared to talk to people because I'm not sure if their bi-sexual, gay, straight, etc. Id be happy to give 5 stars, but I just wish some things weren't so vague...", "It's pretty cool, love that you get notifications for almost everything so you're not waiting for days to heat back from someone. I also like that it's very detailed. The only thing I don't like is not being able to see my likes without paying.", 'I can encounter some great matches in many features on this dating app. Those features are really unique and useful. So for those bbw dating finders who yearn for finding some great dating partners, this is our best choice! I like this curvy tinder app, I get what I want here.', "Overall, it's a good app. The only thing I would say is that it would be nice if you could choose the region for free as well as preference, age and distance in fact all preferences. If the messaging was free for basic users, that would also be great. Maybe if the person is VIP , use 💎 just a thought.", "Absolutely useless for me, I've downloaded the app twice now and it won't let me progress any further than adding my phone number so I can't create my account. Going to look for a more user friendly app.", "Awful app. Most of the people on here are bots and scammers. It's also incredibly restrictive and is extremely hard to actually talk to someone. I was offered a deal for 12.99 for three months. I saw that I was charged for the full price instead of the discounted price since I used this service before. However, on the charge screen it doesn't explain that. Sent an email to support and said they wouldn't refund me and hope I understand. Luckily, Google had my back and refunded me.", "Well, I wish I could say I found someone on this app but haven't. You really need to give more swipes. At least 25 or 40 a day. Then unlimited if you do a month payment", 'The app is easy to use havnt matched with any obvious bots but some profiles do just get the X for being sus. Found a few matches but didnt want to keep chatting after first night. As with all dating apps its free to play but pay to win, you gain a significant advantage by whaling, but loging in each day and playing the dating game will slowly have you finding a few people. App started matching me with people across the world weirdly which is undesireable. Wouldnt pay to subscribe personally.', 'The site has plenty of scammers. It is sad that the developers do not take our privacy and safety Seriously. My suggestion is to change by taking appropriate safety measures before allowing anyone located in the world to use the app freely. Applicants should be asked to identify themselves by taking a selfie and sending it to your team to investigate before joining. Such measures are being taken by your competition to keep us safe because they care, and so should you. Thank you kindly.', "While not the best looking app, it is one of the more functional (when you're not swamped by profiles looking to sell their services).", "I have quite a few profiles under 'my likes' that I either passed on or never even viewed, so I am getting a few incorrect matches. Seems a bit pointless for a dating app? I'm now correcting my rating down because I am tired of constantly being shown the same people - people I have swiped past many times just keep coming back again and again and again. What's the point in going through them if you're only ever looking at the same 10 potential matches?", "I dont think there is a single person left on the app, I've used it before with decent success, 80 likes or so. Used it for a week with the paid thing and didn't get a single like", 'May be real accounts but most are for OnlyFans/Snapchat purposes. Free features are horrid. Search is too basic instead of ease of close by. App performs well tho.', "You only get to like 20 people a day. Everyone you talk to on their seems well Out Of Reach. No one lives within 30 miles and no one has tried to talk to me yet. Feels like all the other app only worse. You have to pay to play and then the only way you're really able to make the most of it is to spend extra money even though you've already spent money on a month membership. I wouldn't be surprised if most of profiles were AI.", 'For some reason I never match with the ones that like me. And I never get them recommended as well. So it seems to be the app is broken. Or people outside my preferences can like me. But even then they will not be recommended. Sorry to the 8 people who gave me a like.', "Doesn't tell you that they are going to charge you until you've set an account up, and then you get stuck in a loop screen trying to cancel and the only way to get out of it is to exit the app with task manager. If I could give you less I would.", "I mostly see people from other states. I still run out of matches even though there is no use trying to match with them since they are too far. There isn't a way to set a distance preference either", 'I\'m trying to sign up and it\'s not letting me. It\'s always "internal error 100003" and it\'s annoying. I\'ve tried over 40 times and it\'s saying the same thing. Pls help meee 😭😭', 'Horrible glitches and it keeps going to the same person over and over. I asked for my money back after this poor experience. We will see if it happens. Later: They told me they would refund my money to my Google account. That was 07/14/23 and over 24 hrs ago. Nothing. I am so frustrated with this app. So many fake accounts, too.', 'No one responds and it gives you more matches way outside of where you live no matter what your app settings are. This is not a good site to meet people and is a waste of time and money.', "Do you have to purchase a subscription to get or see that you've gotten likes? I know I'm not everyone's cup of tea, but I have been using this app for about 2 weeks, and I haven't gotten even one like. And most people are too far away. The idea for the app is nice, but it fails in execution.", "Useless. Constant error messages, and when it does work, it's suggesting people 150 miles away.", "This app is WHACK, you have to pay to do anything worthwhile. Why do I have to get VIP access just to see who liked me? And anybody can message you if they're VIP, from anywhere. People you wouldn't even match with. I'm not paying $14.99 a month for something I can do for free elsewhere. I had a better experience using FB dating, at least I can see who likes me. There's also no good explanation on how to use this app either, I'm just clicking stuff to see what's what. Just a mess.", 'Useless app. Can only look at so many profiles a day and they keep showing the same people over and over after clearly not being interested!!', "Woo plus , it's a much better dating app. Than most just full of Fakes from Africa nigeria or Russian & yes I found out from where. And yes 80% Fakers on most dating sites .Most are specially designed to steal money from men all day long. That are lying to you trying to steal your money hidden behind a Beautiful fake pictures. Very few dating sites are clean enough by over 80% non fakes. And that's what this app is way ,way cleaner than most.", "DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY OR TIME 🚩 The profiles are inactive. I paid for the premium subscription and haven't received likes or matches in days, it's practically a ghost town dating app. If anyone does chat with you beware they're most likely a scammer pretending to be in the military and out of the country. 🤨 I want my money back. I basically paid to like fake/inactive profiles. Scam app! 🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩🚩", "Nice app, in theory. Cool spin on dating app features. I like the flash chat and open forum in moments. I'm a free user because I have a problem paying for things I feel should be free. Would've been 4 stars b/c I don't like the most recent promotion or the few matches to likes. I have 70+ likes that I can't see, which is fine b/c free is my favorite. But in my rounds they only send 1 or 2 of them. I think they're in cahoots with scammers b/c they deleted my bio for mentioning scam behaviors", 'Easy to use. You\'re set up in less then 5 minutes. I do wish that the filters you set up extended to the daily picks and who is able to see your profile. Lots of "likes" from men younger or older than my started range. So good but not perfect.', 'Not impressed. Super complex UI with almost everything behind a paywall and I\'m not even entirely sure if I\'ll get a match without paying. It\'s also difficult to set your location. All of the attractive women have tons of comments and likes on their "posts" so it\'s not really worth the effort.', 'I like how it fills the plus size niche very well. Profiles seem genuine. I like the FREE messaging only once mutually liked each other approach. Edit: I subscribed to the premium service, largely to support this, and discovered it\'s now worse! Instead of only messaging after mutual likes, I\'m forced to cold message now... Not worth. Edit2: The "hi" feature is behind a paywall now and the Lucky Draw draws you a discount for paying for Premium. How lucky O.O lowering rating', "Just like all other dating apps just another waste of time. They all claim to be completely free but notice it says #10 grossing app because like the rest they lure you in to pay with fake profiles but you will never find anyone in your area or have to pay to actually talk to someone because the people that message you are bots and you can't really message anyone. Even if it was security reasons it would at least be a feature to let you or a person choose to get a message.", 'I get the monetization of platforms and I understand that the app is free, mostly, but now being charged to send a greeting which you could only send daily for free anyways, now that\'s a bit of an overreach. They took the ability to look at your old matches and monetized it. Now you can\'t even send a simple "Hi".', 'Probably fun for the boys. If you ask to see both men and women, you get nothing but girls. I guess that makes sense. Probably more girls have a reason to be there. I ended up switching to all men. The guys who are available are enthusiastic... sometimes to the point of inappropriate, but not far beyond other apps. Some obvious hookers, and one guy kinda offered money for "adult fun". But hey, they like big girls. The app mostly pulls it off. It just ain\'t changing the world.']

title: OkCupid: Online Dating App
description:
Get the best free dating app and find your kind. OkCupid is the online dating app that helps you make a match based on who you really are and what you love.

Online dating is personalized and fun with OkCupid. Romance and great dates come from great connections - that’s why OkCupid shows off who you are beyond a photo. Match and find love based on what makes you, well, you - because you deserve it.

Meet singles in India who share your interests. OkCupid’s unique questionnaire helps us match you with singles we think you’ll really connect with. Date for romance or to meet new people and discover the Indian dating scene online.

OkCupid is an online dating app that highlights your personality and interests to let us know what you care about most. Match and meet up based on your passions and deal breakers so you can match on what matters.

Match, chat or have a deep conversation through our one-of-a-kind love chat messaging system and focus only on the connections and relationships you’re interested in, without the ones you’re not.

Meet new people and start a romance no matter who or what kind of relationship you’re looking for. Whether it’s romance, dating or marriage, OkCupid can help you find someone special.

Love doesn’t discriminate, and neither does OkCupid. Whether you're gay, lesbian, nonbinary or don't fit into any one label, OkCupid can help you find love. Flirt and find a date, no matter your gender or orientation - you can even set your pronouns at registration!

Find love, build connections and go on great dates with OkCupid – download now!

OKCUPID FEATURES:

INDIAN DATING APP
• Build an online dating profile that highlights what matters to you
• Match with singles near you who share your interests and passions
• Find friends and matches by swiping and explore in-depth profiles all on the same dating app

LOCAL DATING – MEET NEW PEOPLE
• Flirt & chat with our unique messaging system
• Match and connect with someone you're compatible with
• Local dating features help you meet people nearby
• Online chat to meet people and set a meetup for a date

LOVE CALCULATOR BASED ON WHAT MATTERS
• Find local singles who share your passions and interests
• Local dating with partners who are just right for you
• Plan a date night with your match
• Set dating preferences, whether you’re straight, gay or anything in-between

DATING APP UPGRADE
OkCupid is absolutely free to download and use, but we offer an optional premium subscription that unlocks exclusive features.
• See who likes you without having to like them first
• Search with advanced filters and additional options
• Enjoy OkCupid ad-free

Meet up with singles and find a great connection – download OkCupid today!

WHAT PEOPLE ARE SAYING
“Want to have ‘hell yes’ first dates? OkCupid is the perfect wingman.” - Huffington Post
“OkCupid may be the OG of dating sites, but that doesn’t mean it’s done innovating.” - Glamour
“OkCupid is giving you a chance to really connect with someone…” - Elite Daily
summary: Find your kind of love on OkCupid! Meet singles online and go on great dates!

comments: ['Well, the last update removed the "nearby" filter while swiping. The app already completely ignores your filters, you will never see or be seen by anyone within 100 miles. Been using okc on and off for almost a decade, it\'s really fallen off. The questions are the only unique selling point, and no one fills out more than a handful. Using this app is just swiping left on the same people every day, regardless of whatever dealbreakers you set. At least messaging is still free, bet that won\'t last.', "The search function on this app JUST SIMPLY DOESN'T WORK, making it aggravating to try and use. You can select 50 miles and the app will still show you someone well over 100 miles away. The passport feature, allows you to search for women in other countries unless you plan on traveling to that country this feature is useless, and theirs no way to disable it.", 'This app is poorly created and tested. When I look at the message list, it doesn\'t show me the last messages with my connections. It just shows " It\'s a match" which is absurd. I would like to see the last message without actually clicking on the connection to read the history of the conversation. This happens after few days of you and your connection talking over the app, roughly 2-3 days later. It works fine for the first couple of days.', "Ridiculous! I remember when this app was less than $20/mo. To ask for almost $50 now, is ridiculous. Pros are search parameters, which are some of the best options around; less profiles seem fake. Cons are that the experience is no where near the price you pay. As with most dating apps, you'll magically receive matches all throughout the period you're not a subscriber, but when you're finally able to see them, they're totally outside your set preferences. Those preferences should apply to all", "Currently one of the better dating apps I think. Texting is a little slow if you write multiple messages. It stops and erases what you're typing. I'm also getting the same match notification like 15 times. And it sends you notifications that someone likes you when you're out of swipes for the day, that's a little annoying. Otherwise, plenty of people and plenty of matches!", 'Decided to try the a month of the subscription to see all the matches that had piled up, 99% were from across the world and had almost no profile. My preferences will reset randomly and show me "recommended" matches outside of my search parameters (age difference, gender, location, etc). Sending a like let\'s you send an "intro" to stand out - but super likes don\'t? You can still see the profiles of the people you\'ve liked, but not the ones you\'ve super liked or sent intros to. Save your $$', 'Months ago I paid for a subscription which is supposed to allow you to see all of your intros at once. It does if you use it in the browser, but if you use the app it says "upgrade to A list to see all of your intros" which isn\'t even the name they use for their subscription anymore! I contacted support, was never given any sort of resolution, & cancelled my subscription. I signed up again yesterday & the app is still doing the same thing - no fix for this ongoing, documented issue. Total SCAM!', 'Still won\'t load past 20 of my "You Liked", and is only partially showing "Matches". Swiping is clunkier than last update. Can no longer see the intros I wrote to people I haven\'t matched with yet (I think it used to be in the "You Liked" section or my Messages). I can\'t find my Matched in my messages anymore if I leave the screen before the "You Matched!" popup finishes loading (which used to be ok!!). I matched with someone and sent a message, but I can\'t find it anywhere after!', "This is one of the few dating apps that actually functions correctly, and has actual humans on it. There seems to be a few fake profiles, or at least some really old ones that haven't been touched in years (people still wearing masks and talking about the China flu). Overall, it's ok, and you can match and chat with people without paying. It can be buggy at times, and the app seems to struggle with distance limitations, but it does do what it claims.", "First off I really love how customizable your profile is. I really enjoy being able to answer so many questions and getting to see how much you match a potential partner. That's a great idea and no other apps do this. However the base app gives you criminally low swipes before you have to wait to swipe again. I paid for the basic ($34) for unlimited swipes and I don't feel like it was worth it tbh :/ I have 47 likes and can't match with a single person :/", 'instead of a "your turn" category in the messages, just make a panel of every one who has messaged me and make it stay there even if i replied again and they haven\'t yet. also add a search bar to find people better. i have more than a hundred matches and the messages categories are really inconvenient. not happy about it. it would also be very useful to be able to select multiple people to unmatch instead of doing it all one by one.', "I paid for a subscription, and all was fine, but for the last couple of weeks before it expired, I had no likes and no matches of any kind. It ran out yesterday and overnight. I have 13 likes and lots and lots of matches. Obviously, it's a way to try to get me to resubscribe, but what a con restricting access to matches and likes towards the end of a subscription. Bear this in mind if you use this service.", "Recently come back after a long lay off. It's exactly the same. Except now it just recycles all the matches you've left swiped on. I must have seen the same people now about 300 times each. - anything that's a deal breaker you have to pay, setting preferences doesn't work at all and still shows you matches nowere near you. You can swipe for free but everyone, and unsuitable matches and even in other countries are shown. I have a ton of likes and obviously you have to pay to see them. Scam.", "The people are awesome and I like the option to answer questions and see other people's answers, but the app is loaded with bugs. At one point half of the likes I got and my conversations were deleted and the support couldn't do anything about it. From time to time the app stops working and I can't login. Now all the text I wrote in my profile got corrupted and the support can't restore what I had there. These issues happened mostly recently, so I hope they'll start fixing them soon.", "For some reason, the app refuses to show people in my distance preference. I live in a rather large population area, but regardless, I'm only shown people over 25 miles away when my preference is 10 miles. I refuse to go a whole state away just to have one date. Fix this problem.", "I tried this in its heyday,; interesting method of a social networking system by a series of interest and questionnaire. But I tried logging today, even post update seconds ago. I couldn't, tried the web version. Denied too. I guess not only could I not delete my account but even after the latest update, this app has officially been turn redundant that logging in is not possible. Farewell and onwards to hopefully better ones.", 'Don\'t pay their subscription. No matter how broad your settings, there will be users who selected you but that you cannot see. They will keep spamming you with the same profiles over and over no matter how many times you\'ve swipped left. Do not waste your money on their subscription. They also hide their top picks "cupid\'s pick" behind additional payrolls even if you are already a paid subscriber, while feeding the same profiles over and over. Do not pay for the premium subscription!', "The worst dating app. I don't know if this is true, but I'm guessing the vast majority of profiles are very very old. No way to verify new vs old profiles. I have had pretty good success on every other main stream dating app but not Ok Cupid. I did get tons of likes from people on other continents however.. totally useless and prob the most expensive of all dating apps. If I could give it Zero stars I would. Garbage.", "Wow this App doesn't work in a million different ways. I subscribed and paid the six month fee, and the app started to malfunction! All my matches and conversations either never saved or would disappear. Any messages I would reply to would not post to the match and then my filters didn't work! I was getting feeds of people outside my choices even though I had deal breakers I contacted support and fortunately they gave me a refund. It still doesn't work...What's the point if the APP doesnt work!?", "Won't let me cancel premium. Ended up getting billed for a month I didn't want, and it is set to bill me again for next month. So the link to disable your subscription in the app doesn't go anywhere. It's decoration that tricks you into thinking you canceled. You have to log in on an actual web browser to cancel a subscription.", "The main advantage of OkCupid over its competitors is its matching questionnaire/algorithm. But, the questionnaire page has a horrible interface. In the web version at least, when you re-answer a match question, the screen then takes you back the top, forcing you to scroll all the way back down again, re-loading the questions that are too far down. It ought to be divided into multiple pages instead of set up as an infinite scroll. You also can't skip questions that you had previously answered.", 'I paid. But the features were not worth it. It was still impossible to change the preferences. After the subscription ended - exactly the next day, I received 10 likes (while only 2-3 during the whole 3 months). It is up to you if you think it is real or fake likes...', "Something's terribly wrong with this app. Notifications don't work no matter what I set in the app or in my phone's settings, the Likes and Messages sometimes have a dot in them despite having no new content, Boosts get actived by themselves (cache issue?) some of the profiles text is gibberish and events always feel delayed, wether it's the animation lagging or the backend. It's like the app is drunk; either that or the developers.", "Absolute worst. It has just been a day since I installed, created an account, and paid for the subscription. I was using the app when I got logged out unexpectedly. Now, I can no longer access my account using my mobile number or my email address. Wth. And yes, I tried reinstalling the app. It didn't work.", "I just signed up 10 mins ago. It said success and then was shown a sign in page. It would not let me sign in. I tried installing the app on my phone. Tried again. It told me my account was banned. I have no idea why. I'm just a normal person using photos and info I've used on 2 other dating apps. Tried contacting support. I can't. It's requiring me to sign in to speak to support. That's the problem. I can't sign in. Maybe someone there will read this and help me. :/", 'There are pros and cons to this app. Unfortunately, in my experience there were more cons than pros. Pros: I like the questionnaire & the commonalities percentage meter. Cons: Needing a subscription to see likes. Most likes were from foreign countries on the other side of the world. After paying for a subscription, the app went radio silent. OK Cupid ran out of recommendations for me and suggested looking at profiles in other countries. In my opinion, save your money and try a different app.', 'Probably the best app there is for what it does. Where other dating apps requires insane kinds of cash for just about anything, this one actually allows you to look for people, and send them an intro message, without it costing anything. If your intro, or match, is returned, texting them costs nothing. However, there is a massive amount of mainly Asian/South American/African location faking going on - You might set range to 50km, which apparently includes several continents <- Only gotten worse.', 'Worst so-called dating app. Very low quality profiles. And same profiles keep rotating. 70% of profiles have no pics. Even if you set preferences, the app disregards those and keeps showing you profiles outside your preferences; because number of profiles are very limited. You will not get a single decent person to talk to. Just waste of time. Uninstalled after trying it out for a month.', "The best of the dating apps, in my opinion. Tons of users, tons of swipes, able to send a comment with every like, able to like specific parts of the person's profile, able to change location, able to look around in the global pool, all for free. You can also really customise your profile.", "I like the idea and concepts. But technically it works so bad, matches don't appear on the list. I encountered multiple bugs and when reached to customer support they treated me like an idiot and dismissed my problems. I repeat. The app is super buggy and doesn't work correctly", "This app is loaded with bugs and it's gotten worse over time! The same people keep coming up even though I swipe left on them everytime, even the blocked ones! Intros on 99% of the profiles are gibberish and not legible. People with a 90% match have complete opposite answers to mine... And how are there so many profiles without pics of the people's faces? I uploaded a pic once that didn't show my face and I was emailed numerous times warning me that it would be taken down! Not a good app at all", "What a scam, 44 new likes, pay $100 to see who they are....sucker! They're all from other countries even when I select nearby. What a grimey app. I want a damn refund...NOW! You app isn't allowing me to cancel subscription to premium. I select cancel and it glitches or does nothing. This isn't surprising, you've found a way to trap subscribers into being locked into a system where nobody can be contacted to cancel payments. I will he speaking with my lawyer.", 'Deceptive advertising when you uses their app several times and are charged $45, then they can\'t find your app. No refund because you used their service. They should advertise "x" communications cost $45, rather than make you think you have unlimited access. This is the definition of DECEPTION ADVERTISING. I have gotten a dozen from letters that claim they are working on it. Support is worthless. They tell me I am using the wrong email, which is why they can\'t find my account.', "Another app with no customer service what so ever. Just automated responses. I've emailed them 3 times saying I can't login or reset my password and they email me a link to reset my password.... I really hate technology sometimes. The app also has this weird bug when I'm writing in any of the bio sections it just scrolls all the way down and I can't see what I'm writing.... The price for a month of the premium service is absurd.", "The pricing of premium has wildly increased over the last 4 years. The cost of one month is now what 6 months cost 4 years ago. 6 months roughly works out 162% increase in price nearly triple what it was 4 years ago, which could be an indication of the app collapsing, some of the matches aren't even real profiles anymore, it has fallen far from where it was", "Recommends individuals far outside set preferences, from age, distance, and smoking preferences Allows spam bots from foreign countries to fill up likes Continuously keeps pushing ppl you pass on, unless they like you, then you'll never see them show up in your feed again Could be a great app, but they'd rather add more gimics to get $$$ from people.", 'Hello, Recently I noticed that my new matches do not appear in my list of matches which gives me no possibility to message them. They simply disappear right after the pink screen saying "it\'s a match". I have updated the application but the problem is still there. Can you please correct this as it makes the app completely useless as I am not able to speak to new people. It\'s a shame because otherwise I really enjoyed using this app, when it was working...', 'Better site now you can message/intro without matching again, and Profile and Photo verification now added though few do it. Still too many fake profiles and catfish that unfortunately fill up the site and waste time. Too many profiles also reappear again and again, even if you swipe left! Being able to share photos in messages would be better too, then you would know the petson is real.', 'I don\'t normally review apps, but this one was so bad, I had to say something. I\'ve been off and on this particular dating app for 4 years(give it take), the only "real" interactions I\'ve had fizzled quick. But lately, I\'ve been seeing the same profiles I\'ve already swiped on. Right or left, doesn\'t seem to matter, but why would I pay for a broken app? And based on others reviews, the paid version isn\'t any better. Talking to random strangers will get you more matches than this app ever will.', 'Support used to be the best thing about what WAS an excellent dating site and app. You used to be humans with COMMUNICATION SKILLS. But I\'ve been reporting since 7 MONTHS AGO (Jan\'23) a bug where I see "INTROS (1)", but on going to that tab: "You have no new intros." It isn\'t just the app - also on the website (both mobile and desktop), in 3 different browsers, on 3 devices... yet idiot botbrain can\'t get past suggesting uninstall/reinstall. And version 79.2.0 (Aug\'23) still hasn\'t fixed it.']

title: Tinder - Match. Chat. Date.
description:
🔥 It’s about time you showed up.🔥 
► Featuring 26 million matches per day and over 60 billion matches in total🔥
► Tinder is more than a dating app — with users in over 190 countries, it’s the most popular free social app in the world🔥
► Discover new people on Tinder and chat whenever and wherever you like🔥

With 60 billion matches to date, Tinder® is the 🔝top free dating app🔝, making it the place to be to meet new people. Whether you’re looking for friends, need a date today, or just want to chat: We’ve got something for local singles everywhere, plus features that give you the best dating experience possible. It’s proof that the best things in life really are🆓 free!🆓

How do we do it? We thought you’d never ask😉 	

👉Swipe Right™ = LIKE👉
👈Swipe Left™ = NOPE👈

You won’t be flooded with messages from singles you aren’t into here: We invented the double opt-in, which means two people have to show a mutual interest in each other in order to become a match — You can only chat with people you match with. 

Whether you’re using the free version or not, there’s no limit to the amount of people you match and chat with giving you endless possibilities to find relationships, meet friends, or find a date. Take us with you on your travels and make the locals— Wherever you go, we’ll be there. Some people call us their 🔥“most dependable matchmaker”🔥, some people call us 🔥the world’s most popular dating app🔥, but you can just call us when you want to meet up with people in your area. 

Take advantage of features that will elevate your Tinder experience: 

•	Whether you’re gay or bisexual, be proud of who you are with our Orientation feature🏳️‍🌈🏳️‍⚧️
•	Prove your the real deal and verify your profile with Photo Verification🤳 
•	Find out what you’ve got in common with your potential match with Interests🤝

Craving something extra? Tinder Plus makes it even easier to chat with singles. 

•	Likes You allows you to see all your fans, saving you precious time🕰️ 
•	Unlimited Likes for you to catch feelings for as many people as you want💚
•	Rewind for you to undo your last Like or Nope⏪
•	Use Passporttm  to go anywhere in the world to find people online outside your zip code✈️
•	Boost your profile to the top for thirty minutes to get more attention⚡
•	5 Super Likes per day because sometimes you really, really Like someone💝 

And if that feels good, but it isn’t quite enough, have a toast to the Gold Life🥂: A Tinder Gold® subscription gives you access to all of our premium features. Enjoy everything that comes with Tinder Plus® while also saving time by seeing who Likes You🌟. 

Match✅ Chat✅ Date✅ That’s our mantra. We invented the double opt-in which means two people have to show a mutual interest in order for there to be a match. How many dating apps can say that?🤔 

-----------------------------------

If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus or Tinder Gold, payment will be charged to your Google Play account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the Play Store after purchase. Current Tinder Plus subscription price starts at $9.99 USD/month, and one-month, 6-month and 12-month packages are available. Current Tinder Gold subscription price starts at $14.99 USD/month, and one-month, 6-month and 12-month packages are available. Prices are in U.S. dollars, may vary in countries other than the U.S. and are subject to change without notice. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus or Tinder Gold, you can simply continue using Tinder for free.

All photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only.

comments: ["I don't know what kind of engineers and testers you hired, many features are not working in your app. I've tried to get photo verified my account, but it showing something went wrong everytime. For that issue, I tried to attach a snapshot but that feature is also useless, that button is not responding. Pause your app in production and deep dive into that.", "Another pointless update where the design is changed to the disadvantage of the user. Before, you could highlight a bio and run it through a translator and translate it into English, for example. This is no longer possible. Furthermore, the new design is simply more colourful. It's as if the UX/UI team has been dismissed and replaced by 1st semester students. The people responsible should either rethink their quality standards or be replaced. Non of the last updates improved anything.", "A great idea in principle, but seems to either not be working as intended, a lot of fake profiles, or could even be site generated profiles to keep you active/ interested. I've had push notifications of matches and messages, and there is nothing on my contacts. I've matched and messaged, and had no replies. I've tried reinstalling the app, several reboots and still no better. I am not a gold member, but from what I have seen so far, I would not pay to upgrade.", "The location is extremely lacking on profiles. I have to use a map app to ensure profiles are actually in the state as I've had several searches day a city and that they're 10-20 miles away and they are in another state! Sometimes across the country! It would help if they put not only city, but also state in the location. The distance can also be fixed for better accuracy.", "Bugs that haven't been fixed for years (like when you accidentally super like someone and undo it you still don't get the super like back). It's obvious the app is not made to find a partner, but only short term hookups. The whole app is made so that you should just keep coming back to it, pay for more and more functions, over and over again, forever. Tinder is made and controlled by very, very, very evil people, but their abominable karma will deal with them eventually, of course.", "The app with the most users I think, but so many bug's on it.. So annoying. Not receiving notifications when someone message me, or receiving a notification, but nothing when I open the app to see it. Trying to show which song I love most on Spotify, but you can't actually do it. It only shows random songs that I don't even listen to, or listened it once lol. Lots of tiny things like that that makes to overall experience not so good.", 'Piece of junk. It seems impossible to get even a single match. After going through the stack once, any new entries are junk. No profile. Can\'t see face. Cynical. Not so much a problem with the app, but it\'s a miserable experience. User profiles are bare bones. There\'s a list of "Passions" that you can choose from, that really don\'t make sense. You can select "Atari" but not "Video games." You can\'t write in your own. There\'s minimal selection for who you\'re interested in. Man/Woman, age range.', 'Don\'t pay for it. It\'s a cool app, but there is a glitch with the premium features under Likes You. If you add any filter to the Likes, it restricts you to 20 results, rather than letting you scroll through all the filtered Likes. This is only an issue on the app as of the recent week or two. I submitted a support ticket, provided a recording showing the issue and was told, "Unfortunately, this is all the support we’re able to offer at this moment. We appreciate your time and understanding."', "Premium is pretty much worthless. The algorithm still treats you the same way. So you're essentially paying to swipe on profiles that wouldn't even see you. stick with the free version. It doesn't really improve the matches that much. Only real benefit for paying is it saves you some time you won't have to wait a few hours. Also if you are planning a vacation somewhere might help with the passport feature. Feel kinda ripped off to be honest.", "The functionality is basically gone. Swipes won't register, and once you swipe the first time, it shows you're out of swipes and keeps cycling through the same people but won't tell you that nothing is actually happening. I can message my old matches, but cannot view their profile and pics, any attempt will boot you out of the app. Changing distance and age range also has no effect, and changes won't save anyway. The constant ad profiles are garbage too, but at least that much is intentional.", 'I used to be able to easily remove myself from the stack. Now the setting to enable or disable the discovery feature is hidden and it tries to get you to pay for a premium feature instead of just turning off discovery. On top of that the setting has never changed for me no matter how many times I have gone into settings and turned off enable discovery. Being able to turn off tinder without deleting my profile was important to me. Will be looking at other apps.', 'Designed to waste money, customer support is trained to be unhelpful. "SUPERLIKES" are something you pay for. The app is designed to constantly shoot up a big pop up bubble to remind you to use it. If you accidentally touch that bubble, it automatically uses a superlike. You are supposed to get it back if you are a subscriber and "undo" the like immediately, but you do not. Support refuses to help. Tinder is a scam designed to bleed you for money.', 'Customer support is horrible. Constantly just copy and pasting the same thing over and over. Not actually communicating. No phone number for support either. I would buy the standard boosts and I would get prime time boosts instead. Also charged for them as well. They would run automatically while I was traveling. What a scam. Also unable to get verified. The new AI verification simply does not work no matter what I would do with lighting or anything else in their FAQs and CS responses.', "Overpriced, so many bots and fake profiles, you see the same profiles over and over again. No matches if you buy premium, but when it runs out, you suddenly get dozens of matches that you can't see, and so have to upgrade again. Basically, it's a big con to get you to spend money, and an apt representation of the soulless, superficial nature of modern dating.", 'Have had a lot of the "your account has been banned" notification. Even though I\'ve done nothing wrong and after uninstalling the app for a while it usually fixes it. But it\'s very frustrating not having access to my account. Customer service even said they see nothing wrong with y account on their end. But it shows it on multiple devices for me. Idk but it\'s VERY irritating.', "The past 2 days the app freezes during the sign up process. At the final screen where you select your interests, that screen is blank and you can go no further. I've tried uninstalling the app, cleaning up my phone memory/system. Reinstall and giving permissions to the app prior to first run. Still the same problem. Dunno what's going on, maybe something at your end, I've tried everything I can think of here. The app has worked perfectly for years until yesterday.", "Every dating app is the same, swipe left or right and bribes for spetial access making it generally a lower probability for a match to happen. Just this one also has a terrible interface designed to confuse and make mistakes as easily as possible. And of course we all agree on everything negative that's been said already. Design for failure. Oops you missed a match!", "This app could be good, and is under certain circumstances, but once you've messed up your algorithm no one will ever see you and you'll just be cursed to swiping endlessly on people that will never see your card on their stack. Also the premium features are nice but the price has increased exponentially to a point where I don't think I'd ever be able to financially justify even the lowest tier. Like a lot of apps, Tinder has only gotten worse and worse as time goes on.", "Latest update has changed UI for the worse, bunch of pointless borders around stuff that do nothing but consume screen real estate. They've also disabled the ability to zoom photos by dragging down on them like we could do in previous versions, so when users have poorly cropped / zoomed-out photos where you can't see them, now you can't make them easier to see. It also seems like every update makes the blurred cards of recent likes even more blurry, to the point that they're now useless.", "I NEVER GOT TO USE THE APP. Once I created a profile, I changed the settings and started to update my bio. As I was completing the About Me section, prompts came up asking if I was human then a screen saying that I'm banned and won't be able to reactivate the account. I never even got to use the account. The only thing I can think of is that using the option to block contacts triggered it. My photos and everything else weren't inappropriate. A waste of my time and sign not to be on this app.", 'Very limited features, they want you to pay for basic stuff. I get matches with people who I am sure I never liked . Matched me with same people 2-3 times. Doesn\'t show all people around me (I tested with friends). Shows 99+ liked me since last year but blocks and hides those profiles to force me to buy plus/gold version of the app. Once in a blue moon it shows a "secret admirer" but the last time it was a person with whom I had already matched and unmatched. Disappointment', "The app does next to nothing about the constant stream of fake accounts, likely because this gives you a seemingly high number of anonymous likes, which pressures you into buying premium to see them. (Which I've had from the start) For example, every day or so I would get a new like, from a new account, exactly 30 miles away. Dozens of these. The app isn't designed to find you matches. Its designed to string you along for as long as possible to keep you paying for it.", "Every time I open the app since downloading several days ago, I'm met with a screen to verify my profile with photos. When I go to take the photos, the buttons don't work meaning I can't actually verify my account. I can't use the app at all, not even to delete my profile. Support has been giving canned responses which don't actually address the issue. Kind of a bummer.", "The latest update has removed the option to hide your profile, so if you meet someone interesting the only option is to close your account completely instead of deactivating it while you see how things progress. Several days later and 'disable discovery' still doesn't work. The only option is to remove your photos and block payment. Finally, after two weeks it's been fixed.", "The app seems like a scam to me. I paid for the gold membership and I stopped getting likes. Once it ran out, the likes started coming again. The gold membership is pointless, it just gives you unlimited likes and allows you to see who liked you and constantly presses you to upgrade to platinum. The app seems to drip feed you the matches, just enough to keep you engaging and liking other profiles. I wouldn't waste your time paying for it. If you use it for a couple of months you get free matches", 'Practically unusable - gets stuck on "Finding people near you" and other tabs don\'t load content either. The content does eventually load bit by bit, taking multiple minutes for each tab. Images then take even more time to load in, sometimes never actually loading. Other apps don\'t have the same issue and speed tests don\'t show any issues. Edit: no way to undo an accidental swipe without paying. Overall frustrating experience.', "Easily the worst dating app I've used, go find a competitor. I've had plenty of matches and successful dates on other platforms, but Tinder has only ever resulted in a few dead-end matches. And it's not hard to see why. There's no recommendation algorithm, it's just a firehose of low effort profiles which have nothing in common with you. They have a page which gives you a couple of loose categories, but then they kneecap it by hiding important parts of a user's profile for no damn reason.", 'No matches unless you upgrade. Then you\'re getting secret admirers that you already received before. So you\'re basically paying for the same thing, over and over. Also, you have to remove your payment method when you sign up for the upgrades because if you simply "cancel" the upgrade with how the app functions right now, it won\'t work and you\'re going to be getting charged.', 'Weird. This app I\'ve used for only 4 days and for some reason after 3 days of talking to a person that person all of a sudden doesn\'t message back and only new matches seem to respond. And as soon as youbtjink that you\'re going to "click" with someone all of a sudden they\'re gone from your messages. All of a sudden too in the middle of me messaging back to someone all.of a sudden the entire conversation disappears. This app is rigged and controlled. Happened with every single person I messaged.', "If the app is running slow or not responding, try switching from WIFI to Data on your phone. It makes a huge difference for me even though my WiFi is supposed to be faster than data. Not a bad app in terms of user interface and better than many others in this regard. The content might or might not appeal to everyone's needs/taste but this is a reflection of the social environment.", "Practically broken. Every message I send gives me an error or crashes. Spent 45 minutes trying to talk to a match only to have the system fail every time I try. Restart doesn't fix, reinstall makes it worse. Considering it's already designed to be as ineffective as possible this is basically my last straw.", "Super intrusive ads. I get sent push notifications constantly. I can't turn them off because then I won't receive notifications for messages from actual matches. Their monetization model is predatory. Intrusive ads don't stop even if you buy the mid tier option (which is expensive at 15€ a month). Very bad value for what you get. Oh and to get the full experience, without ads etc, you need to pay 35€ a month. Sure, Jan, let me get my checkbook.", "New account, updated profile and pics, everything was supposed to work but out of the blue - banned. And then started working again, purchased platinum and still nothing works. Same people keeps appearing and even if liked, they doesn't appear in the Likes Sent section. Happening to almost all as I can see in these recent reviews of the application, this is just not is expected. I am waiting to see if they can fix it.", "It won't allow me to delete my account! When I click on the option, I'm directed to a screen asking if I'm sure, etc., but there's no button I can click to delete it. I even updated the app, but it's still the same. Tinder has reached a new low! Edit: 3 days later and the issue in the app still persists! I managed to delete my account only through a browser.", '"face to face time" doesn\'t seem to work. At least not in my country. And yes I reinstalled the app and checked connection issues. This is a "safety breach". It requires other apps and disclosure of unwanted personal information to see who you\'re talking to. In the event that users might be disconnecting calls willingly, I would suggest a more informed notification like: "user so and so has disconnected the call" so that one can opt to Unmatch fake profiles and other time waste attempts.', "Not worth paying for. Ive been swiping for ages and paid for additional benefits thinking I'll have more chances. But free version and paid version will still feel the same cause chances are still slim both ways. Only been match with 3. Only one replied but that one didn't work out. So still searching and no real good outcomes. Paid for bumble. I think chances there are better. Been matched to 17 people there already. Almost all replies too. Tinder aint working as it's suppose to. Lipat nalang.", "Makes my phone restart. Can happen within seconds after clicking on the app or after 10 minutes... Phone: ZTE Axon 40 Ultra Will change rating if this gets fixed. Makes it pretty much unusable and is just annoying if you do want to use the app... Other than that the app does what it should do and what you would expect. Also it's like probably all of these apps with a thought algorithm that tries to make you pay.", "App went from something pretty decent to an app where you have to pretty much pay to date almost. Daily superlikes have been removed and instead weekly superlikes were added. Even if you pay the ridiculous amount for platinum you don't even get much out of it. On top of everything, even if you change your preferences to disable push notifications for everything except messages and matches you'll still be met with pointless messages to remind you that you can still swipe randomly 3 times a day.", "Changed a lot since 2016! Less free. Now based around paying for an expensive subscription to view likes and get boosts. That said, I accepted the offer of the Gold subscription, 50% off for first month (£14.49). I hoped the subscription would allow me to verify myself as the free version didn't. Nope. Also worth mentioning that I'm not straight, and it's frustrating that straight women/ men keep coming up. Distance element is a bit iffy. Can't say I'll be keeping the subscription.", "I used Tinder off and on for a few years now and I tried their subscriptions. The UI is a lot better than most dating apps. And at first I got a decent ammount of matches. The past 2 years I almost never get matches in my homw town, common places I visit, or areas I commute to. I've updated profile pictures, changed my bio, and adjusted my preferences multiple times but nothing changes. Why would I continute to pay for the extras you get with Plus and Gold if it barely produces any results?"]

title: Between - Private Couples App
description:
Are you currently in a relationship? A special privilege exclusively for couples, start using Between! Between is a couples-only app where you can communicate more romantically and store precious memories easily with your loved one.

#Couple conversations with more love!
Between is a messenger just for two where you can use free emoticons and GIF selfies to chat more romantically!

#Precious memories can be stored easily!
You can store your photos, videos, and notes easily. Everything stays saved in Between even when you change phones!

#Schedules and special days saved in one place!
Check each other’s schedules and special days in Between! There is even a feature that automatically calculates the count down for your shared calendar and special days. Use the widget feature to check your d-days easily - like when you started dating or when your next date is happening!

#Anytime, anywhere - a conversation just for two! Try Between!
College couples, engaged couples - just any couple, really. By using Between’s PC version and free call feature, you can always keep the conversation going with your loved one! All Between data is encrypted and completely secure, so you can feel safe about using it!

For more information, please use the button below to read our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use, or visit our website.

[Permissions]
- CAMERA: Grant access to your device’s camera to take photos
- LOCATION: Grant access to your device location to show where you are
- READ/WRITE EXTERNAL STORAGE : Grant access to external storage to take, store, load images
- CALL_PHONE : Grant access to phone to make a direct call to partner from Between
- RECORD_AUDIO : Grant access to record and send voice messages to partner
- READ_PHONE_STATE : Grant access to read phone number when connecting to partner
- READ_CONTACT : Grant access to contacts to find partner’s phone number when connecting to partner
- GET_ACCOUNTS : Grant access to account data for advertising purposes
summary: When the relationship becomes official, Between.
