comments: ['The app does what it says. Intimate space for 2 people. I have 2 things i would like to say, if i make a call from the app, whenever i want to increase the media volume the phone tries to manage call volume. I have to shutdown between to manage media volume. And also, the calling feature is amazing, no lag, clarity is outstanding. Could you also add video calling feature? People who are in a long distance relationship would love that.', "The gifs/video sharing/stickers are great but as a whole, the messaging feature in the app is primitive. Would be great to see new updates of a more advanced messaging interface where you can select to reply to which message and so on. Perhaps even send likes to certain paragraphs etc. Also, lately I've been noticing a problem with the notifications. It's not always consistent. It's easy to miss out on texts. Please fix it, thanks.", "It's cute couple app. For starters it is good with photo albums, dates to remember and count downs. It will be awesome if the couple can share a to do list and update it apart from the notes feature. Also, if some couple goals are introduced where common and individual goals can be set and checked if met or not. the app has long way to go for being a more holistic couple app.", "Using this app for couple of months. Overall, a nice experience till now, sometimes, notifications are late, but the main disadvantages are: 1. Documents & locations cannot be shared 2. No options to send pre-recorded audios 3. Can't see whether my partner is online or not 4. Similarly, last seen feature is also missing 5. Main chat screen doesn't change automatically if my partner changes it", "It's a fairly nice app, and my girlfriend and I like it immensely, especially the animated stickers. However, it seems to lacking several features which would make the app more awesome. The only one I'd like to mention here and see first in sn updated version would be a feature to reply to specific messages like in WhatsApp or Instagram. That would be really helpful.", "love the concept and have used it for over a year. There are however some glitches that have remained. I don't get notifications at least half the time when I receive texts.When I open the app it says connecting and just doesn't send messages even over a stable internet connection. We prefer using this over whatsapp but for a messaging app it is unreliable. It would be great if we could reply to individual texts . Can improve the user interface.", "I love it but there are some issues with the audio call. The audio is very laggy and I wish there was an option for video call and also there's a problem in receiving notifications. If you could add a feature to reply to specific message it will be really helpful. Good app but could have done better . I'm also facing issue's in getting notification on my iPhone too even though I am using a new phone and have updated everything. Please add video call features.", "Have been using this for a few months and it's good. The best things are the uber-cute stickers and the gif selfies. Messaging overall is decent, and the calendar has potential. The in-app calling isn't totally up to the mark and notifications are sometimes skipped. Overall, both me and my girlfriend enjoy the cuteness of it and not having to be spotted as online on other messaging apps. Could you also add the option of deleting sent messages? I'm sure a lot of relationships can be saved by that", "I think is a nice app but the partner's last seen & the online need to be include and also i feel that it really less number of stickers and everything look similar ,it is not fine. Also it doesn't have even emoji,its bad. Its also unable to make video call .but the main idea was extremely Good perfect app for couple. I love the home screen and the special dates... please include all these in the next updates Thank you", 'Its a really nice app. Gives you the private space that you desire with your partner. Love the joint album feature and the important dates reminder. It would be great if the app could add the feature of replying to a specific message. People tend to talk about a lot of things at the same time..', '1. If the app had a section where the wall exists, to post texts/photos like facebook wall/a personal "social media". 2. Messaging could have a primary option to deliver reply after certain time passes, instead of sending reply when it\'s sent to minimise textual interactions. 3. When the other is busy you could have a pre-made reply if message is received during particular hours of inconvenience. This will help couples immensely, Great App!', "As someone who paid for the lifetime product, it's good, with room for improvement. I would like to see much better audio recording quality, calendar importing and exporting (to Google for example), GIF libraries, a snappier interface, a desktop browser UI (not a clunky app) and video chatting. Something like WhatsApp offers some of the basics mentioned above in a much better package.", "Like it, but I suggest some improvement 1. Video Call, so we don't need to change to another apps. But I realize this feature need more bandwidth or server setup. 2. Replying in chat. I hope it will be implemented in near future 3. Cost Control documentation, it will be nice and trackable to record our expense every our dates, or our saving for future milestone in relationships. Thank you very much for your app.", "It's a lovely app and a great idea but I think it could have a lot more functions. Could you please make it possible to edit each other's notes and make notes together? An idea would be to make a bucket list on the same page...we can edit in our own time so it syncs together. Or checklist? Or shared calender?", 'Almost perfect! The shared calendar and photo storage with notes plus cute customizeable themes, my partner and I purchased the life time subscription! However, the messaging can be improved by adding video call feature and replying to specific messages as well as emoticon react to each message as well. Hopefully this gets added in future patch updates!', 'Bought a lifetime access a few years ago, great app, really nice and simple. Adds are removed but I noticed on an update they enabled it and you have to turn it off in the settings. Not gamebreaking but annoying.', "Amazing app. I've been using it for years now. The only thing I wish is that there would be a search feature for the stickers. Or offering smart suggestions for stickers to send. We have a lot of stickers but it's difficult to find specific ones and know what pack they belong to when typing quickly.", "love this app so much I subscribed to the premium service lmfao. my wife and I have been together 1449 days( yes this app keeps TRACK!!) and it will keep other anniversaries for you for anything you want! we use this feature all the time it's so fun! Having our own app for texting and sending love notes to each other is awesome 😎 we would love a way to take notes together to keep track of movies we need to watch, we think this app would be perfect for that if there was some sort of new feature!", 'The app is awesome, especially the schedule feature. However, it would be great if there are more options for repeating schedule such as every two week, every third week, specific day of the month (ex: every third Tuesday of the Month). Also, i wish there are more function to customize the schedule such as colors and theme. Over all, it is a great app and worth buying the pro version.', 'NEAR PERFECT.. it desperately needs the feature to reply to specific messages. And emoji reactions to messages would be a great feature to see as well. All other functions of the app are great!', "My partner and I have been using this app, and so far it's really great! I upgraded to the lifetime plan to ensure a seamless experience without ads. It's worth it in my opinion, and I'm so happy there are a lot of options to share media.", 'Updating app. Suddenly when i type my msg. It sends in a timing in advance?? I\'m sending at 11.29pm. the app shows my msg is sent at 11.30pm. when my partner replies. The notification shows "in a min" den the text content??? Crazy.', 'Have used the app for years and paid for the lifetime plus back in 2018. Got a new phone, and now ads are back. Emailed them about it. No response.', "My boyfriend and I are in a long distance relationship between Florida and Texas. During the times we are in our own seperate states, we like to sleep in voice chat to be reminded of one another's presence. We used to use Discord but it is terrible on mobile with constant disconnects, inability to register voice, constantly invasive UI changes and such. This likely far less funded app still works wonders is such a great replacement! ♡ ^^", "I do love this app. But it's lacking something very important. The ability to schedule something to repeat every 2 weeks or three weeks. Could use more options for the repeat scheduling. Also would be great There was a way to integrate this with my Google calendar.", 'U should update yr app.. one will never come to know whether the msg has been delivered to the person or not until he reads it.. which is really irritating.. just like other apps this apps should hve this feature in which u came to abt the msg u sent has been delivered to other one or not.. Else.. would say overall a gud app..', "Smooth app. Private messenger. A shared calendar. Bunch of cutesy stickers neither one of will ever use. Bought the lifetime option. Feel that for the price there should be something more. Something for both partners to do together, interact together. It's a solid app but feels like there could be more to it. Will probably check out other apps. Try to find something more exciting.", 'Very complete system for couple: Stories, posts, gallery, personal chat, you can do everything there. Maybe improve the multiple messages in one notification part.', "I gave you 5 stars because this app is very useful for me and my gf to keep our memories. But we're facing a problem about limit of special day. It will be better if there is no limitting for special day creating.", 'Unstable connection and slow..Sudden server down and no notification or whatsoever from support.. Used to be good. Getting worse everyday.', "Excellent app. Only thing I wish this app would allow is to be able to manage what is done with pictures shared. I would like if you had the option to have them automatically download but other than that it's been great", 'Great app, my gf and me are in long distance relationship between Morocco and greece ! I wonder if i purchase subscription to get premium will my partner get it too ? Or both of us have to purchase ?? Also it ll be cool if u add more features such as video call and reply specific message as well reacting message, and add feature game ! As well a daily question about relationships and any topics!!! So on', 'App is good but some feature should be updated such as notification (dont know y but i really dont get any notification of msg from app) nd secondly reply to particular msg feature this 2 updates should be made as soon as possible for better experience', 'Its a great app. My girl and i use it everyday and we love it. It can use a some new features, however. Like replying and reacting to messages.', 'really awesome app, only thing our family need ir schedule for an event on every other week, because we work that way, im sure you will add this feature later!', "Good app and cute stickers that are worth buying. Needs a reply to message button so it's easier to see which messages you are referring to.", "Love the overall usability of this app but a bit peeved that 1. Pictures taken via the in app camera doesn't get send automatically - we have to choose first if we wanna crop the photo or not, 2. The messages don't get auto sent once there's a connection, and 3. messages sent via the app doesn't get displayed on either of my Samsung gear 3 or Huawei GT 3..", "Good idea bad execution. So if you buy premium you still need to manually turn off the ads. They tout privacy, and you can even lock the app behind a pin or biometrics but when on the active apps screen it doesn't blank out, so information can still be visible. Pictures are also not stored on devices, meaning everything uses data and lots of it, every screen takes time to load because it's all server side. One problem and you'll lose all access. Wish I knew this before buying it.", "It's a very cute app for long distance couples but the calls are very buggy and they crash after just one minute. It's frustrating because sometimes we just want to use a private app while not using the mainstream social media apps and call apps. I'd give it 5 stars if this feature was fixed.", "I'm abit on introverted side, so we didn't post each other on social media much. This app allows us to collect our memories together easily, rather than just sitting in gallery without any organization. You can't batch upload videos, but i understand that maybe the developer do it to save bandwidth and server space, so i'll still rate it 5stars."]

title: Pet Perfect - Puppy & Dog Care
description:
Recognized as one of the Best Apps of 2022 by Google Play🚀

Embark on a Journey to provide the best care to your Doggo 🐶.

Get easy to follow, daily schedule of activities, curated by experts.

As a dog parent, we know you are tired🤔 of wasting time looking for info according to your pets age & breed. It’s hard to keep a track of their daily key activities like feeding, walking, bathing, brushing, etc. Many a time you can’t remember the vaccination & deworming dates📅. Don’t know what steps to take for your doggo’s perfect upbringing? Because your pet can’t tell you what they need! We seldom seek the opinion of experienced Pet Parents & Veterinarians. But in reality, we need one place to learn all the best dog health care practices.

Pet Perfect is your one-stop companion for everything you’ll need to make the most of your furry friend. The best companion for your pets, curated with love and passion😇.

🐾Pet Journey- feature provides pet parents with step-by-step tasks on every stage of dog life according to your dogs age and breed.

🐾Pet Engagement - Have fun with your furball with our vivid range of perplexing dog sounds🔉

🐾Vaccination & Deworming Tracker - Get automated reminders for your dog's vaccination and deworming dates with just a single tap. 💉

🐾Dog Community - Get your queries resolved by Experts and Veteran Pet Parents & make new friends who share our love of doggo🐕.

Check our website here:- https://www.petperfect.in/

Also, do follow our Social Media Handles:-

Instagram:- https://www.instagram.com/petperfect_ig/

Facebook:- https://www.facebook.com/petperfect2021

P.S. Currently, we support the following pet types: Dogs

title: Mingle2: Dating, Chat & Meet
description:
Millions of people are signing up to Mingle2 every day because it is a fun and easy way to find meaningful connections. You will be able to make new friends, chat, and even date once you sign up! We make it easy for our members to meet each other. This way, we save everyone the time and effort of doing things on their own.

Our dating app, together with our website, is one of the biggest free online dating services out there. So no matter what you're seeking, we have a solution for you. You can seek marriage and relationships, or just make friends - Mingle2 has something for everyone! Meeting new people and making friends has never been easier. Whether you want to date someone, just find a friend for chatting with online, or even meet them in real life, it's easy with Mingle2. 💕

✨ Why Join?
➛ Get instant matches and recommended matches every day
➛ Search locally or in a foreign country and chat internationally with people from all over the world
➛ Find nearby people and see who is online to start chatting right now
➛ Find someone who shares commonalities with you - like age or ethnicity.
➛ Send and receive free chats daily
➛ Want to flirt with someone online and gain attention? Send them a super like with some nudges, winks, or hugs!
➛ We take your privacy very seriously and will never share any of your personal information with third parties. You can delete your account at any time or block anyone on the app.

✨ One of the best things about Mingle2 is that it never limits your interactions as other dating apps do! Mingle2 is free and unlimited: you can chat and hang out with as many new friends as you like and eventually meet up for a date. It can be hard to find dates these days, especially when you have so many other distractions. And that's why, at Mingle2, we want to provide the most accessible and user-friendly way for you to meet someone.
Dating apps are a dime a dozen, but Mingle2 stands out because it is available on a wide variety of platforms, and you have the opportunity to improve your chances of meeting someone who shares your interests

✨ How to use Mingle2?
1. Sign up! It only takes 30 seconds to create your profile.
2. Searching for that special someone in your local area? Browse through our database of profiles and find the person you've been searching for.
3. Find someone you like? Start a chat!
4. Filter and search based on many different preferences with an easy-to-use system. You will only see members that are a good match for you!
5. Want to chat right now? Who's online will show you all of the online users in the world.
6. Play Mutual Match and meet someone wonderful!

✨ We love our members and want them to have the best experience possible.
1. No Fakes! Safe and Secure! We strictly monitor who uses our app, so if you don't want to talk to someone, you can block them with one click.
2. Prove you're the real deal and verify your profile with Photo Verification.

✨ Our Mission:
Our mission at Mingle2 is "helping people connect," so we invite you to be a part of our community and enjoy all the perks that come with being a member.

Mingle2 is free to use and available on multiple platforms, and that will never change for our main features. If you're looking to get the most from Mingle2, you can also subscribe to our optional subscription, MinglePlus.

Download our free online dating app, find your match, and have fun!
-------

Terms of Use:
https://mingle2.com/welcome/showTOS

comments: ['Very limited in the "Free" version as marketed. Basically it is the platform that holds portfolios. Inable to interact or communicate or even see who viewed you, it\'s pay to play. This is fine but don\'t over emphasize and market a "free" application it is only the doormat. Second, have the option to organize potential matches by distance and when someone says within 30 miles, if there\'s only 6 people show me 6 people. Don\'t change MY preferences just to show me more of YOUR customers.', 'This app is very similar to Tinder, which I very much like. The price to view members who like you is just where it needs to be. However, the app always restarts when my phone accidently loses wifi connection, which happened while I was writing messages and making my profile, so I had to start all over. The distance spectrum is also way off, when looking for people within a 50 mile radius, it was showing me people well over 2 hours away. A few tweaks and this app could easily surpass the others.', "Sooo many likes by strangers, you can click on every profile and never find them lol. Also I've clicked X on some profiles yet they still show up. Seen same people in different profiles which tells me fakes. I got more likes on here then all other apps put together. So many Asian people are nudging all the time. No one from local area/country or at least who are ever online lol. Literally no one ever talks", 'Update: theres plenty of activity and i would give a higher rating if profiles were verified or vetted a bit better cauae theres a lot of fakes and the messaging system seems a bit buggy, i have to go out of the app and re-enter for messages to appear often. Original.. as soon as i signed up theres apparently all these likes etc etc and a few conversations ensued which were so obviously fake its just totally disheartening.', 'Wonderful experience. The pricing of the membership is a bit high. Perhaps relook at the structure. But the caliber of potential partners is lovely. Also on the filter, if a person does not answer the questions they are includes in the search results when you want them excluded. So please attend to better filter', "I'm giving this app 3 stars only becuase the dating app seems to be charging people money in subscriptions. And the subs are not worth it. Becuase you pay for monthly and the users you want to be interested in they won't reply back to you. And the coin icon I don't know what's this for only for subscriptions. It's a bit like one of my projects to do with the coin. So my review is 3 stars. The users SG girls from Singapore on mingle seems to be inactive. And not one of them replys. 3 stars.", "Lots of fake accounts. This app looked promising at first. It allows for easily matching those that liked you but the more ladies I encountered, the more I realized they were all fakes. Most don't even bother to fill out their profile. As always they want to take you off the app to another messenger app or media account like Google Chat just in case their account gets deleted. Awful!", "Distance set to 25km? Here's a user from 200 miles away, y/n? (Ps - it's a fake Chinese account 80% of the time anyway). Usual outrageous stuff too, like getting 'liked' by one of the fake accounts immediately on sign-up and being taken to payment pages for eye wateringly priced 'premium' services (which you can shove). I didn't even explore it beyond that, was installed for less than 5mins. Awful, awful app.", "Excellent app to search a person for friendship, dating and making a relationship. It's easy to use and ad interruption is very less so we don't get frustrate with ads. Chatting is free that's the biggest advantage, but yes to get more benefits we have to buy subscription. Overall it's a genuine app and very few fake profiles are there.😀👏👍❤️", 'So far not too bad. LOTS of fake accounts, but that\'s part for the course for a dating app. I\'ll update once I start finding matches. Update--after having a account for less than 2 days, I have over 143 likes and about 10 messages from one picture accounts (with no other info or a location) all just saying "hi". I am not that attractive people. I don\'t think there are real accounts on here. If there are, you need to slog through the literal deluge of fake accounts.', "The app is good and works nicely but the site is absolutely riddled with scammers They need to block all these accounts. I have 81 likes I can't see, but I won't pay because they're probably all scammers. They say they are from the UK but they don't know the location of the city they say they're from! Often say they work in fashion, own business and also investments. Pictures are often young asian girls. They try to get you on Skype. Sometimes WhatsApp, not uk numbers.", "I been on the site for ages(months or years) and all I see is fake profiles, women who are on other sites with 17 different profiles and names, women who are not the age they say they are, or women who are after hookups, I'll be staying on the site but just won't be there as much as I used to be. I report fake profiles but nothing gets done, they just keep making new profiles, I am using Badoo more as I can select to search ONLY photo verified profiles, which Badoo DO check and verify.", 'I have signed up to see if I could find a friendship/relationship. I do understand that this site is public and for that anyone can sigh up and post what they like. In just a few days I have come across a few very strange characters, individuals asking for "business" , many without any info on their profile, a fair few who lied about their age and some who will not take NO for an answer. Everyone should provide all info on their profile including up to date photo. Men should not pose topless!', "I've been pleasantly surprised by this app. It's a huge improvement from it's competition with a lot more options and opportunities for the free user. The standard of users I've found to be much better too. I'm really liking it so far and I'm likely to go to a paid account as I can see the benefits along with a lot more genuine users compared to the likes of hily. I've only given 4 stars as I haven't been on here long enough to make a full assessment but it's looking good so far.", 'The Best App one can really understand the way of legitimate surrounding but not Easy to find Real people but honestly now mostly are asking for payment . To meet and to see nude Video all are mostly fake just in the name of any profile they lure and trap them so kindly do such a way atleast authenticity of people who address mingle .', 'Very good app, free to use for the most part, match contact freely, payments are only really for seeing who has liked you and unlimited likes, things like that. The free likes are decent enough tho, overall very good!', "Worst and most BS App ever! It didn't have any real people on it! It only had scammers, and frauds on it. The one person that seemed real scammed for more money from me to come see and ignored me after! Everybody on there was worth reporting because of that nonsense... I want my money back but their tech support is lame, and totally unresponsive! Don't get it and if you do don't even spend money on it. You'll regret it I promise!", 'Awful app, I\'ve seen more fake profiles and scammers than sand grains on a beach. I\'ve reported loads to mingle but they obviously don\'t have face recognition software as the same pictures come up again and again under different names. Then to top it off they have stopped me reporting people saying "user bad". What a joke. AVOID AVOID AVOID. Don\'t waste your money on this 4th rate app.', 'A lack of default verification, and typical spam-like initial contacts, location changes, bot-like comms, etc. Better than some other sites, but will see if things improve.', 'I first joined Mingle2 in 2019. I liked it how fasted I was able to find a compatible match within two weeks. I like it and I often use it to meet new friends', "Don't bother using this app I traveled over 1000 miles from home to another country and the exact same profiles said they were close in the area i was in and they are all Chinese looking females. I must be special if they all followed me to Bulgaria from uk And I changed all my location and settings in the app to my location I was in but never changed any profiles. They message wanting your email or whattsapp number", "I am new here but this app is ok for me, organized not too messy. Just worry to pick match coz some of it no details, no photo or photo only 1 atleast 2 to proved they are real. And i guess showing date of joining is very helpful to know who's new and not.", "Just a friendly warning...Im pretty sure you're aware, but for those who are not.The profiles that show their what's app numbers or contact are not real people, rather an escort agency.. I wanted authenticity.. Though the app is way better than most... This should be scrutinized ASAP", "Great app. Awesome way to meet new people if you're done with bars. Not sure if everyone is real but the ones that message you definitely are.", 'Easy to use. Free with ads and the ads are not too invasive. The option to purchase an upgraded version.', "The app is good and responsive but a good amount of stuff is pay to access, when people like you, you can't even see who they are until you pay for premium, other than that I haven't used long enough to tell what else is pay to use but most features are.", 'This like so many dating apps is filled with profiles using photographs, mostly from well-known adult film stars. The photos are actually giving away free by the adult sites and promoted and then used to create fake profiles. In two weeks alone I probably closed or reported close to 50 profiles that were using false photos and information. 80% or more of the profiles use fake or stolen photos. And that might be conservative', "I'm very happy with this app and easy to use it. I meet and date from different countries people. But be careful are to much lazy scamers frauds parasites using fake acounts here and from other people pictures using they, so they just looking for fast cash 💸 you can got them with first contact so because - They understand just what they want.", 'One of the best dating app in all. It was very easy to use and to dates. No needs to any amount. We can make so many likes. Five star ⭐✨⭐✨⭐✨', 'App is very nice works pretty well. Provide a nearest users which helps to get connected with people with similar interests.', '"Hide" button needs to be fixed please. The girls I don\'t love will stay on my likes list and will keep adding up. Makes it look messy and crowded. I will eventually have 99+ likes and it will take too much time to find the few girls that I am interested in.', "Very bad service doesn't validate verified pictures. Can't log into my account. Once again very disappointing you subscribed me to a daily points scheme and without any notification the daily scheme just stopped. Please add the remaining points asap. To top it all today even though I haven't been sending any messages or putting anything offensive on my profile for weeks my account was banned because I have received many bad reports . You are just a bunch of hypocrites I'm glad not paying", "What I'm looking for in a dating app, although so far lots of scammers (which the app is upfront about and regularly gives tips on avoiding) it has a lot of potential and I hope it gets more real people.", "Very Bad Expernice.It's worst app having seen, just getting only fake request and mostly r here pimps. So many problems with software. Range n age limit increase itself. Sorry", "It's a nice app, I feel it has potential I'm really looking forward to it and if I does well I'll give it a full rating all though it doesn't really matter.", "Using this app is simple, but wait that's what others app too. The main issue is to find the right profile/person which we are searching. There are lots of fake profile, which are trying to scam you. I think the developer team should come up with new ideas by which the profiles became genuine/verified, so that we can get for which we are using the app. Another issue is about the filters, the filters are here for only show. They are not showing proper results, which it should be showing.", "It's easier to use than Tinder, with Mingle you just scroll down to see more pics, also the app gives you access to features for free periodically. You can message and meet ppl on this app totally for free, plus if you need help, you simply msg the staff from the app. Ads are shown infrequently, but beware many fake profiles", 'Would give more stars but 90% of the profiles are spam/scam bots. The function of the app itself is pretty good, not overly restrictive like every other dating app out there. I would reccomend 2 things. First, there really needs to be some kind of human verification process. There are many out there. Second, in notification settings there needs to be a way to turn off promotional notifications.', "The app gets stuck alot and unlike other apps you can't view the people who likes you, on all other apps you see emediatly who liked you without paying for premier or extra features.", "I have had TERRIBLE luck with dating apps as a demisexual. Most people jump right into the bedroom stuff but with this app, you aren't allowed to be sexual in your bio and you can report anyone being a creep. It has put me at ease completely and I have found it easy to not only be approached, but to approach others. Which is great for a shy introvert who has been out of the game for 8 years lol I HIGHLY recommend this app!!"]

title: Bumble: Dating App & Friends
description:
Welcome to Bumble 💛 The community with millions of people where you can find dates, make new friends, and meet people.

Bumble is a free dating app and social network for singles; the perfect place to meet new people, in an instant. Whether you want to find friends, make genuine matches, find meaningful connections, chat with strangers, make new friends, or even expand your professional and social network, we’ve got you covered.

Changing the rules of dating

Bumble is a free dating app (to download and use) founded on respect, equality, and inclusion. You can find dates, meet up, and meet new people the way you've always done — but on Bumble, women always make the first move. You won’t find that on any other dating apps. 🕒 With heterosexual matches, women have 24h to start a chat, and men have 24h to respond 💬 Other matches (LGBTQIA+) have 24h to start a chat or reply before the match expires 👥 Bumble comes in 3 modes to suit what you're looking for: Date, BFF, and Bizz

Discover our amazing features

Meet new people, make new friends, or find a great date using our free dating app. We’ve levelled up from the days of dating sites, and now you have all these features at your fingertips: 👉 Unlimited Swipe: Meet new people by swiping left and right as much as you like 💬 Unlimited chat so you can find the right matches 🎵 Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends 📹 Use Video Chat to get to know your matches better

Match with the right people

We're the first app to combine dating for singles, meeting new people, and making professional connections all in one app. We’re different from other dating apps, because we make it easy for you to connect. 📹Use Video Chat to get to know your matches better 📷 Send your videos and favorite pictures while you are chatting with new friends 💤 With Snooze Mode, hide your profile whenever you want (you'll still keep all your matches!) 🎵 Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends

Boost your dating life with Bumble Premium

Bumble is a free dating app to download and use, and always will be! Our Premium features help you enhance your Bumble experience. 💛 See everyone who swiped right on you (your Beeline) 🔁 Rematch with expired connections for a second chance at a date 🔄 Extend your matches by 24 hours The buzz is real Bumble is much more than just a dating app for singles, or your average speed dating night. Join our like-minded dating community, meet new people, find your ideal partner or date. Here are our core values: 💛 We believe healthy relationships are fundamental to living a productive and positive life 💛 In the fight against old-fashioned hetero-norms, women always take the first step. 💛We've changed the rules of the game to switch up the dynamics of dating 💛Unlike other dating apps, kindness is at the core of everything we do Inclusivity is key We’re committed to being totally inclusive, and supportive of our community whatever their gender, sexual orientation, or religion. Whether you’re looking for a place to find friends, a gay dating app, a bisexual dating app, a lesbian dating app, an LGBTQ dating app, a Christian dating app or a Jewish dating app; We’ve got everything you’re looking for in our lovely community. --- Bumble is a dating app that is free to download and use. We also offer optional subscription packages (Bumble Boost and Bumble Premium) and non-subscription, single, and multi-use paid features (Bumble Spotlight and Bumble SuperSwipe). Your personal data is securely stored on Bumble - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions https://bumble.com/en/privacy https://bumble.com/en/terms Bumble Inc. is the parent company of Bumble, along with the dating apps Badoo and Fruitz. Enjoy all our dating apps!
summary: The dating app to meet new people, chat and date with singles or make friends!

comments: ["It is a total waste of time and money. It does not matter if you have premium, you won't be receiving any matches at all (I had subscribed to the premium, still the same). It's like a window shopping app where you just keep scrolling and scrolling until you're satisfied without hoping to get anything. For once I thought this app could be genuine and I purchased the premium, but no, if all I had to do was left and right swipe people, I might have as well stayed on Tinder for free.", 'The UI is quite user friendly. But few things which can be improved on. 1. Message notification doesn\'t pop up a lot of times 2. Call notification doesn\'t pop up ever, plus call drops multiple times 3. Filter option doesn\'t work properly, for example if I choose age range 33-36, I still see people of age 23 4. Algo for common interest can be improved specially for best bees feed, I get best bees who want "Something Casual" while my preference is "Relationship"', 'Totally wast of time & Money, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "1. Poor algorithm. When you don't have premium, it shows you all persons within small distance. Once you subscribe to premium, the people shown would be around 100 km. Very few local profiles are shown. So the developer's motive seems to attract people to Premium subscription by showing good profiles, then serve trash. 2. Even though I cancelled the subscription in advance, it charged me for another month and didn't give premium features. 3. Useless app. Never coming back.", 'As a long-time user of Bumble, my recent experience has been disappointing. Despite being active, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', 'I can not escape the feeling of a jacked up algorithm. One that puts people on the bottom despite their subscription in some sort of "lead with a carrot" business model. That or no one\'s on this app, and the app does not seem to want to take people who have not been on the app in months in the algorithm. Furthermore, there seems to be no quick, obvious, and easy way to end your subscription.', "I used the app for about one year and had a few decent dates out of it. However, as soon as my paid membership expired, literally overnight, I went from having zero people interested in me to 47, of course being prompted to go back to the paid version. Didn't change location or filters during that time, so obviously, they are manipulating the truth and the end user.", 'For an app that requires access to your location, you\'d think they\'d give you an accurate mileage estimate for people near you, but nope they can\'t be bothered to do that. Just saw someone who lives in the next state over from me and, according to Bumble, they\'re 85 miles away from me. However, when I enter the city on Google maps, it gives me a much more accurate mileage: 156 miles. That\'s a 71 mile difference, nearly double Bumble\'s "estimate."', 'The worst of all dating apps. Like Tinder, gives you options from ridiculous distances, especially if youre in rural areas. Most people are visitors from very far. The worst part is once youve swiped left on a potential match they are removed from your likes and you probably will never see them again."you\'ve missed a potential match" forever. Also they put the location at the bottom so you have to scroll the whole profile just to see the distance factor. Overall a very bad experience', "This app is ok but needs work. I canceled my premium. One of the big thing that must be added is letting me know when the last time a person logged on. That way I'm not wasting time on someone who hasn't logged on in a month. That's a waste of a swipe especially a super swipe. Also need to separate straight people from gay. As I have swiped on the wrong person and they get all offended. If these things were fixed I would keep logging in.", "I have emailed support multiple times about transferring my premium subscription from a previously deleted account to my new account and there has been absolutely no response from anyone in support. Unlike other dating apps that allow you to re-instate previously purchased subscriptions without having to email support (that doesn't respond to you anyway), Bumble just really need to sort its issues out.", "Terrible app! you have to pay for basic Things like just to see who liked you you can only see the people that complimented your profile and that's limited, You have to pay for everything like super swipes & to go back if you made a mistake. They took down one of my photos for going against community guide lines but it's a picture of me in a long dress no nudity nothing inappropriate. & whatever preferences youre allowed to choose (age and distance) doesn't narrow down the field", "Still an awful app, I've tried it multiple times and men never see their related matches. We get search results from 97 miles away from people who don't match our criteria. And you can tell even from the blurry images that you never see the people who actually do swipe on you. It's entirely designed to keep you swiping without any actual results. Don't waste your time", 'Waste of time and money, the location of people is totally hit and miss, when you do "match" with someone it is debatable if they are actually real or generated by the app to keep you interested. For an app that is meant to compliment your social circle/find people with similar interests and so on, no one actually talks. Might just stick with the old-fashioned way!', "All the other dating apps I get plenty of matches, but bumble is awful at what it's supposed to do. No matches, and because of the time limit to message you often miss the matches you do get. Pointless app and a waste of time. Edited, after the reply I received more likes than before after I left a review, strange, then they started to get less and Ive just realised the compliment feature has been removed. I think the free compliments were the only thing that made bumble worth using.", "Because you can't filter results by important categories like religion without paying, the app is essentially useless. You are forced to weed through thousands of profiles that aren't close to your value specifications. The profiles layout is also a mess, listing interests in a buckshot-style jumble where things like children, religion, age, location, etc are thrown into the mix randomly and you have to look around more to find it (those should be at the top of the list).", "I think it's more likely to get struck by lightning and win the lottery at the same time than get a match. It's way too easy to accidentally swipe left, and those swiped on can't come back, and the highlights cost 8 bucks each. Like, who even? Fix your app.", "What's the use of having the dating interface if you can't even contact/connect to a prospect without having to pay a bloody fee? And even then, even if you do want to spend on it, the chances of getting catfished is unbelievably high. The aspect of this side of the app is completely useless. I will give it props if you're using it for business networking purposes and works well if that is your ONLY objective. The dating interface is bonkers.", "it's very picky and decisive wanting you to spend money just like any other app. they shouldn't just give the option free to connect with anyone but they should make a lot easier if you want to say hello or block or do what you would like explicit or not. there's filters for everything. just make it all around app that everybody can use. it's 2023 and this is the longest run on sentence I've ever done. but we all know what we're looking for in the beginning and in the end and who may b in middle", 'It\'s just as bad if not worse than Tinder surprisingly. Customer service is 0/10. I can\'t get a hold of any humans to discuss my problems, I\'ve sent at least 10 emails. I get photos randomly taken down because they "violate" community standards according to the algorithm. I\'ve purchased the lifetime membership twice and, like anyone, deleted and reinstalled the app many times, but now I dont have the lifetime membership, and they won\'t fix it. Summary: All dating apps suck.', 'Bait and switched into "subscription". If I wanted to continue after the 1 month trial I agreed to paid for, I would have chosen a less expensive package. I cancelled the subscription and contacted support 20 minutes after charged, I had to open a PayPal case. 2 weeks later Bumble hasnt responsed. Bait and switch auto-subscriptions are theft. Ive lost $60 to this "free" app and have zero dates to show for it, just "content sellers" posting their Instagram and onlyfans.', "Bumble is useless without a premium subscription. All filters except age & distance are now locked behind a paywall, so rooting through all the bad matches to find someone is a chore. You only get 24 hours to respond to a match, otherwise you have to pay to rematch. And if you accidentally swipe left on someone you do want to match with, you have to pay to undo it. If the woman matches but doesn't start chatting within 24 hours, (Something that happens A LOT) the match disappears completely.", "Not sure how I feel about it. So far I like how the verification process goes and the app runs smooth but been on it for 2 weeks with premium and not worth it. You don't really get as much people due to the fact that the premium is expensive and also the notification when you do get someone doesn't really appear on either the app notification or email. Also anyone you've liked you can't tell if they even seen the like. Definitely needs more work for the cost.", "I like this app, in my opinion it' s very nice but it's just ridiculously expensive. probably the most expensive app I've tried. so I subscribed in different app although I still use the free features on Bumble. Some things could be better. don't like the fact that only match girls can do first move, think that's silly. I've been on a date with a girl and she complained that men never say anything, then I said we can't, first move has to be from girl.", "When you pay to upgrade and it run out. I have found that when you get likes the system doesn't match you with them. I wants you to upgrade. They then timed out and their gone. Don't pay for the upgrade or you'll just have to delete your account like I did. It should be above all, about finding a connection.", 'Having a limit on likes per day isn\'t a bad idea, but this app\'s limit is almost cartoonish. I can\'t spend more than a few minutes per 24 hours swiping without being told I need to pay 3 WHOLE DOLLARS to keep going. It\'s asinine. On top of that, almost everything else is locked behind paywalls. Though I do like that you can list your pronouns without having to first pick "man or woman." But that\'s just basic decency, not a feature', "I've been on Bumble for a few weeks now. Ended up paying for the boost, matched with someone who, for their prompt, asked me to verify my photo. Prior to this I had tried probably 20 times to verify, and was never able to. Yes I tried photos with just myself. Mimicking the pose, hand gestures, and even location exactly, but couldn't verify. Now I'm stuck on the verification screen, I'm being ignored by the support team. 0/5", "To the pros: fairly clean & simple UI, tho a bit outdated. Cons: gps based search, meaning swiping endlessly tons of people in proximity, including tourists & people in the airport and there's no way to filter out. And you have to scroll all way down to find out person is living somewhere else or doesn't disclose. So looks like tinder at this point and more oriented towards finding one night stand nearby. Exhausting & very disappointing experience for me and after a long time trying it, I'm out", "So there is a subscription model for 21 dollars a month, but this subscription does not come with the ability to see who likes you. For that, you'd need ANOTHER subscription 13 dollars more expensive than the regular subscription. To unlock seeing who likes you, you have to pay 35 bucks a month. That's gotta be an accident, right? Why would this feature not be in the regular subscription?", "Don't buy the spot lights!!!! The app will self activate them and email support stopped trying to help! I tried just not being on for a couple days till subscription weekly one was added when I did log on it has already used it and times out! Yes I emailed them and they tried a couple time but stopped helping. Lost 5 so far. And they are not doing anything to help. Very disappointed in you guys. I'm done I've cancelled the subscription and not trying to get your help when you just blow it off.", "It's...ehhh. My issues are the inability to filter out poly/ENM profiles looking for unicorns, continuing to get likes from men when I am a lesbian, the constant message ads and empty notifications, and the high cost of premium. Been using it for a few months now, met one potential person but I'm demoralized. I won't renew my subscription.", 'I tried several times to get my picture verified, including taking a picture, posting it, and then without moving, taking the same picture in the verify area. They still said I could not be verified. I contacted customer service about it, and my app got stuck on the verify photo page and would not leave that page. I then contacted customer service two more times about it and still stuck. It would be nice to at least be able to try the app out.', "Well developed but core functionality is behind a paywall, and there's no incentive to pay for an app that feels dead. Honestly it looks great but actually seeing who has matched you is behind a pricy paywall, so it's a dice roll as to whether two people see each other, and this makes the limited ability to like people (an otherwise good feature) greatly lower the ceiling on chances of matching. People have moved onto other apps.", 'The app needs work on how it recognizes and interacts with phone media. It\'s difficult to get it to recognize videos & it has double standards when it comes to photos and videos. The app allows the most pixelated pictures you\'ll ever see; however, it won\'t let me upload perfectly fine videos due to "low quality" (they\'re not), wrong dimensions (huh?), or not being shot on my phone (really?). So far, it\'s not very user-friendly.', "Swear this app is a con. I have 9 so say 'matches waiting for me'. I just used a boost and spent the full 30 minutes swiping to see if I would get anywhere with any of them (get rid of or properly match with them) and I didn't come across a single one of these people. It is so blatantly a scam just to make people feel like they have no option but to pay to see more etc etc...", "The customer service for Bumble is absolutely terrible!! I have contacted them over 10 times in a two week span and Bumble has not replied to ANY of my inquiries. My account is stuck on photo verification and I cannot access any othet part of my account. I am currently paying for the Premium option as well. Don't use this app - they dont care about you at all.", "Bought premium (little under $9/wk because it was on sale). Was good at first but right now it's not letting me view profiles of people who have liked me (I can see their picture but when I click on them a blank square comes up instead of their profile). Literally the only reason I bought premium was so I could see people who liked me, so it's very frustrating that the feature stopped working. Hopefully it will work again soon. Edit: also not letting me send or view messages right now. :/", 'Very good idea but poor efficiency; is a pity that girls have only 24 hrs to establish a contact... Also, you should put more filters: for example: eyes color, hair color, etc., and stablish options to search by that criteria; for exemple, if I only want to meet people without kids or blonde girls or short (or tall) girls, be able to find those persons easily.', "The premium option is nice, maybe a little expensive for what you get. My issue is that with the premium subscription you run out of people within your filters. But if you're subscription ends you will run out of likes before you run out of people within your filters. Things don't add up properly.", "Even after having premium it doesn't let's text to someone who liked my profile. It clearly showed in best bees match. But it didn't let me text. What a pathetic app. They just want you to keep browsing and keep paying for super swipes or compliments even after buying premium. You will get nothing here. I think they just got some profiles when they launched the app. Might be no longer active because this app doesn't let people text even after liking from both sides."]

comments: ["Overall impressions is that at this stage, the apps not worth the time. The biggest issue is that there are absolutely nobody on here. Even in a major Metroplex there is no one on here outside of the occasional working girl. I can log in at any point and there be nothing. No one is interested in this app and quite frankly it's but one of many trying to prey on men trying to get their rocks off.", "Bots, bots, bots. Two matches one initially England and then after the message usa, second also England and after first message norther Ireland. Also keep begging you to go to Telegram, I don't even know what that is but it was clearly a scam/bot account. Terrible app and after a couple days no matches within 200 miles. Savage and yeah don't bother with this thing.", "Not bad at all, only issue is... If your looking for people in your area. Your not gonna come across to many people... I had to set the setting for distance to 200 miles away and there obviously more people to see, that are closer but then your limited on how many people you can like. Then have to wait so many hours to be able to react again, but then the app tells you there isnt anymore profiles to see and to adjust your settings. That's the only thing I dont really like about it.", "Downloaded this app because I was like 'oh a new app, wonder what's it about' then it basically told me in order to continue I need to verify my account which is fine, but a hour goes by of me not using it, I get a like, and it tells me my verification failed and I got kicked out the system and I couldn't recreate a account and I even tried to uninstall and redownload it, nothing. I can't use my number or a email address", "Need a lot of development at this point, constantly get the same repetitive profiles, which are clearly scammers, even after reporting these profiles, it seems though nothing is being done. Not enough verification, or filtering to prevent this, and even after upgrading, it doesn't seem to be worth the money, most profiles are inactive or just people promoting selling content on other sites. App need a lot more restrictions, and needs to stop promoting inactive accounts.", "I got vip. It's ok and I've met one person that was a nice person but not what I imagined from the profile. Other women I've talked to seem to follow the whole scam attempts that you run into on every dating site. Not many matches so far or people close enough near me but not giving up quite yet. Just wish people were more real and honest. Ran into a few fake profiles, and when I match sometimes they seem to suddenly not be interested, which makes me believe it's an algorithm push.", 'Worst app. Used the app for 3 weeks. Zero success. So many fake profiles. If u happened to connect with any, after few text messages you get a pop up asking u to match to continue chatting. Waste of time', 'This app is glitchy, I have to restart it multiple times while talking to someone. Other than it being buggy and glitchy all the time, its a pretty good app.', "Another app afraid to let you see how few people are in your area or how few are recently active. Anytime a service won't let you confirm it has active local users then it's because they don't. What's worse is these kinds of tactics are exactly why they don't attract enough users. You'll have more activity if you stop putting basic confirmations like this behind a paywall, because that's what stops people from signing up or staying with you.", 'Disappointed difficult to understand the use of the site, lack of response, even with all aspects of interest, it made no difference to make a contact, pointless site, total waste of money, and my time 😕 . Total bs site', "I'm not sure how old this app is. Doesn't have hardly anyone on it. And most of the ppl it shows you profile pics of, havent been for wks or months. I should be getting paid to use this app, honestly.", 'I think this is a scam app because it says its free messaging and as soon as I went on the app I had to buy a membership and it wanted me to rate them straight away but at least I only paid £12 for a 1 month membership & the women who liked me where far away.', 'Just signed up. It got my location wrong and to change gota spend 12$, seems un reasonable for information they got wrong. Atleast let the person put in the location once the first time for free.', 'On the screen where it asks to create a username it doesn\'t let me hit "next" to go to the next screen. I was not able to create an account because of the glitch.', "Filled out profile did some likes or interest in a female quite a few actually. Then it was like what jus happened haven't heard anything for 2 days or 3 can only look at the people ya didn't wanna pick or have common. Interests with .KINDA REALLY SHOCKED .", "They don't fact check if a guy is sending or asking for nudes/$&you won't reciprocate they blackmail you&get you banned so it's too hard to make any connections w/real people&then they send you an email suggesting that yoU're fake&asked for$/scamming people when you did no such thing your messages are dry&you get flagged for sending photos or your pet&asking if they like animals. I have enough toys. I'm so convinced that the creators of these dating apps are phishers/hackers/terrorists. Can't d", "Pretty awful; verification took ages, pictures keep seeming to dissappear from my profile and to be able to do anything worthwhile, you've got to pay a pretty steep amount for what seems like an app no one uses", "Very difficult app even though there isn't much to it. I suggest that if somebody likes you that you should be able to see some of the profile to let you know if you are compatible or not.", 'Wildly disappointing. Instantly had 4 likes! Like as soon as my profile was made. Needs work but could be viably good with some changes.', "Definitely the best hook up app available. Find ppl close by and message for free. Doesn't push upgrading like most other apps. Great app!", 'I literally can\'t respond to the first message I\'ve gotten because the bar to enter text is all the way at the bottom of my phone and gets covered by my phone\'s buttons, so whenever I try to respond to the message, all I\'m doing is hitting the "back" or "home" buttons for my phone. That makes the app unusable.', "A lot of the accounts are classic scambait. The filters are... Speculative. You never know what you're going to get. Arbitrary center point for searches and no indication of cities/towns so if it's '40 miles away' in a 100mi search you could be from 60 to 140 out. Maybe it's a European thing.", "The only issue is distance is a little difficult and a lot of profiles don't have pictures. Also the messaging part needs some work. Hard to see the other person's message if you are typing at the same time. Otherwise a decent app", "SO HERE IS THE WORD, DONT TRY & PURCHASE A PACKAGE OR ANYTHING CAUSE I JUST ATTEMPTED TO & AFTER IT CLEARED, THE UPGRADE STILL HASNT TAKEN EFFECT IN THE APP. SO THIS IS AN ISSUE. I SPOKE TOO SOON On another CONSTRUCTIVE note, the glitches & the profile videos not loading needs to be addressed. Also, yuh should be able to chose a max distance between yuh & yur potential matches. A MAX DISTANCE THAT DOESN'T JUST CHANGE BACK TO IT'S DEFAULT.MAX SETTING AFTER YUH TRY & CHANGE IT.", "Trash app. Doesn't update actual current location unless you pay. Only desirable profiles are fakes selling OF.", 'I got on the app and used it for a week without any action. I went to my profile and although I distinctly remember selecting 6\'0" as my height (my actual height), the app placed my height at 5\'0"! Hilarious, but I\'m sure I missed out on plenty of potential matches because of this glitch! Also, not enough people use the app in Florida', "Best hookup app on the market, still bad. All the hookup apps are atrocious because of the prices. This is no different. Sure, $15 isn't much but for a hookup site that's way too much. Plus, while I have had some matches most are either not going to respond or not follow through with making plans. Whether someone is active or not shouldn't be hidden behind a pay wall since that kinda makes the effort of that account wasted.", "Unable to view profile once you've matched/messaged someone, bit clunky but other passable.", "Says someone likes you but it's not a new like, ie after notification, you swipe yes on all of the new swipes (about 3), not one match", "My experience hasn't been so bad although the matches it has provided have been SEVERELY limited. Usually I try not to rate anything I'm not going to give five stars to, but since it kept INSISTING that I rate it every time I check or write a response or two, it gets what it wanted.", 'Good App, easy to use. Did not get any response/messages. I have deleted my account and uninstalled the App.', "Super frustrating that you guys set my location 3 hours away from me. But I can't fix it without paying premium. Which I won't do without using the app for a few days or weeks. So why isn't there an option to just recheck my location??? Don't reply telling me you sent the info to the team.", "Hardly anyone in my area uses this app. Also doesn't help the app pushes you to rate 5 stars....must be why their ratings are that high.", 'Very Easy To find people to talk too and get along with, Im surprised i get actual responses from people instead of Someone trying to sell me content or want me to subscribe to their onlyfans', "Full of fakes and scammers just like most other dating sites. It's a shame that there isn't one site that filters out the bs.", "Money Grab app. Have to have one membership to search and then upgrade again to message. Rip off. Don't use", 'One of those apps which makes the amateurish mistake of having crucial buttons hidden below your Android home & back buttons on certain phones.', "I fell for it... There's a reason that last-seen button is disabled for free accounts. No one within 60 miles in the last month and I'm 20 miles from two cities. Functionally the app seems fine.", "App is pretty good although people who you match tend to be quite far away. Also it's hard to keep track of conversations without timestamps and read notifications.", "I uploaded a photo. They made me do a verification photo. Claims it's not me. Same face, same shirt. Same me. But I cannot go past that."]

comments: ["Well when most of the people on your site are in their twenties they're not called Seniors. There's no seniors on this site it's another fakr site with bots. You get messages left and right just liking someone's page as soon as you. Can you get free automated responses I have nothing to do with your message and you can't even send messages for free either.", "Even though I have paid for the premium it keeps telling me I have to be verified I go and get verified the next time I log in again it tells me I have to be verified then it doesn't match you with who you ask to be matched with and I would like to cancel and I can't find anyone to cancel my subscription. Is any else having issues with this app ?", 'Near Me ?????? I am in Ontario Canada and requested within 100 miles. Have had many in all parts of the States, Ghana, Germany etc but Canada let alone same province not showing up. Not interested in world wide but something realistic. Not impressed at all yet. Might be short time use', "This site is full of impersonators. Only one person turned out to be real. Don't waste your time with this app. It's also impossible to contact any customer service to cancel your account.", 'It keeps asking me to verify my account enough sent a lot of pictures and it keeps asking. Also it says everyone is near me but I do not live in the Philippines this app is a joke', "It's easy to install it's easy for a senior to have this app. Hope we can find more friends in here.", "A New user. My profile photo could not upload after several attempts. Please fix this bcos I can't find a match yet", 'this app keeps on telling me to verify account even though I have verified it and it confirmed. also bringing people outside of my chosen age bracket', 'I am not really happy with this site because I live in London but its showing me people mostly from as far as America.Its discouraging because I am a premium member.', "It is extremely security minded, it has multiple barriers one has to navigate. I almost gave up, but they came to my rescue by giving me another option. Unfortunately I cannot pay for premium service, as social security doesn't pay near enough to make ends meet. Great people, good site, beautiful yummy men.", "I can not access the app for about 2 days now, it has refused to open and i don't know what is the matter.", "I thought this was good at first. Really easy to use. But there are spelling mistakes in the notifications. The filter system doesn't work properly, matching you with people in other countries that I never asked for. I believed I had met a lovely man. But after 4 days of chatting online, he suddenly wants £500 to unlock his broken phone!! Total scam. And the others just wanted online sex. And finally, one man's profile picture was his genitals. Total trash.", "My profile still shows as regular member even though I paid for premium and have sent several emails asking for it to be corrected. No replies, no acknowledgement. It's seems to just be a money making machine someone put out there but no one is responsible for. Lots of inappropriate photos not monitored. It's been a waste of precious money!", 'good platform to meet matured people to make friends', 'it is realoooo I never new how good the app was until I used it my self like it is very important to reach out who we love', 'nothing but scamners and weird people. preferences are not observed AT ALL', "not easy to chat even if you're premium", "For me this app is the best one I've tried. All the others want you to pay a subscription before you can use all the features of the app but the Senior Dating let's you have more without subscription and the subscription isn't as expensive as some of the other apps.", "After 12 hours of use, 100% of my 'notifications' have been from people outside my configured area of interest.... and a significant number are under 40. (Not that I would have a problem with attempting a relationship with someone young enough to be my child... but it's a bit, well.... smells like bait for a scam) Not impressed with the number of local contacts.... but that says more about the reach of the app, than the app itself. I'll give it a bit longer before actually removing.", "A very neat and clean app without any zig zags. I suggest to organize tabs regional wise to make it easier. Easy to operate Ann's no demand for money like other apps do the moment you open the app. As far as I know, this is the best dating app so far with excellent operating system.", "Just started to create profile, and having just tried to do the same on another app but glitches prevented me from even creating an account so thought I'd review this one and say how easy it was to set up a profile etc. The app is easy to use and I'm really hoping that the user experience is good for the future!", 'I paid for a membership almost immediately, but only 1 mo, thank God. Now the site won\'t "verify" my account and no one will answer my emails. That\'s only the beginning. Tons of fake profiles mixed in with the real(?) ones. Apparently NONE of the profiles are getting "verified".', 'So far, best app for senior dating i’ve ever tried. Clean and intuitive interface design , making it easy to connect with other people looking for mature relationship. I’ve met some great people here!', "OMG! THIS SITE IS IN POLAND!! Only been on one day, had to pay $5.67 for the 6 month option and I was charged $33.99 just to look at my likes. Decided not to be on this site after all because the closest area search is 50 miles and there's nothing, so then the next is 100 miles, still nothing then 200 -300 miles! It's just RIDICULOUS! So I deleted my account. But I'm STILL on! I've tried to delete my account 5 times and it says it will delete the account, but it doesn't!", 'good and easy to use', 'I thought I\'d met a real one, a good one, genuine and honest. Within the first couple of message exchanges she invited me to Hangouts. When I couldn\'t get it to work, "she" asked for my number for texting. As soon as that started, she began to hustle me, insisting that I should trust her. That\'s a common opener for scammers, which I learned the hard way. Shameful.', "spent almost $40 and zero activity. no messages or notifications. no interest in me and I know other dating apps I've been on my phone blew up everyday with hits. I know I'm not hard to look at and have always been able to receive attention from the ladies so yeah this app is sucking and regret getting premium. I wont be renewing", 'Great experience so far,nice application to meet people and make friends... Still hoping to meet with my soul mate and making more friends. Just Navigate to get the actual and exact location you need. Please continue the good 👍 work of connecting people.', "Don't waste your time with this application! I'd say if your truly wato find a relationship this app is full of scamming men. Multiple profiles looking to take advantage of vulnerable woman! Please be cautious and don't even waste your time. No customer service! They state verification but what Exactly does that mean? Nothing at all considering I caught 7 people! Yes!!!! 7 men with fake profiles and had enough of this website! They don't care! Just looking for the money and not looking for cust", 'Do NOT get!!! FULL of scam artists! After second day i requested a refund. They never responded (all communication is through their email address, NO phone number listed anywhere!) I wrote them again 4 days later and still have not received a response from them, that was 2 weeks ago! The subscription it self is part of the scam!', "It seems interesting. Still trying to discover what it's all about. I will give a perfect unbiased review as soon as I meet someone. I would not like to give a full review appreciating when I have not yet used it for daust", 'Fraudulent individuals run rampant despite "terms of agreement." Senior Dating allows this behavior with no vetting. If you use the site, do yourself a favor and also download a facial recognition app to check on the profiles you like, or who likes you!', 'Photos of females are available but one wants to send message, app starts asking for money, which is very awkward. If you made it for senior dating then why are you asking for money. Without chatting with your friends how can rates any app. Very cumbersome situations', "This app is great. It's one of the few mature dating apps around, there are a lot of profiles to look at, and the features are great.", 'Is this a scam app or what. After paying for a premium subscription, they keep swinging me back and forth between regular and premium. Then you get screwed when you need to reach them through the help section and discover there is no contact in their help section. Just for the fun sign in, have fun😍💋! If you tickle fancy keep liking it! 👍💪']

title: Woo - Dating App for India
description:
Woo Dating is a ‘made for India’, online dating & matchmaking app that puts women *first*. 

We understand your issues with Indian online dating, which is why we built an app to inspire trust and comfort. Woo helps you  meet like-minded people, who feel just right for you. We know that gut instinct plays a big role when you like someone new, so we built our app from that place of sensitivity.
 
Woo Dating has matched over a 2 million single women and men in our core cities of Bangalore, Mumbai, Delhi, Gurgaon, Noida, and Pune. we realize how important it is to create the right environment. Unlike casual dating apps, singles on WOO feel secure and comfortable in finding, chatting, voice calling and meeting people they like.

Our matchmaking algorithms help you find and meet new people with a simple and easy to use digital dating interface.
Our curated community of ‘Verified Profiles’ match you to the right people. We recognize that there’s more to dating than just random flirting and casual flings. Our app gives you the means to spark great conversations and make meaningful connections in the real world. With the premium version of the app, you have a better chance of finding a date quicker not just in India but around the world. 
 
Key features:
 
📞WOO PHONE: Single women can place a voice call directly from the app while their number remains hidden and private. This specially created feature, unique in the world of dating, is available only to women.
 
🤐WOO SECRET: Single women's details (name, number, location), remain confidential. This information is not seen by anyone on the app. Dating should not be scary!
 
🤳WOO ANSWER: Users can add interesting answers to our fun questions and be discovered even faster. 

🌎WOO GLOBAL – with this international passport which is Free for  WooPlus user. You can meet interesting new matches in the USA, Canada, UK . Even Dubai and other Asian cities.
 
➕WooPlus: Woo Plus has many premium features which help you get matched better and quicker! Some features are: 👁️See who’s visited you, liked you, revisit the profiles you skipped by accident, get unlimited likes.
 
Here’s how it works:

1. Woo recommends profiles based on your 📍 location and interests. Match with people you like and kickstart something great.
 
2. You can anonymously like or dislike a profile by swiping 👈  or 👉! Woo gives you the power to 👍  or  ignore someone without revealing your identity.
 
3. If you both like each other’s profile, it’s a  match! A private chat room will open for the two of you. You can then send text messages and let the conversation flow!
 
 
 
_______

While Woo can be used free of charge, Woo Plus unlocks a tons of extra features! An auto-renewing subscription once taken will be charged to your Playstore account. The same will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period (depending on the pack purchased – for a 1 month subscription this will imply a renewal charge 24 hours within the end of one month). Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in Playstore after purchase or by contacting us via our support email. No cancellation of current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you decide not to purchase Woo Plus, you can simply continue using Woo for free.

Here are a few heart touching stories of couples who found each other on Woo.
https://medium.com/@dateonwoo/

Privacy and Terms:
https://getwooapp.com/privacy-policy

FAQ:
https://getwooapp.com/faqs/

A final word of advice -

Our romantic lives may or may not hinge on popular dating apps where Cupid's arrow may strike. But sometimes swipes and clicks don't cut it, and relationships become more than virtual. Couples may walk down the aisle, bringing their online connection into the real world, where the sparks may truly fly.

title: DogLog - Track your Pet's Life
description:
DogLog is an easy-to-use pet care app that makes pet ownership less stressful. It helps dog owners track their pet’s health, coordinates daily pet-related tasks, and lots more! DogLog is great for single pet parents and for families and has been downloaded by +100,000 pet owners.

PUPPY OWNERS
1) Track your puppy's training.
2) Understand your puppy's potty schedule to get them potty trained.
3) Set reminders for upcoming vaccination and record vaccination dates. 

OWNERS WITH SICK OR ELDERLY PETS
1) Track your pet's symptoms to understand if they are getting better.
2) Share activity and symptoms data with your vet.
3) Set reminders for giving medicine to your pet so you never miss a dose. 

PET SITTERS AND DOG WALKERS
1) Add your pet sitters and walkers to your Pack so all activities get recorded.
2) Pet sitters/walkers can add photos to your Pack so you never miss a moment.
3) Rest assured that your pet is taken care of.

Don't spend any more time wondering if your dog has been taken care of, download DogLog and enjoy the serenity of always knowing how your dog's day is going.

BENEFITS
1. Form a "pack" with your fellow dog caretakers
2. Log activities, such as giving food, going on a walk, and giving medication
3. Add comments to activities to provide extra information
4. Get notified when activities are logged for your pet with alerts. 
5. Create reminders and alerts so you never forget to take care of your pet. 
6. Use the Statistics page to get insights about your dog’s life
7. Share photos and messages to fellow caretakers with just a few taps.
8. Export data to share with your vet

ACTIVITIES YOU CAN LOG: 
- Food
- Water
- Treat
- Walk
- Pee
- Poop
- Sleep
- Teeth brushing
- Grooming
- Training 
- Medicine
- Custom - Anything else you want

Oldest version we support android 5.1
Icons Provided by Icons8
summary: Track your pet's walk/activity/health. Works for dogs, cats, and more
