comments: ["Have been using doglog for a couple years now, it's one of the few apps that I use every single day. I'd be lost without it. There've been a few bugs along the way but they are always responsive and fixed quickly. I especially like some of the recent changes to the events like the drop-down in Medicine to specify the type. It's a lifesaver for multi-carer packs & dogs with health issues, being able to easily create a log of everything to share with the vet is priceless.", "Fantastic app for monitoring your pet's day-to-day life. We had a cat with several health issues and DogLog allowed us to track her health and daily routine easily and effectively. As a result, we were fully prepared for vet appointments with a concise record of her progress and, in turn, the vet could provide more effective medical care for her. Highly recommend this all for any pet owner.", "I like the app as it is very useful to be able to quickly make notes about your dog that will be organised and sorted in a nice way so you can easily go back to it. However a few things could be improved. One thing is the weight curve. The X-axis should be your pet's age, not the number increment of your measurement. If you don't weigh your pet continuously you will not see the slopes of weight gain/loss as realistic in the time dimension.", "The application doesn't allow me to put in the breed of my dog from my profile. Also, all info I inserted got deleted the moment I pressed 'back'button even though I had saved it. I'm deleting this app and finding a working one!", "Great and simple way to track daily activities, as well as medications. I added my dogs exact medication by name (custom) and a few other things specific to her. I decided to get premium so I can view the usual time or day we do certain things, and it has really helped me plan out schedules. It's super easy to use and pretty inexpensive for the information you get access to.", "It's pretty good. I've been using it for about 1 yr now. No ads everywhere and I like that I can filter by event categories. Only problem I have is that I can't delete entries when clicking the delete button. Edit button works but not delete", "This seems like a fairly helpful app and I love that you can share with a pack. I need to monitor blood sugar checks, urine checks, etc. You can make the categories but I really need a graph like the temp feature. I'm using a diabetic pet specific app but it is not stable. If this app grows to that level I would likely pay as the other features seem solid.", 'Any useful analytical data is locked behind a premium fee that does not justify its cost. I can do the same stuff with a free Google form and spreadsheet', 'Perfect for keeping track of toilet routines. Can adapt new icons for other things to track. Very useful', "does exactly what I need it to: helps clear up confusion about who took the dog for a walk and when to help us avoid messy accidents and be aware of our pooch's schedule. the ONE reason this isn't 5 stars for me is the lack of dark mode because this app blinds me every night i take my dog for s walk. otherwise, perfect little simple app.", "Love the simplicity of the interface with the option to add more activities (repeating for a common task or once, like a skunk attack!). Tracking my 11 week old puppy for the past 2 weeks has been extremely helpful. I can see patterns in what times he eats, when we go outside, when he's most likely to have an accident. would be better if you could adjust the time of the event as you are entering it instead of defaulting to current time. Slow app loading screen can be frustrating.", 'Very user friendly interface. Simple to use. The free version has enough features to get started with what appears to be paid for optional extras, which appear useful but not essential. So, you can get started for free and add the extras later, which is nice. Non-intrusive ads too. It has been very useful for us where there are six people plus two dogs in our pack, as we can each log our shared responsibilities and keep track of things. Very useful app.', 'Great app, especially for pups with multiple caregivers so you\'re not constantly texting each other "did you walk the dog before you left?". Intuitive and the simple interface makes it easy to add entries with one hand while being dragged along by over-enthusiastic puppies! The most recent release addressed the only two things I didn\'t like about the app.', "The app is exactly what I look for to keep track of my pet's daily tasks. It has a simple interface that its easy to use. I can easily add more custom items according to my dog's needs. N easily edit items by pushing the task to left. I do like them to record it in current time, so i can calculate walk time, by tapping walk at the start n grooming(cleaning) at the end of the walk. I really hope the data in the app can extracted in later version so it can be presented in doctor's visit. Thanks!", 'Great app for tracking a new puppy\'s every move. So easy to track food, weight, bowel movements, training etc. I love the option to add a photo and "like" or comment on everything. Also easily customize your own buttons (for example, we added "rest" in addition to the "nap" option). Overall great app that we are using as a "pack" with other family members who also have a new puppy.', 'This app used to be perfect. All I needed it was to log food walks and bathroom breaks. However, since my initial download several months ago they have broken every aspect of this. It has gotten to the point where I literally cannot open a dog. I have downgraded to a version of the app from 2018 and have zero issues. I have been sending crash logs regularly in hopes that they fix these problems to no avail. I will be happy to fix my rating once stability is back. Edit 11/4/19: The update to 3.8.13 has certainly fixed my stability issues but it has introduced a new problem. On the previous versions that I was using, when logging something a popup overlay would appear in the center of the screen to select the dog and write any notes. However, now it shows a redesigned full screen page. While I do like the aesthetics of this new page, it now places the dog selection and finish button at the two farthest points from your hand, at the top. With a majority of phone screens exceeding 5.5 inches this makes maintaining the leash complex. A remedy for this could be rearranging the icons to be at the bottom and placing the add a photo button at the top considering that most stabilize photos with two hands making the reach less bothersome.', "This app is the perfect thing that we were looking for. You can create custom recurring events as buttons to reuse. We created ones for sleeping, napping, and crate time. It's really the perfect solution for tracking your dogs habits. Especially great for learning a new puppy's time between eating and eliminating, and bladder control. Thank you for creating this!", 'Been using this app for a year, since shortly after we adopted our first cat and love it! Pretty easy to learn how it works, no obtrusive ads, and a great system for sharing access to the whole family. The only thing that could make it better to me would be the ability to hide certain actions from the "Log Events" screen because I don\'t plan to use some of them for kitty, such as "water" and "pee".', "Update 1/17/23 - Suddenly cannot use the app; it won't open, despite uninsta/reinstall. :( Really like being able to log when she went potty, when she ate, etc - very helpwful if you have ADHD! I also track when we train, go for a walk, any health issues that concern me (e.g. scratching a lot), and when she takes meds. I do wish there were more icons or you could add your own, because I have to repeat them a lot for what I track because there are so few and a limited variety.", "Good but offline issues - If you're out of the house without the internet & switch to a different app, when it goes to reload, it won't, and then when you get back home again & connect to the internet, all the information you added when out the house disappears. Just lost all the walk, pee, poop, drink, eating, treats, vet appointment logs etc I made when I was out. It's very annoying. It could at least store information on my phone to sync up later if I'm offline. I subscribe too.", "Responsive developer. Definitely the best app available. I'm looking forward to the updates. Currently, no ability to enter time of events at initial entry. The log is confusing to read; maybe use the pet photos on the log also? Currently everything looks the same. My Swype keyboard does not work in the app. Maybe allow for a neutral note entry in the log. To keep track of weird occurrences in the pup's life.", "This app has been very helpful to us logging three animals activities between 4 caregivers.  It's simple to use.  My only issue thus far is that when I log an activity it auto-selects every pet, and I have to unselect all, then just select one pet.  I can see where this could be handy for larger packs that do things together. However, I would love the option to set a 'default' selection - I do most activities with just one pet at a time.  Having a preset, or having none selected to start, would save me a couple steps each time.", 'I really love this app. I always end up with orphaned kittens that people bring me, and I often do the record-keeping on paper. This is even smarter. There are options for potty going and feeding. I do wish there was a way to keep records about temperature and body weight and the option to have records for cats as well as dogs. Also, a widget of some of the info would be awesome, too. Over all, it mostly filled the requirement I need in a tracking app.', 'This app allows me to customize events as well as reminders in addition to other already programmed preset options for me and gives a lot of freedom in regards to how many events and reminders you can log at a single time. When I had a question, after emailing, I recieved an answer to my question within half an hour. I may have personally needed help but I would say this app is user friendly and simple to navigate. Very happy with it.', 'Needs a lot of work. Can\'t edit/delete a record once you submit it. Can\'t mark an accident. Have to manually enter the start time twice. No "now" button for the end time to use it like a stopwatch; you instead have to manually input the end time. Default units are arbitrary. (e.g. for "poop" it defaults to a quantity of "miles") Back button on my phone always takes me to the dog chooser screen instead of screen I was previously on. Lack of stopwatch functionality is a deal-breaker for me', 'Was charged for the trial of the premium version. Unsubscribed immediately. Have emailed the developer asking for the money to be refunded. Waiting for a response.', "It's such a brilliant app for keeping records of everything about you dog, especially useful if they are regularly poorly so you can easily track records.", "Easy to add events. Would be better if you could set the time when you're adding an event, instead of having to edit it afterwards. Super for multiple people, nice notification when someone else logs an event. Statistics aren't great. I'd like to be able to visualise the time of day she's going to the toilet, and also in relation to feed time. Would be nice if the information could be exported to csv.", 'It\'s not a bad app, but it\'s crashing all the time for me. I can\'t log anything - I need to try at least 3 times before I\'m able to log anything without the app crashing on me. Also I don\'t understand why they stopped showing the weight history that we had since day 1 of us getting a puppy. For a couple of weeks it started showing only the latest logged wright event, but now it says "No events" logged - it\'s very upsetting :( I have the latest version of the app, but it still doesn\'t work.', "It's good but the only downside is there doesn't seem to be an undo button would be a nice feature. EDIT - There is a way to delete! Thankyou support team that makes the app so much easier to use! 10/10! Really useful for keeping track of toilet training and I love the fact you can add other activities 👌 would absolutely reccomend this to my friends with pets particularly puppies", "Great app, but there is no way to edit the log entries. I made some mistakes and also want to switch the way I document the heats, but I cannot go back and edit the old entries. I would make new ones but then I would have the entry doubled, since I can't delete the old ones. I like the possibility of creating custom log categories.", 'Edit: Thanks for responding! I updated my rating. Looking forward to the new version :) . . . I wish you could delete events, edit events, and add more than three pets (I use it for my ferrets too). I also wish there was a "vet" option. Other than that, it serves its purpose and we\'re able to communicate when we bring her out and feed her with everyone in our household.', "This app is AMAZING. A few small QOL things, but completely offset by how helpful it is. I'm tracking so many things for my cat who has some issues I need to keep an eye on, and this is MUCH easier than notepad. But...... Huge banner ad appeared at the top of the app today. It's very obnoxious. Still very worth it, and I 100% support them getting some income for it. I donated through the link. But maybe if you're going to go the ad route, you could have a paid ad free version? Still 5*, but 🤞?", "Update: They fixed the crashing issue really fast! I love this app because its really easy to log what you need to. It has a lot of features to use. However my main reason for getting an app like this is to be able to predict what time my dog will go potty. I was hoping the app would do this for me, but you have to pay $40 a year for it! I can't spend that much a year. I get that the makers of this app need money too, but I wish they would let you buy individual features without a monthly cost.", "I really like this app so far. The only thing I'm not happy with is in the profile feed. There are some fields like breed and food brand that I would like to add for my pup, but you seem to have to select from a dropdown. Having a rescue mix, my breed is not on there and my food brand also doesn't appear in the list. I would like the option to either select Mix or Other. Otherwise a freetext input field would be much more useful.", "Though not a dog owner, this app is the best I've found so far for tracking feeding and other necessary reminders for caring for our cats. I would love to see this expanded to include other animal breeds!!! My only downfalls, again not a dog owner but a pet owner who needs to keep track of pet health, are that some of the profile details don't have the option to be written in (food, breed, etc.). Also, I would like to be able to delete some of the activities that I do not use (i.e. outdoor activities). Again, this app would be PERFECT if it included other animal types as well!", "This app has helped me so much with tracking everything my new puppy. It had made potty training so much easier! One of the best free apps I've tried!", "Exactly what we needed for our new puppy. Especially if one person is taking over responsibilities during the night, morning, work hours, etc., we can easily see what happened and when to anticipate the upcoming events.The only thing we wish we could figure out is how to share reminders with the whole pack. Right now it looks like it's only visable to the person creating the reminders, but we are using this feature to set upcoming vaccinations, etc. and want the whole pack to get the reminders.", 'Briefly, overall, it gets the job done. But important things just arent options. We play ALOT more then we walk but there is no button for, "play". Each picture needs to be really small which sucks. I take many pics that I cannot send. There\'s no place in the feed to write a simple written update. I have to send 2 long texts during the day to give a more detailed update. The caption with each activity has to be under 7ish words. I could write a lot more. Definitely could be better IMO...', "It's a nice app with a clean interface. I like being able to track things about my puppy's health. However, the biggest downside to me is that I can't seem to find a way to edit or delete log entries. I wanted to add notes to a log after I made it, but I haven't found a way to edit it and I can't delete it and recreate the log with notes. This seems like a major feature that is completely missing. No options to work around this defect as far as I can tell."]

title: Petzzing: Pet Care & Grooming
description: Ready to treat your pet like royalty? Petzzing app offers top-notch services that will have your furry friend wagging their tail with joy. Petzzing app takes the hassle out of pet parenting, offering a wide range of services from pet grooming to online vet consultations. Your pet's health and happiness is our top priority. Trust Petzzing app to provide a pet care experience that will leave an everlasting impression for you as well as your fur babies. No more dependency on “word of mouth” for finalizing the vet booking or trainers for pets because Petzzing is a one stop shop for all the pet services. It is not just any pet care app, but a pet community to help you raise your furry ones right. You can avail yourself of pet products and services such as kennels, pet daycare, dog & cat grooming, chews & treats, health supplements, etc. Features Of The Petzzing App 😸Buy pet care products and accessories: With our exciting offers and discounts "purr-ing" in, shop for them at the best price.🐶 😸Book pet boarding & day care services: Looking for a cat or a dog boarding? You need not worry about housing your pets in a safe location before going on vacation because our trusted and verified service providers offer the best of these facilities.🐶 😸Reach out to pet doctors online: Vet booking can be made easily from this app, and you may avail medical facilities at the most affordable prices.🐶 😸Looking to connect with animal lovers?: If you are one of the new pet parents, things might become confusing and challenging at times, but not if you have this app installed on your phone. Here you can raise all the "pet-uliar" questions popping up in your head in the pet community.🐶 How Can Petzzing Help You? If you advocate strongly for animal rights & adore them, then this space is the perfect hangout for you and your fur babies. New pet parents get overwhelmed at times with the new set of responsibilities, especially when it comes to dog training, cat grooming, dog care, etc. This online pet grooming app serves as a host to various other pet-related necessities. How To Get Started? It is as simple as downloading this app from the Play Store or App Store for free and signing in. You won't be able to "paws" until and unless you find the best foods, accessories, pet training, and boarding services. Additional features are: ➤You can share pet updates from your life in the pet community regarding your pets' whereabouts and also browse through the cute collection of animal pictures and videos. ➤You will no longer need to search for “ pet service near me" because this single app has all the solutions to your "pet-ty" issues. Petzzing acts like your pet care app and locates the perfect cat daycare, dog daycare, and many more online services. ➤ You can create a profile for your fur-ry friend in the app with its name, photo, age, location, and an exciting bio stating its nature, likes, and dislikes and also update its health records which can come handy at times of online vet booking. A Safe Space & Friendly Community For Pets We oppose animal cruelty like abandoning, breeding/ selling, or any illegal activity. We strive to create a pet-friendly atmosphere by making all their necessities & luxurious indulgences accessible. Users should immediately report any illegal activity they encounter on the app. Reach out to us for everything pets, such as the best pet stores, bakeries, transport & other services. Also, if you are looking for a dog trainer, cat boarding, dog grooming, etc, we have all covered in our pet care section. Reach Out To Us On Our Vibrant Social Media Channels Instagram - https://instagram.com/petzzing Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/petzzing Youtube - https://www.youtube.com/@Petzzing If you want to leave a review or ask any PET-icular questions, please write to us at support@petzzing.com As a pet parent, you no longer need to worry about pet care, Petzzing has your back!

comments: ['Needs major UI improvements and upgrade on listings. Some bugs or potential deliberate algo but is counter intuitive 1. Once u like a pet it never appears in your search again! 2. Hence there is no way you can even reach out to the parent 3. Listings arent enough. Obviously it is not humans so takes time to build DB but I still think they could do better. 4. Probably making it at least 3 4 images per pet will make it more meaningful 5. Lastly, there has to be some purpose /looking for section.', "I downloaded this app for pet matching. But honestly, I am kind of disappointed. Finding a pet for mating should have simple options and filters. It's very complications to scroll through each profile when there can easily be filters incorporated for male/female, dog/cat, city/state, age, etc.... Request to developer to kindly put filter option to make it easier and less time consuming to select options.", "Paw and body massage was not given to the pets .Both the services were included in the app. Also body shampoo and conditioner was not used.Only tick shampoo was used for both the pets . After checking for the same the groomers replied that all are included in the tick shampoo if that's the case then why shampoo and conditioner was mentioned seperately in the rate chart . Even after that also i paid the entire bill amount. Because they spent lot of time for both pets while giving services. Its", 'The initiative is good. The interface too is good but common guys if you will take so much time to update the app with a major flaw wherein you cannot place the adoption request, make the whole purpose just a purpose without some noble outcome. Looking forward to see the update and editing my review asap. Keep up the good work. Thanks. Edit: Really disappointed, no updates, no details available. Waited for more than 7days honoring the commitment of the developers. Uninstalling the app finally.', "It's the coolest app for pet parents. Stands true to its name, you can easily find your pet's companion on this app. Lots of interesting features and easy to navigate. Highly recommended.", "Superb app. Easy interface and working fast. It's very easy to use. Really great concept. Highly recommend it to all. Best I've found yet... This app is very useful to me. Thanks for the developer.", 'Very great app for pet parents and service providers to get connected with each other. The team is very freindly and making the process super simple. Most under rated and definitely deserves more.', 'App required a lot of improvements. There is no date so that one can know how old are he post is. Sometimes we keep on sending request on very old post. Also petmate app owners should continuously contact the post owner and mark the complete on the post if it is no longer required.', 'Very very helpful app fr pet lovers only problem is notification. Just need very effective notification, if anyone sms it shld just pop out. Or else very very very helpful app. 🥰👍 keep it up. PetMate', 'Yes i liked this app after the executive solved the problem , and this desreves a 4 star but im rating 3 star as there are many fake profiles in it and many people doesnt put pets for adoption but for sale . The team should look into these problems and many services are showing like 1000kms fr from me . Other than this all , its a good app , if u are a pet lover then do download this app', 'I keep my doggo son Simba with paw paradise since 1 year when we travel outside the city and have been doing the booking through petzzing app. My simba is well taken care by the boarding team. I am very happy with services of both petzzing and paw paradise. Absolutely recommend them 🤗', "Getting some irritating notifications of 'you have 3 pending requests for adoption' but unable to click them and check the requests. Poor app unable to reach the contact person.", "Finally one pet app which says and does what they say. I'm seeing positive results as soon as I've started using the app. Very user friendly too. Thank you guys for doing this. Many of us need these kinda platforms.", 'Good initiative but there are lots of improvement required in this app specially the slow data load and user experience. Edit: Revised rating is for giving frustration to load screens.', "Surprised this app works so well, runs fast, smooth and clean, syncs between myself and my wife perfectly and haven't had any issues at all", 'Keeps crashing during onboarding on the home tab itself. Edit: Got a call enquiring about this issue. Waiting for a resolution/update.', 'Everything with app is perfect, but i am not able to find a way on how I can have inbox conversations with other users on petmate, waiting for a solution', 'Excellent Service.. Looking forward to on-board my pet again.. very prompt in terms of response and communication and the services provided.', 'Best app! You must have it if you have pet or want adopt. I got my baby adopted in matter of days. It also has tinder like functionality for your pets. Love it!', 'Nice app... It does what it is supposed to do... The problem is that the owners are not replying when we send them the message. Our cat is trying to find a mate and we are doing all we can. Please help us.', "This is the app for all your pet needs under one roof be it anything . Infact there are such type of unique services which I wasn't aware of in the first place . Great . A must have for all pet lovers and pet parents .", "This app is a privacy hazard. Won't even let you open the app without personal details such as Name, Email ID and even location access. Uninstalled.", "Very slow updates for adoption listing. Most of them are like an year old listing. Owners don't reply when you message them personally.. Looks fake..", "It's an amazing experience with Petzzing they have very experienced groomer's and there customer service is also excellent. I would definitely recommend for pet parents", 'I would never imagined for such a wonderful idea of having a Pets Network, the app is super useful. Its an very good Application.', 'Smooth grooming experience everything went good there was no issue and the grooming was also done by professionals very happy with the experience', 'Nice and user friendly app. Good initiative. I gave couple of feedbacks on email to support id and received quick and good response.', "I love this app... But only one problem... It doesn't show us the date when the post was posted... Hope u will fix it", "Not a user friendly interface, my dog is Japanese spitz and you don't even have breed listed.. not even spitz .... I don't think I can use the app 😂. Or may be you have only limited dog's breed database please update..", 'Never expected such cost effective and professional services from the beginning to end. Definitely a 5 star and would recommend them to my colleagues', "Worst app don't believe them at all Don't even install the app worst app experienced in the app they confirmed my booking then they are saying the service is not available", 'First time in India have seen so much of features in app. You can add daily routin of pets feature in app. good feature', "Basically the thing is I created everything and all and it shows notifications that another dog has liked but when I go to check it doesn't show please help", 'Worst ever. Groomer was very bad gave the wrong haircut, cut my puppies sanitary area and other parts of skin. Very rough with everything.', 'The app is not upto the mark. But the good part is it gives information about the nearest pet stores and vets.', "I have a question seee I not downloaded this app but didn't open because first i want to know. We can adopt pet with out any commission? If yes then i am ready to take pet.", 'Why do you want to share our personal info with third party and deluge us with your marketing ventures. The concept of the app is very good, however there should be DND option while collecting personal data /info. Once it is achieved then this app will be the best. Respect our privacy please.', 'I just installed the app and try to update my dog profile but it was not updating and I was not able to change the details of my dog profile', 'Great experience from the start. The manager stepped me through from the moment I registered & my pet had a happy stay at Happy waggers. Great job & app experience!', 'Was very happy.']

title: Online Dating & Casual Hookup
description:
This online dating app will help people to swiftly hook up new friends and meet sweet dates. Life is short, casual dating brings color to U!

* An easy way to enjoy dating with perfect match
Tap into this online dating community gathering with like mind singles, you’ll get an instant quality match! Here you can hookup, match, chat and date with a multitude of people. It support both meaningful relationship and casual hookup dating finding. You have so many options to find a date in your city. Once you start dating here, you feel confident and happy!

*Instant hookup & chat with singles around you
If you have lost confidence in some online dating or hookup apps you once used, and now you just want to get quality matches and go on date at your own pace. This app is a choice. U can instant hookup and chat with someone. It keeps pace with the times, and the innovative, convenient and intelligent system will make matching more accurate, fast and safe. Even if you are busy at work, you can find a date online as long as you can spare a little time.

*Find friends and meet sweet love online
If U are tired of being alone and you want someone can give you hugs, love or just talk to you online one night; Or you may enjoy being single and don't need a sexual partner, but you still need like-minded friends to care for you. Or you need friends to travel with this summer, or you’re looking for a partner to build something meaningful. Or, nothing, you just want a sweet dating. Well, you’re at the right place! Swipe feature will help you fast hookup and meet potential like-minded date online. Once U date someone successfully, you will get a sense of meaning. We believe dating makes people happy!

You may have a long-term relationship with someone, but he/she doesn't always understand and support you. Don't be depressed. At some point you need a new friend to have a sweet dating with you, or just share your adult secret; Or you may be overwhelmed by a serious relationship, and you need a casual dating to help you find your true self. Or you are lonely and want to hook up a  pure fwb to get a casual dating. This casual hookup app can help you. It can match real new friends for you anytime, anywhere. So let’s enjoy fun with this Online Dating & Casual Hookup application!

It is more than a cupid for love.It's a bridge between people who crave real connections.

*What you need to know
Like plenty of dating apps, we cover more than 100 countries and encourage diverse dating styles. If you want more than just flirt someone, we recommend that you fill out your profile honestly and verify your information, which will increase your chances to get accurate and perfect matches.

We have staff verifying each profile to ensure they are authentic. If you find a fake profile, please report it immediately. We also have a strict policy against falsifying personal data. Please do not upload any inappropriate content or write inappropriate resumes. We will keep it discreet to ensure the safety. There is no need to worry your privacy and safety here. Your information including personal contact information, address, photos and secret conversations etc is secured at the hookup dating app. And, we never sell or rent your personal information to any 3rd party.

Since this is an adult dating app, each user must be at least 18 years old. You need to abide by all of this dating app’s rules and prohibit the dissemination of obscene content in the form of videos, pictures, text, etc. Otherwise, we will prohibit you from continuing to use this dating app.

title: Hinge Dating App: Meet People
description: Find a date. Delete our app. Hinge is an inclusive dating app for people who want to get off dating apps for good. That means we’re for real people like you looking to chat, meet people, date and find relationship. ◼ 3 out of 4 people on Hinge want to go on a second date ◼ #1 mobile-first dating app mentioned in the New York Times wedding section ◼ Fastest growing dating app in the US, UK, Canada, and Australia ◼ Home of viral Voice Prompts Dating is hard. We try to make it a little less-hard. ❤️‍🔥 The internet brings people and friends together, but we are here for those who want to meet people to fall in love with. Usually, digital dating puts matches before connecting, in person, where it counts. To change that, we built a dating app designed to be deleted. AKA, a dating app built to get you on actual dates with people who are more than us. 💌 We quickly learn your type and only introduce you to people we think would make a great date for you, increasing your chances to find love, not friends. 👋 Your answers to unique prompts help other people see beyond just a profile picture, making it easier to match, break the ice and start to chat and organize a date. ⭐ We get the conversation flowing - matches begin with a Like or Comment on a specific part of someone’s profile, giving the chat a smooth place to start and helps you assess chemistry. Could you be more than friends? Are they also looking for a relationship? 🔎 We actually check in to see how dates are going and follow up on how we can make better recommendations for future matches. We want you to fall in love and get off dating apps, not scroll through them forever. A dating app that is designed to be deleted 🌐 We ask about religion, politics, future plans, etc. to help you share what is important to you even before starting a chat or meet someone on a date. 🌹 Roses kickstart potential matches, chats, dates, relationships and possibly love. 🎯 Focused daily standouts help you meet the perfect match. 🔒 Our experience team is dedicated to maintaining a safe, inclusive space for online chats, offline dates, and connecting with people to fall in love with. 🎙Voice prompts give you a better sense of people’s personalities off the app before meeting them on a date. If you are tired of meeting people who only want to be friends, and want to power up your dating life, download Hinge. Our app is perfect for those ready to take a leap in the dating world. Whether you’re seeking love or to match and chat with new people, our features are designed to help you build a relationship that goes beyond just being friends. comments: ["This app is, what I saw, one of the few dating apps that might actually work and help to find the worthwhile person. Only thing are the glitches! For example, I really liked someone's profile. As I was about to type the comment, the text blinker vanished, and whatever I was writing it was showing a white empty text box. When I exited the app and launched again, that profile went away. These things are really frustrating when they happen. Please look into it.", "Disappointing. Got matches, but they disappear after some time. It seems as if Hinge deliberately unmatches people so that they stay on the app for longer time. Also unmatching feature is kept in such a way that it's extremely easy to unmatch somebody accidentally. Also photo verification doesn't work despite trying several times.", "Horrible on purpose... This app doesn't display distance or state when it shows you people. It'll just say a neighborhood or city name in the location box. That would be fine if it would show you people in your location preferences. But it doesn't. It shows you people hundreds of miles away, even if you have your preferences set to 50 miles... Because *that person doesn't have location preferences set, or has them set at 1000 miles. So get ready to Google maps each match you get. Really sucks", 'The most compatible only shows people for me that I have absolutely zero interest in. In fact the only time I "swipe right" it would seem, is on the one where I have to spend roses to like someone, so I only end up swiping right once a week. Some amazing algorithm or whatever it claims to be to tailor compatible matches. I guess they are right with their motto though, when they say its an app designed to be deleted, because of how awful it is.', "The actual platform is pretty good, like that people can put audio or video clips in their profiles. Other than that, it sucks and has become almost overrun with fake profiles! I see multiple fake profiles every day now. I was reporting them, but Hinge doesn't remove them, and I can't keep up anymore, so users beware! Also, just like every other dating app, they will send you alleged new matches right when you let your subscription expire - dont fall for it.", "Idea is great, app bugs ruin it. I get notifications of matches, but the matches don't appear unless I reinstall the app. Same with messages. The fact I had to do it once was bad enough, but it's been a repeat issue. The app itself, when it works, is the best dating app out there. It's not just a right or left swipe, and you can actually comment on things without a paid subscription. But the bugs are killing it. I want to see notifications, not be told they are there with no way to view them.", "Horrible App. You pay to see all the people that have liked you, otherwise you can only see the last person. Then, after you've matched, texted, and even met, they still show that person. You can't get to the next one until you've liked them again or X them out. Well, that's ridiculous. I'm not ready to X him out, but don't want to send a heart in the app after we've exchanged phone numbers. I asked support to fix it and they responded that it's set that way by design. So, $99 wasted.", "so far I have some glitching and for the price, I don't like having the option of selectingb things with no history or not being able to find good matches after you select them, they go into some void... that is hindering possible connections and should not be happening in an expensive dating app... I've lost 3 profiles now, no way to find them, no way to see history, very dissappointing. won't be keeping this app, it's not worth the frustration of being teased with Good potential connections", "Pros : The user interface is decent, fresh and modern, combining text, pictures and polls in a clean way. I can't fault its design practices. Cons: I have spent 3 months on Hinge X. For this price point (circa £40 a month), you still have to pay extra for Boosts and sending Roses on top (be it they don't help). However. every single contact made in 3 months (literally) has been a scammer with fake photos/details, trying to sell me Trading Shares or Crypto and are never based where they claimed.", "I don't feel like the prompts and the sending of likes is ideal for building a useful profile that will attract the right people. Almost as if the app is trying to avoid small talk...with irrelevant prompts, which ia really no better. I also don't like that I get people from far away even though I listed distance as a dealbreaker.", '"The app designed to be deleted" You got that right - great business model. Well,I opened app, all my matches were gone, reached out for support it says read a FAQ & Restart the app. Not Helpful, didn\'t work. Now no matches populate, you Swipe yes then next day it\'s the same profiles. Time to Delete. meUpdate after Update. Lose some features, double sending messages, locks up (have to restart app) but I get it.', 'Poor overall experience. All the profiles feels similar because there is a lack of details to filter and search. The messaging part of the app fails and crash each time you tab out and back of the app. It is not possible to send picture to the other person. The recent update today logged me out in the middle of a conversation, and LOCKED my account for "too many attempts to login with that phone number". My previous login attempts was 2 days ago. This should have never happened.', "I like this app because its slowed down compared to other apps. However, I am only able to get 4 likes per day with a free account, even though I set my location to a large city & have my distance to 100 miles. I'm able to receive hundreds & thousands of likes on other apps. I don't want that here due to choice overload, however, this just lets me know that they aren't showing my profile to many ppl. Paying doesn't increase the chances of being seen by more than a handful of ppl. Such a waste.", 'While this might sound pathetic, I feel I would share it as it seems odd. Every time I organise a meet with someone on the app, I receive a message form them that shows up on the notification, as soon as I select it the match disappears. I was told that I either get unmatched on purpose or accidentally. It would help to see the last message before the match disappears to see what they said', "I like how the matching system works, that you match by picking something in the user's bio/promts and attaching a message, I don't like that they can be left blank though because it feels like you get solicited into writing a first message by half the matches, who do in fact leave it blank. The app has been very buggy in the past, but it's a bit better now.", "Doesn't show as much people as would be within ones area, it just defaults to compatible and these are miles upon miles away, what's the point? I think settings for body type should be a thing. A plus is at least one can message with likes, maybe the only worthwhile dating app out there, only it's still a trickster app. Your recommended likes are never within the basic feed, so they want you to spend money on roses or deal with further away persons. What a gimmick. It's depressing actually.", 'So when I open the app and go to the section where it shows the people who have liked my profile, it shows a person and their comment before dissapearing after a second and displaying the message "no likes quite yet! " this app is buggy and frustrating to use. The motto is "designed to be deleted" but I\'m thinking it is not because you\'ll find a great match, but because the app is so frustrating and useless that it should be deleted.', "If you run out of matches, there's a Change Preferences button you can tap. Right under it is a Review Skipped Profiles button that can also be tapped. It's poorly placed and I've accidentally tapped on it twice. It should be moved somewhere else with a confirmation screen added to avoid wasting time seeing the same profiles.", 'There are so many glitches the support team continues to refuse to acknowledge. Likes are showing up & disappearing. It keeps saying there\'s no one within 4 miles of NYC over 5\'9" between 25-37 years old even tho I have barely swiped in a city of 8 million. People who messaged me are showing up a week later. I\'ve now uninstalled and reinstalled this app 6 times in the last 2 weeks just to get it to work. And they refuse to refund on top of all of this despite not being able to use the features.', "I've been trying to use the video selfie vérification feature but everytime it fails. The picture is blurry as it seems the app is compressing the file way too much before sending it to the backend service. I tried multiple times using different natural lighting and it's always the same problem. I can take high quality selfie pictures with my phone but not while using the Hinge app...", "I don't know what's happening with this app but the bugs are constant. I've uninstalled/reinstalled numerous times and I still lose messages & matches. Support doesn't help at all. There's a lot of fake profiles, I see the same pictures on numerous profiles but with different names. Please fix this app.", "Too much effort for little to no reward. The intention for the app means well but the implementation is a waste of time. There's a reason why the subscription model comes in after the app has developed a community. It worked with tinder, it worked with bumble. But there's no one on this app, and whoever is on it is getting absolutely harassed with upgrading to a payment model. Might aswell go out to the bar and waste your money there.", 'Still not a fan of the swyping style of browsing. I prefer to scroll through all the profiles before selecting someone to message. I think the swiping method is supposed to be more addictive. I just find it frustrating being forced to make a decision on every profile the first time I see it.', "As an asexual, this app wasn't very helpful. I really liked that I could list Asexual as my sexuality (there were a lot of choices which was great!). But you can't filter on that sexuality when looking through profiles, even when you pay for the app. It makes Hinge useless for asexuals and anyone looking for a specific relationship. If that was fixed, I would say this would be a good dating app as far as not getting a lot of useless matches of people who don't read your profile.", 'The program is completely inefficient, until you pay for using the program, you will receive messages from women but you cannot see them, now when you have paid to open the messages, no one will answer you and send you messages. This is a scam, I only recharged my account for one month, but they withdrew money from my account again without my permission and knowledge. The cost of the program is very expensive', 'I constantly get a pop-up saying "Billing Error" and literally nothing else. No indication of what actually went wrong or what I could do to fix it. A Google search brings up results suggesting my number or Play Store account might be shadowbanned, but I\'ve never touched the app before this week so IDK how that would be. Weird for a dating app to not want to take my money. Most have the opposite problem. Oh well. 🤷\u200d♂️', "The least predatory of the dating apps. The layout and UX are much nicer than other apps, too. Somehow the userbase on Hinge is...less trashy, for lack of a better term. Fewer bots, less porn, not many cartoons, fewer junkies, and far fewer morbidly obese people. I actually go out with some peope from Hinge, and have deleted almost all the other apps. 2/5 stars because filtering is EXTREMELY limited without a paid subscription. You can pick gender, age, and distance - and that's it.", "The dating app meant to be deleted BECAUSE ITS CONFUSING AF!! This is not exactly the most user-friendly app. Most dating apps have a swipe left swipe right or perhaps even a button to push to like the entire profile but to my understanding this app you like individual things on a profile? It's clear how to say no cuz there's a giant actually corner but there's really not a clear way to say yes to the whole profile", "The app itself is okay.. better than your average swiping dating app. Although, with the people it attracts it's all pointless anyway. I've matched probably dozens of women at this point and it would not be exaggerating to say more than 95% of matches, people that apparently were interested in me, lead to absolutely no where and lucky to even get a reply from them.", "Matches and recommendations are pretty good, it really gets to know your type. However the app is super buggy rn. I'm on Android 12 and it constantly hangs, crashes and clears mid-typed messages. If it worked well enough to use without constant annoyance this would be a 5 star", 'App can be buggy, and the two-tiered subscription service means people who pay more get promoted excessively. Some people are put behind a pay wall, and I usually see all those people on Bumble anyway, so the paid features are high cost and low benefit. I find Bumble much more egalitarian overall.', 'The app is made to uninstall it faster, yes it is. First, it "checks" what kind of people you are attracted to, and then selects exactly the opposite ones, and then it will show a notification that there are no more people nearby. But, if you go to a place where "you can give roses", then there will be 100,500 people in your area. Magic', "It's okay, but its main goal seems to be getting you to buy a membership and stay on the platform rather than meet someone and delete the app despite the ads claiming otherwise. The quality of people I met from the app seem to be a lot higher than other dating apps though so it's not too bad", 'the absolute worst dating app I\'ve used. you can\'t do a thing as a man without premium features. I also don\'t think my premium account is being advertised at all either - forcing me to pay yet again for boosts. "how do you know its not just a bad profile? " - because the exact same profile has matches on Tinder and bumble. Don\'t waste your money.', 'Nice and buggy. You write up half a message to someone then turn your phone screen off to tend to another task. When you unlock your phone to finish typing the message the message is gone and the person is thrown back into the mix. You then have to swipe another 100 people to see them.', 'I was logged out and now I am unable to login from my number. Everytime I try login it says there is an error as there are too many attempts to login from the given number. The support team is unable to answer me and has not given me a proper reply but just auto generated replies. This seems like a total scam as I have already paid for the premium services.', 'UI is nice and I like the thought behind only being able to "like" a specific part of a person\'s profile. It has some massive bugs that even after talking to support about it I\'ve gotten no response and they haven\'t responded since saying "we\'ll get back to you soon." Edit: taken down a star because it\'s been over a month and a half and I still haven\'t heard back from them on my email. One of the bugs seems to have been fixed but the other hasn\'t.', 'The free experience is alright, but the paid version has issues. One of the biggest draws is that people you pass on or even liked are often recycled into the "standouts," aka the pay-walled daily selections that shouldn\'t contain people that I have said no to or people who said no to me previously. The prompts are also dreadfully dull, promoting simple answers that make most people sound the same. While this keeps things tame, it\'s also very boring to read through.', "Hinge was probably one of the better apps, making you actually put effort into swiping someone and give you lots of personality in your profile. Since I've been back on it, I just don't seem to get any matches and it repeats the same people constantly.", "Ton of scammer profiles & Hinge doesn't get rid of them when you report. Note: the profiles always have less than the required 6 photos. Also, one day all my likes randomly disappeared & messages would say send but then when reopen app they were gone. Contacted customer support who replied they would escalate the issue. Never heard back. Had to delete app. RIP guy I had been talking to for 3rd days. It wasn't you, it's Hinges' devs. :("]

title: Google Meet
description:
Google Duo has been upgraded to Google Meet. Now you can securely connect, collaborate, and celebrate with the highest-quality video calling, all in one app.

The updated Google Meet app allows you to easily and instantly video call your family and friends or schedule a meeting in advance. Connect with anyone, anywhere across mobile, iOS, Android, web, tablet, and smart devices*.

Features you can look forward to:

Host video calls and meetings, all in one place
Bring everyone who matters most together with group calling or set up your next brainstorm meeting for up to 100 people.

Access on any device
Works across mobile Android, iOS,  tablet, web or smart devices* so everyone can join.

Enjoy high-quality audio and video
Low-light mode and noise cancellation allow everyone to be seen and heard, clearly.

Play with backgrounds and visual effects
Filters, AR masks, effects, family mode and backgrounds make connecting even more fun.

Share content
Present documents, slides, and more during your conference call. Live sharing allows everyone in the meeting to interact with the content being shared, creating a collaborative experience, not just a one-way presentation. You can cowatch YouTube, curate a playlist together, or take turns playing a game.

Follow along
Google speech-to-text technology transcribes your content with real-time captions**, so you won’t miss a detail.

Meet and chat safely
Video meetings are encrypted in transit and our array of safety measures are continuously updated for added protection.

Anyone can join a meeting on Meet via an invitation. However, some capabilities are available only to Google Workspace customers. Learn more about Google Meet:
https://workspace.google.com/products/meet/

Follow us for more:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/googleworkspace
Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/googleworkspace
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/googleworkspace/

*Works on Android TV devices with Android 8.0 or higher. If your Android TV does not have a built-in camera, you will need to connect a USB camera and microphone to your Android TV device.
**Not available in every language.

Data charges may apply. Check your carrier for details.
Specific feature availability may vary based on device specifications.
summary: High quality video calling for Android & iOS phones, tablets, Google Nest & web.

comments: ["I love it. Better than WhatsApp in video quality and audio clarity. Then there are numerous features which depends on how one would want to use it. Overall very satisfied. Not sure if all devices are supported. I had trouble making video calls from my Samsung device as the other person didn't receive my call. The other person was using a Pixel device, that keratin made a video call that i was able to receive and connect.", "It's a very good app, particularly for online meetings and classes. There's one problem with the app that it doesn't work properly with blue tooth speaker, the sound quality and volume, both are not very good with blue tooth speaker. This limits it's usage particularly for classes that require kinesthetic movements like dance, exercise and yoga. Can you please fix this problem?", "I just don't understand why my audio all of a sudden has stopped working after updating google meet. Kindly look into this issue as it's getting frustrating for me to access the meeting facilities properly. I had informed it earlier but no reponse yet received. I have to reboot my system every single time for resolving this technical issues. It's seriously frustrating! Kindly resolve this issue as soon as possible. Thank you.", "Good call quality. Biggest problem is when I call my home devices, it would not give me options to show myself or not. Always makes calls as a video calls. Sometimes I just want phone calls, not a video calls. Another is that u just can't make calls to any number. It has to be a registered number in the Google meet. These two need big improvements. They always make things very complicated w most of their products", "It works really good on full bars for Internet. However, when I get down to 3 bars it glitches then 2 bars it freezes video. Then I loose sound on the last bar. I think it should work better when it shows I do still have Internet at all. Haven't figured out how to send text messages. It hasn't worked for me, yet. Other than that I like MEET. 👍", 'This app was my go-to for video calls for a long time, but the last week or so, it keeps giving me "unexpected error" and "problem starting call". I looked up ways to correct it, which included clearing the cache, clearing app data, and reinstalling the app. It will work for the first call, and then mess up again every single time I do the bug-fixes. Hopefully, there is a way to permanently correct this or some kind of patch update.', "I am very pleased with this video app, although I hope you can get a higher definition of quality for the video picture on both ends of the screen. Also, the more special effects, filters, backgrounds, and extras are so much fun and useful in a lot of different ways. Keep up the awesome upgrades! Can't wait for the next new surprises to come ♡♡", "My partner and I are long distance and have a tendency to go to sleep on call. Despite the fact that we both have full wifi, there have been several occasions where we wake up and the call has ended. Neither of us ended the call, neither of our phones updated, and neither of our apps needed to be updated. Besides that the quality of the calls can be extremely inconsistent, fine one second, grainy, hard to see or hear to frozen video another second. It's inconsistent and just bad.", 'It\'s ok for a video chat app. Main problem is that there isn\'t a button to use the phone speaker. Only Bluetooth on/off, so sound comes out of the phones earpiece only and I can barely hear the other person. The filters are fun, but there\'s just not a lot of what I think are "useful" features. Sometimes I use the children\'s coloring feature as a whiteboard. There\'s no like chat or share features, but not too hard to swap over to text for that. Just an ok app at best, beside that one major issue.', "This has been the most glitchy app I have ever used. I wouldn't expect that coming from Google. If there is a dip in service and it drops the call, I have to restart my phone and not just the app. Half the time, it doesn't hang up and it keeps the call connected while not allowing other calls to come in. My phone is super hot any time I use it. Do better Google", "It was really nice to be able to call with my freinds and family with a face to face experience. I personally have an android so it is one of the only ways I can see freinds and family. The filters and the settings were a bit slow and sometimes didn't load at all, which is a minor issue. Overall, a really good idea, the execution needs some minor adjustments but nothing that won't stop you from conversing woth others.", "When recording videos, now meet automatically lowers the volume of apps that are open. I try recording videos while YouTube music played in the background and it automatically lowers the volume. Also, when this was duo, we were able to zoom in while recording videos and we can no longer do that. Please give us the option to enable these 2 features. I'm in the car audio community so letting my volume while I'm recording videos is really annoying.", "It's a nice app. You can exit out of the app without it kicking you out of the call and there's a share screen option which is nice. But sometimes the audio is pretty bad. Like, I was on a call with my friend and when she said something, a constant beeping sound would play. It was really annoying. And I wish you were able to mute people. Sometimes I'm in big group calls and it's hard to hear others when everyone else was talking.", "The app interface is simple and good looking. I'll be at. I wish the buttons were material you themed also this is the only app I have any issues with the white balance. Quite often the camera blows out and I look like Voldemort and considering this is the only app that does it, it's clearly an issue with the software other than those gripes it's a great app", "It works fine most of the time but sometimes it freezes so much. Even if both users of the call are on full wifi and everything it will glitch and freeze really bad. For long distance relationships and stuff this is a huge inconvenience. It has a lot of trouble connecting sometimes and it won't always show when someone is calling me. These major issues that make the app almost useless sometimes need to be fixed as soon as possible.", 'Updated review: Meet has made some improvements since my last review. Any improvement is welcomed. That said some very basic functions are still missing. Receiving pictures can be difficult if you want to save or copy them. Being able to send or receive notes and or pictures while on an active meet voice call is also missing. Sharing usable hyperlinks is also missing. These simple functions are why nearly all of my colleagues have left the platform. The platform has a lot of potential.', "BEWARE! DON'T DOWNLOAD. It came preloaded on my Samsung S2don't want this app! I can't delete it. When I change the auto-uprate feature in the GooglePlay store to off, it automatically changes it back to allow auto-updates. Can't change permissions/unwarranted authority over my phone in settings. Uses data/wifi/storage/battery. Once it's there, you'll never be able to get rid of it. 0 stars if I could.", "I've been able to use Meet for audio calls using my Google Mini, Google Nest Display (w/o camera), and video calls using a couple of my phones. I've been able to share photos while in video calls without having to send a separate text message, and the sound has been good I was shocked that the Assistant heard me from a different room than it was in to make a call for me. I am having a problem getting it to connect to my TVs. I'm not sure if available on my Windows 11 laptop yet, but hope so", 'When it was Duo, everything was great. Now I have problems with the volume as it only lowers to a certain point that is still to loud. Also, the brightness does not adjust like it used to. It used to adjust in full darkness for me and the person I was calling. Now it just plunges us into the abyss without any adjustment. I cannot figure out how to fix these after going through absolutely everything.', "I don't know what happened in the last couple of months but I can no longer make calls in this app because I can't verify my phone number. I have tried every step on the help page (force stop, uninstall and reinstall, update phone, restart) multiple times but still nothing. The only thing I use it for is video calls so it's now useless to me.", "I liked duo because it did what I needed. Some of us use Android and some of us use iphone. For the most part it works except when it doesn't, but I think it more my connection. The other thing I don't like is that I cannot change the sound to let me know someone is calling. I barely hear it and miss calls because of that. I try to report the problem but never know if anyone gets it and I NEVER get a response. Gabi", "Hasn't worked since the update. I use this app frequently, and it's tuning into an inconvenience. I go in the app, dial the call, and it just beeps. I was able to answer once, but it never actually opened the call. I have cleared all caches, deleted and reinstalled the app, restarted my phone, nothing.", "I couldn't get any of the calls to connect for over a year. I don't know what happened when it changed from Duo to Meet but that was the last time I used it until now 8/8/23. I erased it and reinstalled it multiple times but still wouldn't work. I had to resort to Facebook Messenger which always worked but the quality of the video calls were hit or miss. I tried Meet today and it worked and was clear. I just hope that it continues to work like it did today, because I prefer it over any other app", 'There should be an option for users to change ring tones and notification tones. Besides the ringing not being loud, I need to know which app a call is coming from. By changing the ringtone, I mean having the ability to customize the ringtone with music of my choice. Additionally, when a contact number is opened in the default phone caller, only the video call option is available. There should also be a direct voice option available for contacts saved in the default phone book.', "So much better than facetime! We live in the country and have poor internet service. This uses bandwidth much better than FT. Almost no buffering ever when FT won't connect from the same locations. But this app used to be much easier to use when it was DUO. I try to get people to use it but the I vacation set up and first call is seems VERY challenging for people to do. I wonder why Google improved it so badly?!!!", "Update: it still is not any better. I did send feedback through the three little dots on meet app. I'm having problems with the picture being fuzzy freezing up. echos when I talk and they are unable to understand me or me them. Can you please look at that. I love the way the app was before. And since we do a lot of face-to-face talking through this app it's really a bummer.", 'The setting for disabling noise cancellation keeps appearing and dissappearing for me. I am so distressed because of this. This is making me drop out of music classes 🥺 Edit 1: I dont see an option of update on play store. So, I am on latest version. I have tried removing cache and storage after stopping the app, and then uninstalling it and installing it afresh. Still dont see a section of audio settings (under which noise cancellation option appears) under my settings.', 'Video constantly switches from wifi to data because of weak signal, but signal is actually strong at 450Mbps. I have to turn my phone to airplane mode to use it. If I start the call on Bluetooth and switch off my headphones the volume is very low and I need to restart the call. Recently there also is an audio delay so conversations are difficult. The app has been unusable because of these things. Previous versions worked fine. This has only been the past few updates.', "Google Duo(Meet),is very clear,with excellent sound quality.It even has evolved better than expected.We use it for family communications,it's certainly very trustworthy,and the simplicity is superb. The support team is also very involved in improvements.5 stars for this App is deserving, against fierce competition, thank you.", "I had to edit my review: For weeks now, I have had constant interruptions during video calls. The person I am talking to can no longer see me and I receive a message that my camera is not available. In addition, the call notification is very unreliable, sometimes even the notification about a missed call is missing. I use the Pixel 7 Pro, so I am particularly irritated by the app's lack of interaction with the phone. In the meantime, I have switched to WhatsApp in frustration.", "With so many folks caught up in the rat race I think this app is pointless for the most part. There's too many other platforms (usually preloaded on one's device) for use in business and personal affairs. I agree, it's nice to be able to sync a virtual meeting with my email and what not, but sometimes feel overwhelmed with all the Google apps where so much of our personal information is shared.", "Disappointed 😞! While in a meet, the notification that's showing join and left makes it difficult to exit full screen. And I have waited for half an hour to exit the full screen. After that I found about the long press . So for a newcomer it's so difficult. and it would be a great if you guys can rectify this issue..", "Great app. I can stay in touch with my hubby with video when he is out of town working. Thanks Duo. I changed my rating for meet because it keeps shutting down. Get video for one second then disappears. Will not stay on, on my Samsung. Can't Uninstall and reinstall. Updated and still doesn't work. Help", 'This being Google I am very disappointed especially when on some devices it is the built-in video calling app used and can\'t be uninstalled. Zoom or similar better performing apps should be studied for "Meet" improvements. Samsung uses this built-in app for communication instead of their original which was much better in all ways. Since this is a built-in Com App, it may be time Google put this app on top of the list for super impressive improvements.', "Sometimes the call will have really bad audio but it's fixed whenever you hang up and call again. Otherwise the app works pretty well. I'm not sure where to put a feature request, but I would like to request a way to lock the screen so that my toddler can't swipe away from the call while he's holding the phone talking to people. Edit: thanks Google for the response. I have a Pixel 7.", "Another absolutely trash phone application for googles own operating system. You cannot minimize yourself at all. I have a folding phone and my own face takes up half the screen when I fold the phone to get a good angle. It's still very bad design and must be intended for narcissists that can't deal with not seeing themselves.", "It works as well as any other video call app. I don't like the video pre-call screen though. It shows your selfie camera full screen in the background and it looks like I'm already in an active video call or that I'm leaving a video-mail message. I would like it if I could easily distinguish my call status. A flashing red dot or red scrolling/flashing marquee banner across the top of the screen clearly stating the call status, either that you're in a call or that it's ready to make a call. 🎭🎫", "It is great for video calls and I use it daily. However, there's a forced after-call screen that pops up once I end a call that I made which is extremely annoying. I am quickly moving on to an important notification which made me end the call but I have to see the screen again and then go back to my notification which is the last thing I need in emergencies.", '7/5/2023-I have done all the steps that were mentioned & the app is still not working like it was when myself & 2 additional people are on Meet. The sound is terrible & the picture freezes. I do not have this issue when it is myself & 1 other person. Any other suggestions? Just updated app, can communicate clearly w/ 1 person. However, when trying to connect w/2 people, they can not hear me, and I can not hear them. I can only see them. The app worked fine prior to this last update. Please fix.', "Terrible quality calls. Doesn't know how to register a Bluetooth signal. Randomly dropped calls. Vibrations that don't end even after picking up the call and closing the app. All around a pretty terrible app experience, and genuinely makes me consider buying apple just so I dont have to deal with this."]

title: Old Friends Dog Game
description:
Welcome to Old Friends Dog Game, where love never grows old! Create your own dog sanctuary in this heartwarming pet rescue simulator. Rescue adorable senior dogs and uncover their life story as you shower them with love. Decorate with cute doggy decor, bake scrumptious dog snacks, and experience the joy of helping cute senior dogs live out their golden years in the best way possible. 

Inspired by the real life pet residents at Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary, these cute dogs have heartwarming stories and personalities that you'll uncover as you rescue them and provide the care they need to live their best dog life!

Awarded Gold winner at the 2022 NYX Awards, a finalist for Pocket Gamer's Game of the Year, and a Webby honoree for Social Impact in Games, this cute dog simulator is a must-play!

Gameplay:

❤️ Meet the town residents and rescue cute senior dogs. Help them live their best life by fulfilling their needs and ensuring their happiness. As you feed, pet, and play with your dogs, their love and loyalty grows.

📘 Choose how the story unfolds. In this dog simulator, you pick the path for each dog's story! Unlock multiple chapters for every cute doggy you rescue.

💒 Customize your dog sanctuary and make it a haven for your dogs. Decorate indoors and outdoors with cute doggy decor that will make your dogs feel right at home!

🧁 Bake lip-smacking treats for your beloved dogs, ensuring they never go hungry.

🧣 Dress up your dogs in cute pet outfits! Each dog has adorable accessories that you can earn.

🐕 Give your dog sanctuary the personal touch - feature a custom profile, a unique avatar, and a gallery of cute photos of each dog!

**********

Old Friends Dog Game is developed and published by Runaway.

This game is free to play but does contain some items available to purchase for real money. If you run into any issues while playing or you have any suggestions, please reach out to us at support@runaway.zendesk.com. OLD FRIENDS DOG SANCTUARY™ is made by Runaway Play.
summary: Save cute dogs and help them enjoy life in this pet rescue simulator!
