comments: ["Absolutely loving the game so far! I'm relieved it's not another match 3 or merge 2 games, and really is about taking care of old dogs and managing the sanctuary. I've seen the game's advert for a long time, I regret not playing it sooner. But better now than never I guess! Only thing is the game keeps crashing on me occasionally while loading a new scene (ex; getting a new dog, loading livestream, .etc) I love the game and I want to support the funding, I'd appreciate a smoother experience. :')", "I played the game a while ago and recently reinstalled it, but now it won't even let me past level one. Everytime I try to stream it just makes the screen go black, and nothing happens. I've tried everything to fix it, reinstalling again, restarting my phone, even went online to try and find an answer. Love the game, just wish I could get further with it.", "I absolutely love this game! It's adorable, and I haven't experienced any bugs (I have played for about a month now). Though, for the Dog Blog, there are limited color options, which, as someone with bright green hair, is a little saddening :( Aside from my dramatics about hair color, I recommend everyone give this game a try! It's so customized, and each dog has their own favorite treats and toys, which is so fun to memorize. I love this game!!", "This game is really amazing and I love the style so much! I really like the game because it's supporting a real life senior dog sanctuary too! But last 3 or 4 days I couldn't get in the game because i got a message about some kind of error and I tried everything to get rid of it but it hasn't been working so far. I got pretty good progress there so it's going to be sad if i lose it. I don't know if its a game error or its like that for someone too but I hope it gets fixed soon!", "Very Cute very relaxing it's really wholesome too! But, I've been having issues lately When I stream the screen becomes black and the music keeps playing and I can't go to the next level because my first time of streaming is glitching I've been having Issues with that so whatever you could do please Fix it....", "First things first, this is not a game you will play for an hour straight. More like a few minutes at a time. Gameplay is fun though. Little thing I mentioned pre-edit, So basically my progress reset, (It has been fixed now.) Devs should probably look into what caused that. Also I don't know if the message I sent to tell them it was fixed worked? All in all, great game, great devs. (What caused the game to reset though?)", "A awesome friendly game where you get to experience adventures and journey with these adorable dogs and the amazing artwork! I love this game. It's just heartwarming. And there is so much more potential to expand apon! The fact that it was based on real dogs and experiences is also amazing. You get to read snippets of real-world inspiration the further you progress.", "This is THE BEST chill/idle kind of game I've ever played. There's so much to do! You are always getting rewards constantly, even past the early game. There are only ads very rarely, when you want to increase your rewards. The dogs are so sweet and have personality that you uncover through their individual story lines. You'll fall in love. I had this game ages ago and left it like I always do with mobile games (I'm fickle lol) and this is the ONLY game I missed so much I had to come back again!", "This game is fun but I got stuck on the streaming stage Everytime I tried the screen would go black to the point I just left and rejoin the game and when I kept trying it took my stuff but never worked if u could see if it's a bug please update Soo it doesn't happen to other people", "it was almost an amazing game, except for the fact that it was lacking in furniture and decoration aspects. it's fun caring for the dogs, but i wish i could put more furnitures. there's so many furniture blueprints, but i cant craft becuz the materials for good furnitures are so hard to get. i wish we could buy materials from donations, or we could get from streams. idk. im quite unsatisfied witht the reward rn", "This make me cry so much. I love idle games. I love that this is based off an actual doggy sanctuary with the actual doggies and with pictures of the actual doggies attached. I'm sad and happy and my heart melt. Some lags and bugs are experienced and the game crashes too. But i just love the concept of this game. Good strategy to make ppl adopt senior dogs and cry cause they're gone too soon", "It's really great especially for dog lovers! I Love it a lot and especially that it's also a real sanctuary.. It really makes me wanna donate now :( but my parents do not allow me sadly... I hope some people will still donate :) definitely will recommend some friends to play this..!", "Old friends dog adventure is such a fun game where you care for older dogs and play the challenges! You get to choose what to say and there's even a dog blog! Definitely would recommend.", 'Sancuaty names could be more customizable(wanted to name mine after my old pup, Timber.) But otherwise, The game is amazing. The graphics are great. The dogs are adorable. And I love the hat for Mack.', 'Absolutely what I was looking for in a game, perfect with little to no ads and with very reasonable microtransactions! Would recommend', "Very cute! I would love if the game would emphasize the importance of identifying dog-friendly costumes that won't bother dogs vs coatumes that will make them uncomfortable all day, but overall its super fun 👍", "THIS GAME IS THE ACTUAL BEST! BAGEL IS SO CUTE MACK IS SO CUTE AND LEO IS SO CUTE,there's so many things to do!Decorate your sanctuary,collect new dogs,and it's all so much fun I love the theme and design of the game and how they're based on real life senior dogs!I wish I could meet them in real life!I was quite sad when I found out they only sold the merchandise in USD cuz I'm from the UK but seriously if I could I'd give this game a million bigillion stars out of a million biggilion stars!☆", "I am only on 3rd level, and I think it is really fun, cute, and great for a dog lover. I do find it a bit repetitive, but that will probably change over time. I olso do think Runaway's other games are really good too. If you delete their games, your progress will not be saved, though.", 'This game is so cute and entertaining! The dogs are adorable. Even the situations where almost nothing is going on it is really fun. Just baking food or cleaning the house just makes you feel happy and calm. I love this game and I really recommend this game for all dog lovers! ❤️', "It's such a cute game about dogs and don't love a dog for its age love it forever no matter what because old dogs are cute too and in the game you can unlock cute dogs like mack and bagel and Leo there so adorable doesn't matter how old a dog is love lasts for eternity I love Leo Babs and Captain Ron too runaway pls update maybe fix the bugs? Not asking for much ty the bug is it takes a bit to load and sometimes when I try saving a picture it says contact support game kicks me out any way to fix", 'I feel good playing with old friends, . I recently had to start a new game over because old friends got accidentally erased , I was devastated. Old friends helps me cope with losing my old friend scrappy. He was my everything, he passed away not long ago he was 16 and so loved. Thank you old friends for reaching out and I was very excited to hear from you. Thank you old friends.', 'This Is such a heartwarming game, I love how simple are the interactions with the dogs. I love the little stories that they include of the dogs adapting to their new home. Amazing game!', 'This game is just so adorable, and the fact that it is based on real life dogs just makes it 10 times more interesting and unique! Love it, keep up the great work. ( I also totally recommend!)', 'This game is adorable and I love the concept of it. It is so cute and so fun, and i love that the dogs each have the personalities of the real pups. And favorite treats and toys. Babs is my favorite pupbso far hehe Ten stars from me!', 'Ohh, they have fixed the problem, the game is really wonderful, and very innovative, please I recommend you download it and give it a try', "So far, it's a really fun game! However I wish furniture was cheaper and there were more coupon codes. But overall, it's really good!", 'I love this game but my account got restarted and when i just wanted to play i was in the start again i dont know to get my stuff and my progress back please help i dont wanna start again.I still have the furniture that is needed coupons. But the ones i crafted is gone and the progress of the dogs are gone and i only have mack again', 'Edit: After 2 years of playing this game, it has become quite dull. The events are all repeats from the years prior... I already have all the rewards from the bake-offs, so why even participate? I have been at the max level for probably a year now. Not much to do after completing the stories. I have 3 senior rescues myself (2 dogs and 1 cat), so this game is perfect for me. I recently applied to vet school and want to focus on old animals. This game is everything I want out of life!!!', 'One of the first times a mobile game has truly felt like a game. Love oozes from every millimeter of this experience. Even the ads are non-intrusive, and from what I understand completely optional. Highly recommend!', 'Game has reset on me twice, erasing all my progress. The first time I used recover to get back to my original game. The second time it reset, I tried to recover my original game, but only the two previous reset games appear, making me start with zero progress. If this is not fixed, I will never play this again.', "Super cute and makes me feel better about playing mind-numbing games that get me nowhere. The only complaint I have is that the app randomly restarts sometimes after an ad video. Also, videos have been unavailable for me all day so I can't get Mack his chicken flavoring 🥹", "Love the premise behind the game and was enjoying playing it. The dog message requests bugged out with no images and did nothing when I clicked on them so I rebooted the game and it lost all my data :( I'm scared it will happen again.", 'This game is so much fun, and although you have to work very hard, the dogs are soo cute. Most relaxing game ever!', "It is amazing there's lots of adventures the dogs are so cute but the best thing is getting more of the dog's stories.", "This is a cute game and I enjoy it but I can't progress past the streaming part as the screen just goes black.", 'So far this is super cute and fun. a little bit slow, but really heartwarming and relaxing.', "Cute little game. I haven't closed it since download because I'm mildly afraid of missing things when my attention differs, but that's the only issue and isn't even really one! The whole app is so fun and adorable that I can't keep my hands off of it 🙈", "I don't know why it's taken me so many years to download a wholesome game about dogs. So far into the game, it's easy to follow, lovely story and beautiful graphics. If you love dogs and want causal gameplay, this should suit you:)", "Love this game; it's so nice and wholesome! There has been issues with my progress resetting, but whenever that happens I breeze through the intro sequence then contact support through the game's settings, and they fix it in like a day. One thing I really wish the game had though is the ability to replay cutscenes, because the stories are just really cute.", 'Amazing game 10/10 never run iut of things to do, great asthetics, you just get to chill with good puppers, no annoying ads without consent and great atmosphere, highly recommend']

title: happn – Dating app
description:
Happn - The dating app that lets you find the people destiny has decided you should meet. 

With over 100 million members, happn is the best way to meet people in your area. We’re the only dating app that’s based on real-world interactions.
You only see people you’ve crossed paths with in real life or that you have common interests with, so you know you’re already in each other’s lives or the magic will happen. Have you ever wondered if the person you smiled at on the train was interested in you? With happn, you’ll never have to wonder again! 


TRUE AND SAFE DATING EXPERIENCES:

* Your exact location is never revealed.
* You keep control of what is displayed on your profile
* You don’t have to worry about rejection: the person will never know you like them unless they Like you back and Crush
* You decide who you talk with: only after Crushing, can you send/receive a message
* You can tell when you’re ready to date through our special feature in the chat to avoid the pressure of asking
* You can always change your mind at any time: happn is consent-driven


HOW DOES IT WORK

It’s simple. When you cross paths with another happn user, their profile will appear on your app. Did someone catch your eye? Like them secretly. We promise that the person will never know unless they Like you back: and it’s a Crush! You can then start chatting, see if there’s a spark, and maybe arrange to meet up. (modifié) 


CRUSH WITH CONFIDENCE AND SAFETY

The happn app is based on the principle of reciprocity: you will never have a conversation with someone you’re not interested in.
At happn, confidentiality is our priority: your location is never visible to other members, only the places you crossed paths with them are shown and you can deactivate if you don’t feel comfortable with it.


MEET WHEN YOU’RE READY

Never sure when you should ask your Crush on a date? Afraid they might say no? Or are you sick of the pressure when someone asks you out too soon? No more stress. Now you can tell us when you’re ready to meet, directly in your chat with your Crush. We’ll let you know when they’re ready too.


ACCESS TO MORE FEATURES?

The happn app is free to download and use. If you would like access to more features, you can switch to Premium by purchasing a subscription. With Premium, you get access to the list of people who have Liked your profile and you can send SuperCrushes to your favorite profiles so you’re sure to stand out. So what are you waiting for?
Download happn now and start your journey to something real, you might find your soulmate.

https://www.happn.com/en/trust/
https://www.happn.com/en/privacy-basics/

comments: ["It used to be good in the beginning. but now it's ruined. there are a lot of people not even uploading their pictures just some random quotes or any wallpapers are being uploaded on people's profiles. it shouldn't be allowed. and there used to be accurate results of ppl we cross paths with and i found people with that feature. but now it's random location based users showing. which is not worth it. hope you go back to old features.", "There should be option to filter out distance in preferences. I don't want to match with anyone too far.Secondly there is a bug, when you open and scroll blocked users , suddenly app will go backwards and check the preference for Men as well.When it was not checked in the first place. It is annoying to say the least. Third, it would automatically enable Invisible mode sometimes.", 'The UI is pretty bad. Until the latest update, the accept/reject buttons moved around on the screen, but now this is fixed. Unfortunately, they now moved the "children" attribute into obscurity, so that we have to scroll down to the list of attributes, and then scroll right, for every profile. Such important information shouldn\'t be hidden away.', "Changing the list of personality traits on profiles from a static, easy to read list, to a slider with half the traits hidden by default, is a great way to chase people away from your app. It makes it way too finicky to see if someone is compatible at a quick glance. Also, stop spamming we with notifications of new messages, when it's just messages from the platform on why I should get a subscription. - edit: thanks so much for the impersonal, bogstandard response.", "Ever since using this app since December, it has always been buggy and glitchy. No notifications for messages, since the new update unable to move my pictures on my profile. When chatting with someone the text box doesn't go up with the keyboard so you have no clue what you are typing, only if you click away your keyboard. When you want to buy premium, you can't, it will spit out a useless error message.", 'Notifications still not coming through at all, so I have to actually open the app every time to see if there\'s been a match or any message. The new "add a place" feature needs quite a bit of work; it\'s poorly implemented. The list of places to add seems entirely random and very limited. Why can\'t we just search for places and add them ourselves? Also for some, such as bars/restaurants, only the name of the place is given, no location, so it\'s impossible to tell which exact place it actually is.', "It's broken. It's a great concept, but it doesn't seem to be functioning properly. I signed up in a very quiet neighbourhood, and it immediately showed two people I supposedly crossed paths with. I have since went to multiple festivals, and it hasn't shown me crossing paths with anyone at these locations. It barely shows anyone on my map, even after venturing to busier areas multiple times.", 'Likes hardly result in matches. Sometimes they disappear without a reason given. The whole cross each others path and then like - like the add describes. Is not always the case. Sometimes you only get people from further away.', 'Installed it in the hopes of it having a better algorithm than Tinder. Unfortunately that isn\'t true Haven\'t had a single like in months and when I use the boost I sometimes get a few likes. When I unmatched some old matches I suddenly got "new" likes. Turns out its just the people I unmatched. Only reason it gets 2 stars is because the boosts lasts way longer than on tinder (24h vs 30 minutes) but it wil be ~€9 each. The premium fee is ridiculously expensive, sitting close to €30 a month.', "The latest update left me a bit disappointed actually. Wasn't really expecting this kind of layout and colours especially as I have been picturing it in my minds since the notification of the upcoming launch of a new version. It kook weird and not responsive as it was before the update. Not talking about the app logo, it took a bit to realize that wasn't related to Disney+", "A great idea, but no one near me appears to use it! 😂 30 + miles away is not local! Bombards me with adverts for paid add ons that will 'Get me more matches'. The free version of this app is useless. I wouldn't bother downloading! 😂 A great example of false advertising, as it clearly isn't local. Nothing more than a money making exercise/ scam. Dear developer I repeat, NO ONE NEAR ME USES IT 😂 Deleting now.", "Cool concept but the app is incredibly slow. I've tried it on two different smartphones. Browsing profiles to swipe, checking messages, checking anything... The app loads and loads. Then they gave the GUI, colors, and logo a complete overhaul and it's even slower! Also, it gives a lot of fake messages and notifications that are just the app telling you to upgrade. The company seems bent on aesthetics and pressuring users to upgrade rather than providing a good experience.", 'Notifications never worked, on 3 different phones, so I keep everyone waiting for replies. Well, except for the "open happn to see what you\'ve missed" notification that comes all the freaking time, at random times, and I can\'t turn off. It\'s a mess.', 'Tried signing in with phone number but it just keeps saying "invalid format". Tried 3 - 4 different ways of writing it and still just showed "incorrect format" good job, and send this directly to the dev team, because obviously something does not work. Edit: tried 6 different formats, the app sucks because of signin with phone no longer working no matter the number.', "Absolutely terrible. Takes ages to load profiles, there isn't many, it matches me with people who have simply just visited my area. What good is that!!!! Then I've had a free guess to open a like and it crashes before I can look. It's just terrible.", 'Pulling my review down to 3 stars because the new update made the interface much less responsive. Not an issue in any other app, but on happn I have to tap on the same thing several times and some buttons just seem to do nothing at all. It\'s also harder to find the "sweet spot" when scrolling through the map', "After the update: App touch has become very selective and unresponsive at times. Also, the map doesn't snap as it used too. It has become unstable and also takes a long time to see whom you've crossed paths with. Very unhappy with the latest update.", 'This app seems to be rigged for a money grab. It shows that i have over 30 likes but never shows anyone to swipe through saying "you haven\'t crossed paths with anyone yet", okay, so then how do i have so many likes? Obvously either fake likes to get you to upgrade or isn\'t showing me the people i\'ve actually crossed paths with. I live between a college and a major city so obviously the latter of the two. I\'ve used the paid version and the free version both on iphone and on android both.', "After the latest update this app is even worse. It sends notifications that I've crossed path with lots of new people, and still when using the app it takes up to five minutes for it to finish loading and when done the app tells me there are no profiles that have I've crossed path with. This app is just a SCAM to collect money through memberships and ads.", "Notifications just don't work. Now they had a full overhaul and what they still DIDN'T ADD is the possibility to see your own likes (who I liked) just disappointing. One of the apps that doesn't have this feature when all other apps have it. If you guys fix the translation as it seems to mot be fully working and shows English and French for me, plus fix the notifications I'll up my review. For 5 stars just add the feature all apps have that you can see your own likes 🙂", "At first glance it's a great app especially due to the GPS stuff showing you people in your environment. On second thought its an absolute waste of your time you swipe so many people zero results. The algorithm really really does suck on purpose to sell you premium really. So if you think this is a different app then Tinder or Bumble? Well it's not.", "2. What's with the new update it's a mess....all white with black what were u guys trying to do with the app design. 1The message issue is persistence it shows 12-13 msgs when clicking on message it shows zero message why on notification it's showing 13 & on opening zero either show or no show. Don't be stuck in middle.", "They changed ALL the design but didn't fixed a bug that is there since AGES. If you uncrush someone they will appear as someone new that liked you. Aside of that, the app is working worse than before. The most annoying thing is that isn't responsive it freezes from time to time (no, it's not my phone). Another thing is that the reason why Happn is popular is actually B U L L S H I T. I talked about where I crossed paths with my matches and concluded that it was invented, never crossedpwith them.", 'Very sluggish. I finally gave up on the registration step for adding a photo. Pleasing idea, but initial experience was that the app is unusable, not that it was useless. Probably the just out rewrite is to blame.', "It's a trap! They have a delete account button.... But it just does nothing. UPDATE: the delete button works if you click on the edge of it, but a huge middle region of the button doesn't work. I suspect this has been deliberately designed this way to cut down on people leaving - this is called a 'dark pattern' in the tech industry. If I come back to dating apps it won't be too happn (wasn't good anyway), and will make sure to spread the word not to use happn.", '$42/month to see profiles that are not within your area. I have 2 blurred out "matches", even though there is nobody in my area. This either means Happn is hiding those profiles from me so I won\'t match until I pay or they are outside my search radius. Again. They want $42 (!!) for a month for premium. Thats more than my entire monthly phone bill. Ads are intrusive and change the UI when shown, so you are very likely to activate them (poor advertisers who think they get quality traffic).', "I recently reset changed phones and for some reason Happn no longer recognizes my phone number or email. It goes through the whole profile creation process, name, what I'm looking for, photos etc. The last time this happened I followed the steps and later banned because of this. Not sure what I'm supposed to do...", "It's such a worst app I would suggest not buy it's premium. At first I buied it's premium version and I am not even able to connect/chat with the people who liked me. When I visit the profile of people whoever has liked me it throws an error saying An Unknown error occurred please try again later. I had raised an issue for the same but no response till now from the support team. Disappointed with the app.", "App doesn't work sometimes, the explore tab goes blank when there's more people to show. You have to flip between other tabs so they show up for a second, but then dissappear.", 'Most worst app i have ever seen.. i have purchased your subscription but still cant able to get benefits of it.. all the time app shows you have to buy subscription..i have already purchased it but still.... the amount also deducted from my bank account..i have written many complaints on mail but no response..', "Does not have non-binary as a gender option. That's an immediate red flag. UI is not great. But the worst sin of all is the location settings. Has no preferences for distance, with the only location information being your city. I live in a pretty damn big city, so I was getting people who lived like 50km away from me. Don't bother.", 'Worst app , I purchased for yearly package for nothing, they wont recommend anything unless you pay them , how dare you people saying this to unsubscribe me from premium and direct me to do free likes stuffs. You people dont take necessary steps to modify your app and dont have any features to correct the app but giving an idea to unsubscribe from premium.', 'Update: obvious low effort cash grab. Claims "brand new app" when they only changed color from blue to black and a few icons. UX/UI is worse than before, and I bet front end / back end as well! I recommend you remove the app from the market on your next update. Fire your UX/UI Team RIGHT NOW! Worst user experience ever. Original idea didn\'t evolve with COVID. Just a low effort cash grab. Impressive! 5*', "DO NOT BUY THIS APP. You get to see a few profiles and as soon as you buy the premium, nothing shows up in the app. The app tells me that there's no one near me. I only had 20 mins with the app so I know it cannot be right specially given that I live in a major city. They also send you a message like the one you see below and they never respond to your email. You're warned.", 'One of the worst app.. you have a great concept of near by crossing people But the chat and notification system sucks I got a message and no notification.. also for the crush no notification In this world of AI you should grow up.. and enhance your chat system and notification and the ux better ... The user experience in regards to chat and notification is .. as bad as not having this app is better', "The new version has become very slow and take too much money to show up the matches those who already liked my profile. That's not justified. I have 17 matches waiting but I can't see anyone. Always keeps asking money. It's really frustrating.", "Extremely buggy. Touch controls don't register more than half the time. Certification is broken and does not work. Location is also broken as well.", "Not at all getting persons to meet or chat only showing that to change preference and this is the worst dating app I have ever used and this is my worst experience with this app. This is the worst dating app I have ever seen and every 5 minutes once I need to change the preference to see new people what's this happn team, I want to cancel my subscription right now, kindly do the needful for that. There's no use of reaching you guys out no solution at all", 'App runs horribly. 30+ seconds of "loading" time between profiles. I put loading in quotes because i swipe on a profile, see the next flash, then it loads for 30+ seconds, and THEN i get to see that profile that flashed on screen properly', "It started off okay everything was fine till this new up date not my crashes and glitches every time I open it I won't be paying for another month if this is what we can expect from your team and then matches that don't respond your app looking fake ATM... Not to for get you play crush for your new matches but then the crusher's you deleted are now popping up over the new ones. Like why, I can not recommend to no one as it is."]

title: Wagr Petcare
description:
Wagr is the all-in-one pet care companion for all your furry friend's needs.

🧞 AI Petcare Advice: Get personalized pet care advice with our advanced AI feature. It provides tailored tips and recommendations for your pet's nutrition, grooming, exercise, and more.

🛍️ Shop Online: Discover a wide variety of pet products and supplies, from food and toys to grooming and healthcare essentials. Get everything your pet needs with just a few taps.

🩺 Online Vet Consultations: Connect with experienced veterinarians for online consultations and receive expert advice and support for all your pet-related concerns.

🐶 🐱 Play: Engage with our growing video section, featuring pet care content, tips, tricks, and advice from industry experts. As we expand this section, you'll enjoy a customizable experience and, eventually, a thriving community of passionate pet lovers.

At Wagr, we believe that our pets deserve the very best, and we're dedicated to making pet care easier and more convenient than ever.

Download the Wagr Petcare app now and start taking the best care of your pet today!
summary: Shop, consults, petcare advice & engaging content! Your petcare companion!

title: Dog Evolution: Idle Merge Game
description:
If you’re a dog person and think you know everything about man’s best friend, your world is about to be rocked! Mix puppy breeds like you’ve never seen before and discover a whole new canine dimension that will leave you barking in such awe: the possibilities are much wow!

Dachshunds, beagles, corgies and retrievers are so last week. Evolved dogs should have an extra eye or two so they can watch over their human friends more efficiently, or a handy horn just in case they get into the odd bar skirmish with a mutant unicorn. It’s your duty to let the dogs out and help them evolve!

DOGE FEATURES
• Pantheon: a new place for supreme beings to look down on us mortals and laugh at our misery
• Impostors: watch out for impostors trying to steal the spotlight from the puppies

HOW TO PLAY
• Drag and drop similar puppies to create new mysterious doges
• Use dog eggs to earn coins, buy new creatures and make even more money
• Alternatively, fiercely tap a rabbit to make coins pop from their eggs

HIGHLIGHTS
• Different stages and many dog species to discover
• A mind-blowing story with surprising twists
• The unexpected mix of creature evolution dynamics and incremental clicker games
• Doodle-like illustrations
• Various possible endings: find your destiny
• No dogs were harmed in the making of this game, only developers

The dog days have just begun! Much fun such wow!

Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased for real money.
summary: Combine mutant dog breeds and find out just how wacky puppies can get!

comments: ['Pretty fun, just a bit repetitive but I love it', "I enjoy the app it's cute and it's nice to pass the time, but it's kind of difficult to play a game and genuinely enjoy it when it crashes every single time you play an ad unwillingly. I'll just be in the middle of tapping my dogs and then an ad will play and crash the entire app so I have to reopen it every single time an ad plays Please fix this problem", "I love this game!!!!! its so addicting! who ever is reading this,you should get the game. I've been playing for hours. And it is helpful when your on the go or having no wifi,you cam still play the amazing app!!!! I never really got any ads. the only time i had a ad is when i tried getting more diamond diamonds.", "It's really fun and addicting. I could play for hours and hours, maybe even days. The genius who made this game blows my mind. I can't wait to download more games like this fantastic one. I only have had this game for a little, but I already 💗 it! When I am playing it on my phone even my dog sits and looks at the screen. I 💗 playing this game in a frantic time like this. I can't have a minute were I'm not playing, thinking about it, or talking about it! This game makes me feel 🤪😋😍. I 💗 it!", "It's a good time waster that's ruined by way to many ads that pop up freely on their own when you're just changing a tab in game. I wouldn't be so hard on it if it were just to watch the ads when you want to and get double payout or some type of reward.", 'Love it This game keeps me going and is very relaxing. But, when you get higher in the game, you have to watch an ad whenever you click on Mars. I like the app, but not the ads.', "I've always loved these games. They're my favorite evolution games. The only reason I'm not giving it 5 stars is because I ran into a bug that affected my gameplay. I contacted Tapps, but they have not responded. I hope no one runs into this bug too...", 'it literally shows you an ap every half minute. this is ridiculous', "Fabulous game, very addicting, adorable dogs and I'm definitely going to get into trouble for playing it too much when I'm not supposed to >:)", 'I redownloaded this game after over a decade just for the nostalgia. I will tell you now that this game did not disappoint. I still love this game, it is so cute and easy', 'I have played these games on and off for years and i love them! Funny, weird, cute and casual gaming, from getting far in the other evolution games i know it gets even weirder so i cant wait to see all the doggos. Very easy to learn.', 'Amazing! Its such an entertaining game and there are so many different types of dogs! There is a reasonable amount of ads and there is also lots of ways to make the process faster. I totally recommend it, it is a fun and simple game.', 'It\'s a good way to kill time, but I hate the new "evolution boxes" takes you out of gameplay and if I\'m just trying to tap, I cant do that anymore :(', "TO ALL THE PEOPLE WHO GAVE THIS A ONE STAR FOR THE ADS: There is a very free and simple trick to avoid these. TURN OFF YOUR WIFI. Ads can't get through without wifi to transfer it to your screen, so next time you think about complaining about the ads, remember: TURN OFF YOUR GOD DAMN WIFI", "Interesting time waster, but there are so many ads it ruins it. I can't even find the option to purchase the game just to turn off the excessive ads.", "This game is cool but... It has a LOT of ads. Its like they don't care adout there people who play their games. But it fun so if you don't care about ads play this game.", 'So fun! Lots of cute things to do and the doggos are great. All the little details in all of these games are great! (I have 5 from the same company thing)', "Ok think it's a good game but you need to make the poops cost more ,the diamonds easier to get and the cost of power ups cost less.", 'I have bad wifi so idk why ppl are complaining about the freaking adds i only saw 5-6 adds :/ but its simple, and cute, the designs, are, auhh, i like it but the designs, i dont like it.', "Literally everytime I try and open the app it crashes💔 I'm not sure if it's because of my device, but it's really sad😭 it's despair induuuuciiiingg- I've played it before though so it is a good game! I pray to Atua it will start working👉👈", "The game is good but there are too many ads so I can't able to play the game properly so fix that issue.", 'Its a really fun and cool app to play. At the super market , the school bus , any where is fun to play', '100000/10 I had been grinding this game for a few years when I had my fire tablet and only had one dog and 2 alien dogs left until my brother smashed the tablet. Very enjoyable tho and I recommend to anyone <3', "You might find the ads annoying but don't worry! You can turn off your WiFi, you can play it offline and online!", "It's very fun and it helps waste time. The graphics are good and its super adorable 😊", "Game is nice, but too many cheap ads just keep popping up like every minute - they're ruining the experience.", "*its just an evolution game about dogs.* *that's it.* Yet it's so creative compared to other evolution games. So I give it a 10 out of 10.", 'Very fun, especially when waiting for someone or on a flight or when you need to pass time.', 'I love these games, they are just so much fun to play when ever I am waiting for anything from the end of my break to the bus.', "Ads always show up and it's annoying but I appreciate it when they give coins after watching ads :D", "Great app if you're bored, and inspirational characters. I even drew some of them. 💛", 'I really liked this game, its really fun! Yes there are ads here and there either way its amazing! I really recommend this game! -this is my dad acc and im 12', 'THIS GAME HAS WAY TOO MANY POP UP ADS! Every minute or so.... The game will give you an ad, I say never get the game.', "pretty fun, kind of time consuming, gets boring after a while, but it's still fun", "It's a cute little time waster, but 3 ads in 1 minute is way too excessive.", "Very nice. Very nice. I loike it. Because it's very nice.", "It's SO FUN and the dogs are adorable❤ this game is so addicting and I find myself playing it all day. I highly recommend it❤", "I'm a dog person so I love this game and thanks for the update", 'This is is great, funny, and cute game I have no complaints please dont change anything about this game it is great', 'Great and awesome game 👍 graphics are really clear great quality and controls Awesome make more of these please!']

title: Udolly - Dating for disabled
description: Are you looking for a dating app for people with any type of disability? 💙 Do you have someone in your family circle who has a disability and are looking for a dating app for people with special needs? 💙 Are you looking to meet new people near you, make friends, or maybe find love? 😍 Introducing Udolly, the dating app for people with disabilities, whether you're single or a couple looking to make new friends or find love. 🦾 Udolly is the best dating app designed for disabled individuals, including physical disabilities, deaf or hard of hearing individuals, mute individuals, individuals with autism, intellectual disabilities, visual impairments, mental disabilities, and many other disabilities! 🤝 If you have any type of disability and are looking to make new friends or find your soulmate, Udolly is the dating app you need. 🌈 Whether you're asexual, bisexual, heterosexual, or homosexual, in Udolly, you can chat with whomever you want and find what you're looking for. Everyone deserves to fall in love, whether through sign language or any other language 😎. 👌CHAT WITH WHOEVER YOU WANT FOR FREE In Udolly, you'll swipe to get the best matches that fit your interests. Udolly is a free dating application where you can chat for free, without the need for a prior match like in most dating apps... In Udolly, you can find a partner, make friends, and meet wonderful people. You can also chat with thousands of people around the world 🌍 if you wish. ♿️ACCESSIBLE DATES FOR PEOPLE WITH DISABILITIES Udolly is a dating app primarily focused on disabled individuals. Select your disability when signing up, and you'll get the best matches in the swipe. It doesn't matter if you have a physical disability, intellectual or mental disability, if you're deaf, mute, have autism, use a wheelchair, have bipolar disorder, schizophrenia, or any other disability. It doesn't matter if you don't have a disability yourself and it's simply someone in your circle who does. Here, you can be yourself! And live your dating experience to the fullest! 👍. 💌FIND LOVE OR MAKE FRIENDS The Udolly dating app for people with special needs is perfect for finding incredible and charming people. Whether you're into casual relationships, flirting, niche dating like dating for the deaf, militar dating, veteran dating, virtual dates, speed dating, finding love, or seeking serious relationships, Udolly is the best dating app for all your needs 😉. We want to remind you that you're not alone at all 😞! With Udolly, you'll have a chat and dating platform to find friends, flings, or love 😁. 👍DISCOVER THE AMAZING FEATURES THAT MAKE THIS APP THE BEST DATING APP 🚀. 💙 Unique matching algorithm with other users based on compatible disabilities. 💙 Interface adapted to people with disabilities. 💙 Udolly is free and you will be able to talk to any user without having to make a Match. 💙 Virtual dating through calls and video calls. 💙 Listen to her voice in her description to get to know each other better. 💙 Filter by verified profiles. 💙 Filter by your interests: Serious relationship, Flirt, Casual dating or Chat and make friends. 💙 Talk to people anywhere in the world who speak the same language as you. 💙 Find people near you and talk to them for free. 💙 Filter by preferences: What sports do you like? Do you live alone or with someone? Do you have children or would you like to have them? comments: ["I don't know what is wrong with this app I've got plenty of matches and I've made the first move of sending the text, but there's no reply from any of my matches. And here's a tip for all of you guys who are not getting any matches, just do a right swipe first (just one right swipe) than close the app completely and than again open the app. You will find the same profile again (the one which you right swiped before closing the app), than again do the right swipe to the same profile and wa-Lah", "Very good app overall but there is an annoying bug through all the recent updates where the no Internet message is taped on the bottom of the screen and there's no way to get rid of it and cycle through the tabs. This happens even when the WiFi connection is working. Hopefully this issue will be fixed soon", "It's a pretty good little site but the latest update needs patching with the speed dating it doesn't seem to register people on a regular basis and if you click women only it does seem show any", 'The amount of ads is ridiculous. The UI is mediocre at best. Seems like a quick buck to make at the cost of disabled people. Piss off.', 'The daily affirmations and motivational messages on this app are a lovely addition to the astrology readings..👍', 'Great app for disabled poeple😍 Finally a dating app that works Finding my perfect match, higihly recommend it', "Garbage app. Unless you pay you have to watch a video ad after every 5 swipes. Enfiriating don't waste your time. Edit: Please post your data showing you use 40% less ads tha 95% of the daring apps.", "This is a scam site, you are taking advantage of people with disabilities. You took my money and no matter what no one messages back. Oh look 120 matches and yet no one responds. And the fake accounts are unreal!! I want my money back and I am telling you it's not worth your time or your money. Fake bots or something, also even when you say no to someone they come back as a match. And you can't contact any support it's all a scam!!!! Don't use this app. Also fake reviews. 🤬🤬 Not worth stars", "I don't have any experence because I paid for a subcription and made my profile 100% and verified my email and I haven't been able to do anything😡 rip off. But I will get my money back and report Udolly to the arthoroties for scam.", "Hello admins. I've tried opening it on udolly via my phone number but my account is suddenly blocked how? I just came to udolly for only 2 days. Please check my phone number d in my account open blocked. I can't buy for 1 month", "Couldn't ever get verified no many how many times I tried. It constantly said I had new likes but I could never look at them. It also constantly wanted me to subscribe when there were only 5 profiles to look at with very little information in them. All of them were super far away too. Super disappointing app since finding someone when handicapped is so hard to begin with.", "There are so many problems I can't cover them all, so I will focus on two big ones: 1. If someone has their GPS off they will show up to people all in the world listed as less thsn 1 km away. 2. It gave me my first match very quickly, but since then I would get notifications for 10+ new likes everyday, but I wasn't allowed to see any of the profiles without upgrading first. Even after 2 weeks both myself and the girl I matched with both didn't have any new matches that we could see.", "Site is glitchy ,can't navigate or access features I received 1 msg and was able to respond ,received lots of likes I can't respond to nor do I know which fake picture belongs to which like . Sometimes the loading spinning symbol spins indefinitely as long as on page and loads nothing . I un installed once and re installed does the same ..", "I live in a major city and theres no one nearby. The app is meh, not the worst but it definitely needs a redesign. Maybe if they made the app more user friendly, more people would join, but I don't see that happening.", 'Fun and easy to use🖐️🖐️', "Won't let you up load a photo from your library unless you grant camera access... this app forces you to grant more permission than it really needs... the app crashed 4 times while trying to create an account... had to start over each time... app isn't designed for ease of use...", 'fun and easy to use....', 'One match in 30km then next one in 100km how is that going to work if your disabled.', "Guys, at first I was happy that someone focuses on the loneliness of people with disabilities. But the app is terrible. Every day I get a message someone liked me, but I don't understand who liked me from the UI, it shows the people I liked. I send messages, no replies. What am I doing wrong? You need a better UI asap. And please improve your scammer detection, yesterday I ONLY saw scammers. You need to better this app as a service to humanity.", "ABSOLUTELY SHOCKING. Why bother? Nothing works, photos don't upload, tried to complete profile but nothing happens. Apparently, my rating is VERY LOW. Maybe it is because I am honest and genuine, it seems fakes and liars prosper. I would be interested to learn how many members are actually disabled. If you prey on the vulnerable , that is wholly sickening and utterly disgraceful.", "Couldn't even upload a picture. This is a colossal mess if you want to call it an app. In my book it NEVER would've scored a 4.8 out of 5 from me, more like I shouldn't have downloaded in the first place.", "Useless app. Wouldn't even let me upload a picture. I tried numerous times with several pictures and it wouldn't do upload them or anything.", 'Udolly is a great dating app for disabled people! The interface is easy to navigate and the community is supportive and welcoming.', "Why is it that this app only brings out the same fake people profiles and can't search or bring out new faces or real disabled people profiles....😠it's really annoying, you people should work on this app please it will be an interesting solid you work perfectly on it", 'The app itself is fine the issue I now face is the sub unfortunately am not able to sub for the month for the 7.99 as it does not give me the option to continue and the device was restarted so any suggestions on what should be done as far as the sub goes', "I was unable to get my account verified and I'm under the impression that that is why I didn't get any messages and was unable to chat with anyone. I tried repeatedly to get it verified but had no success. I am wondering if a new method of verification could be installed or if a new method of verification is in the works.", "I never thought I would find love on a dating app, but Udolly proved me wrong. I've met someone amazing and I'm so grateful for this platform.", "Just discouraged. They say my profile is only 88% done, but the only thing left is they want to know what my social media's are. I don't think that's a proper requirement, unless you want to put that down, your own choice. It's no one's business what else I might be on. So it says my popularity is low...🤔 not very social.", "I couldn't choose my preferences in terms of who I'd like to date,or my birth date. That's as far as I was able to get. However, if that can be fixed I'd like to rejoin and give it a try.", "Bogus app... Mostly users outside of the us. People like supposedly yet never message, doesn't say who likes you without paying... Another scam against the disabled. Deleting promptly.", "I've been using Udolly for a few weeks now and have already made some amazing connections. It's refreshing to be part of a dating app that is designed for people like me.", 'Edit on my previous comment: DEFINITELY a scam. Literally, two minutes after posting it, I suddenly had a "suitor" who wants to chat with me. How is that possible when for every other thing I try to do on the app, it says "Oops, sorry can\'t find anyone right now."? Yeah, I bet you can\'t find anyone right now. Such a hoax. For shame, guys. Why are you trying to play the disabled like that? We\'re disabled, not lacking in intelligence.', 'I don’t know if its only on my phone but everytime I tried to install this application, it says that it cannot install. I’m using android 12 by the way.', 'This app is amazing 🦾', "Uninstalled right away. I tried the app but couldn't get past the loading screen. please fix this", "disabled people don't have the money to waste on random searches", 'Not only is it filled with bots but the filter is useless when it comes to inputting your desires in regards to gow far away you want matches from', "I love this dating app! I think it's great to be able to filter by preferences, it's very different from the others.", "It's fake, just collecting subscription. And it's hard to delete your account.", 'As a person with a disability, it can be tough to find people who understand and accept me. Udolly has been a game-changer for me and I highly recommend it.']

title: Puppr - Dog Training & Tricks
description:
Meet your new dog trainer! Puppr includes step-by-step video instructions to help you teach your dog basic obedience like “sit” and “stay” to advanced tricks like “fetch leash” and “sit pretty”. Great for both new and experienced dog owners.

Features
• Over 80 lessons taught by celebrity dog trainer Sara Carson & The Super Collies (America's Got Talent top 5 finalist)
• Live chat with our team of world-class trainers to get your training questions answered (requires Puppr Premium subscription)
• Step-by-step instructions with videos make lessons easy to follow
• Built-in clicker makes training on-the-go easy. All lessons are taught with positive reinforcement!
• Track your pup's training progress
• Collect badges as you train and master new tricks
• Support for multiple dogs
• Puppr Shop that includes hand-picked product recommendations from Sara and the team to help with your training

Live Chat
Our team of professional trainers are available 24/7 to help with (but not limited to):
• New puppy or dog
• Unwanted behavior like puppy nipping, jumping on people, barking, etc
• Leash training
• Potty training
• Separation anxiety
• Trick training
• Any training topic you need help with!

About Sara Carson & The Super Collies
Sara Carson is considered one of the top dog trick instructors in the world and was a top-5 finalist on season 12 of America's Got Talent. She and her dogs (Hero, Marvel, Hawkeye, and Fury) travel North America teaching dog trick workshops and performing with a popular stunt dog team. Sara and Hero currently hold the Guinness World Record for most tricks performed in 60 seconds (49 tricks!).

In-App Purchases
Puppr includes premium lesson packs that each come with 2 free lessons and additional locked content that can be purchased.

Subscription Pricing and Terms
Puppr offers two auto-renewing subscription options for Puppr Premium, which unlocks live chat and all the lesson packs. Pricing options are:
• $12.99 per month
• $99.99 per year (after a 7-day free trial)

These prices are for United States customers. Pricing in other countries may vary and actual charges may be converted to your local currency depending on the country of residence.

Your Puppr subscription will automatically renew at the end of each term and your credit card will be charged through your Google Play account unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the term. You can turn off auto-renew at any time from your Google Play account settings but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term.

comments: ["Great app, without having to pay! Has most of the basics, and majority is free. The tips actually work, and now my dog has great grooming skills. Wish it had more interactions (people/cats/kids/dogs) or preventative/behavior training but it's a great groundwork without a personal trainer. I actually want to buy the extra thing but I don't have at the moment.", "Quality app, can't believe it's free. Breaks training down into very simple steps with helpful short video demonstrations. I subscribe to a paid app that is not as easy to use as this one. I'm not a fan of the in-app clicker but I guess it's a decent alternative if you can't afford an actual clicker. I would love to see expanded content for the future.", "I've had this app since it was released. The tricks keep growing and so do the features. It's a handy app. I've been training dogs since I was a kid. I don't specialize in trick training, so it's been quite helpful to have some more random fun tricks with a basic how to on training methods. Plus they keep adding tricks, so we'll have plenty of material for a while and I really like the new badge feature. All and all, its a fun, helpful app that both me and my dog enjoy!", "I'm a certified animal behaviorist, and I have enjoyed this app so much! The lessons are easy, the mechanics of the app work very well with the lessons. I love the simple, straightforward format for the menu, as well. Prices are incredibly low as well, and there's a surprising amount of free lessons available from the get go. Love this app, hope maybe you can add more about addressing specific behaviors perhaps?", 'This is an excellent app for training your dog new tricks. But, I gave 4 stars because there is a heavy emphasis on earning badges and there are no visual check marks on each completed item, which makes this feature lacking. I would like a better home screen with less clutter where I can upload a picture of my dog and have buttons to continue the lessons i left off.', 'I really enjoy this app! Only one I\'ve seen in a while where I want to buy the Pro and it\'s absolutely worth it. Well done on dog training explanations! Only reason it is 3 star instead of 5.. I can\'t open the "circus" trick jump through hoops arms without it erroring out "cannot play video"... I never asked it to play video! Then the app freezes and I have to close it entirely. If y\'all can get this working I\'ll change my stars n buy pro.', "Has helped me train my dachshund to do several tricks. (I can't think of higher praise. ) I haven't bought additional packs yet, but it seems fair & I'm glad it's not all or nothing. The way tricks are broken down helped me recognize when to be patient, when to try something different. (Plus: what to try!) I wish I could use the clicker without opening the app but there doesn't seem to be an API call for that accessible from automation.", "The steps are really easy to follow. I had reservations on if it would work, I was pleasantly surprised,that they actually worked, we've now completed the basics and are on the silly training. If you want an app to help you training your new puppy, then this is the perfect one to use.", 'Wow! This was exactly what I was looking for: concise written instructions with short demonstration videos, no ads, and an elegant and intuitive interface. If I could give this 6 stars I would. After trying about 10 different dog training apps, I found this one, and it is the best by far. I rarely leave reviews but this app is just exceptional. The free content is so good I will happily and gladly support the app developers by purchasing the additonal content. Good stuff.', 'This is a great app for dog training. It was very helpful and u got to teach my dog great tricks like spin and how to hug someone. So cute. The only thing is alot of tricks are locked that you have to pay for. Same with the chat with experts. You can ask professionals for help or this and tricks but that also costs money. If you are willing to pay for those things, this app is easily five stars.', 'I absolutely love this app! I love having a visual as well as words when teaching my dog, so seeing that helps. my dog responds well to all the techniques used, I definitely recommend this app! Cant wait till my dog can roll herself in a blanket haha...easy to use and clear instructions, just amazing and free!', "This app is overall not that bad. I think it'd be very helpful to a beginner dog owner, BUT..Over half the tricks are locked and need to be paid for, which I really dislike. Don't get me wrong, I've taught my dog a new trick from this app,and it's pretty easy to use,but I just wish there were a few more options without having to pay for it.", "This app is amazing especially if you don't want to spend money! you can still teach your dog simple commands for FREE! THIS really helped and actually worked out great! But if you would like to teach your dog more harder selections you would have to pay money but not a lot like you would expect.", "This training is super easy to follow! Our shows both infatuation step by step and a video for each step which replays over and over. It sets up both you and your dog for successful training! My 9 week old dog knows her name, Come, Stay, Sit, and is create trained and clicker trained! We are working on others and can't wait for advanced training. The only issue I have is when the buttons stop working. The fix is to close the app and restart, so it's not a big deal.", "Great start. Simple, basic and easy to follow. Best part, it's effective training for your dog. I have a 3 month old beagle and we doing great using this app. She is progressing on sit and down after only a few sessions. On to come and stay over the next few days. Even thinking about purchasing some of the advance training but that's a ways off still. Highly recommend. Gives you needed structure to follow. Very helpful in my opinion.", 'This app is amazing! So easy to use and informative! I\'ve been searching for proper guidance, as a first time "dog mom" it can be very complicated to do online research on your own. I was feeling overwhelmed, there is so much information out there and it\'s so generalized...I was struggling trying to find the right advice for us. This app has helped more than any other source I\'ve come across! I\'m so grateful and I most definitely recommend it!', 'I really like the app, I didn\'t realize you had to pay to access ALL of the training though. Wish it was free, but I understand that people need to make money. Left off a star because it isn\'t \'free" like advertised. Each training is a video and step by step description.', "This app didn't help much. it seems like the instructions would help, but when I tried to teach them down, I said, Sit and all they did when I put the treat down thr got up and just bent down to grab it I tried other things to and it didn't work. This app wasn't really the best app for me.", 'Not useful. The tracking of the tricks is very poor, with only few options (not trained, in progress and trained) which isnt useful. I need more detail or customization, where you can rate the dogs performance and specify in what part of the training your are working (inside home, in the garden, in the street, with people etc). The app also keeps disconecting my dog profile and showing an empty one.', "I just started using this app and I absolutely love it. The tutorials themselves are clear and concise and each skill has a short video clip that shows someone teaching their dog that skill, so it's perfect whether you're a visual learner or prefer step-by-step instructions.", "I bought the full app. I really enjoyed the free demonstrations and paid for one of the packages then paid for the full app to get everything. The tricks definitely depend on the dog. Some I had to modify the steps to teach my dog, some tricks are very difficult and not explained great from the videos provided. I was between 3 and 4 stars but have enjoyed it more than a mear 3 stars. If your enjoying the free performances then try out some of the paid content. I'm reviewing this app after 1 year", "I LOVE this app, I've bought the full lesson packs, so I have them all, however I've only given it 4 stars, because the updates/new lesson packs always come out on the iPhone first. I understand that is because most people use iPhones, but normally after a few months the new lesson packs become available on Android. Well, I've been waiting months and months for Charming 2.0, and other packs, to no avail. Hopefully they'll become available to Samsung soon, because I do love this app so much. ❤", '1000% recommend! This app is so thoughtfully designed to help you teach your dog a large variety of new skills of all difficulty levels. It is so easy and fun to use, and breaks down each skill/trick in simple steps, visuals, along with helpful tips!', "On many levels I've been very impressed with this app. The instructions are simple and easy to implement and I love the clicker option. What is keeping me from giving this five stars is that I'm not seeing a heeling/loose leash category. This is one of my biggest struggles with my 18-month-old 81 lb Doberman. I don't mind paying for it but I am very disappointed if it's not included somewhere. Please let me know if I've missed it!", "This is an easy to use app and breaks the tricks down easily. The basics and clicker are free but you have to pay for the fancy stuff, but it's reasonably priced and worth it if you want to learn some cool party tricks to show off and blow your friends' minds!", "I love this app. I have been training dogs for years but never trick training, the app is very easy to follow and pictures make it beginner friendly. A lot of people complain about paying but don't understand that classes to learn all of the tricks would cost hundreds of dollars so only paying $12 is an absolute steal.", "This would have been such an amazing app if you were able to lock anywhere on it to get the clicking sound. If only the clicker button was in the middle of the app. It's quite difficult to use practically when training, because one has to search for the clicker button and that's not very user-friendly. Such a pity.", "I love this app it is so so so helpful and very easy to use! I love the built-in clicker it makes training so much easier! 10 out of 10 would recommend! I had a question though this app was recommended to me for the chat feature and I'm not seeing it anywhere I have purchased all of the training packs and I thought it might come with that but I still don't see it? Even without this feature it has helped me so much just curious!", 'Great training room with videos for many of the tricks to help guide you through the steps. Hopefully they will continue to add more tricks, video tutorials, and badges. Built in clicker for those who need it. Make tricks easy to understand and teach. Would love to see the next update add "carry an object" or to "pull a toy while walking". Also would love to see a section for the different AKC Trick Dog Tittles and CGC standards.', 'Good instructions, but you have to pay in order to access all the tricks and the "badges" don\'t work, I\'ve completed many of the tasks, and the ratio on each badge shows I\'ve completed it, but the app doesnt recognize it for some reason. Kind of disappointed, could be great', "Much easier to use than a dog training book with step by step guide and videos. I can keep a record of my dog's progress and the inbuilt clicker is handy. There's the option to purchase individual packs of additional tricks, or all additional tricks.", 'Epicccc It really help and there are some cool tricks on here. Some even help with obedience training thank you!! But one request is that maybe give more access( not having to pay) for the cooler tricks like jumping over your arm, or sitting/standing on your feet while in the air ( i dont remember the name) but i know u need that to keep the app running. Anyways thanks for showing me some tricks, and stuff, its really useful for my energy ball.', "super helpful for training! love the variety of tricks and the little clicker sound! my most favorite part of this app is even if you don't pay to subscribe you have access to all the basics of training and step by step techniques. very well executed.", 'I love this app and downloaded it shortly after its release (and went premium). The photos are beautiful and the steps are easy to follow. The ONLY reason I give it four stars is my primary device is ios has way more trick packs and even a store. No word on social media if they are working an update for android in the near future.', 'I paid for the upgrade hoping to get the additional lessons, which I was really hoping to use. Except these are only available on iOS and not Android (which is not clearly stated...if at all). I essentially paid to have someone via "chat" tell me I don\'t get the additional lessons on an Android device. What a waste of money. So if you have Android, be warned and don\'t pay for the upgrade.', "Hello. I've had Puppr for a while now, and my dog has learned some pretty cool tricks, like Shake. (I call it Paw) but here's the parts that make me feel a bit upset: 1. Some of the lesson packs, well... You have to pay for them. 2. It needs more lessons that are actually FREE! I mean, the basic pack IS fine, but I feel like, my dog needs more things to learn... 3. I don't think the notification for training actually makes a sound. But other than that it's fine But I also have ideas pls send web", "The overall idea here is good. Although, they really need to do one of two things. 1. Make the clicker button centered and bigger or 2. Have a clicker only mode where clicking anywhere on the app will trigger the sound. When you have an energetic puppy, it's difficult the track down the clicker.", "I have not used this app yet, but impressed it teaches how to load the clicker or give it meaning to the dog. A lot of clicker training leaves this important step out. Looking forward to using the app as another way of bonding with my dog. I don't care for things like the rock back sit, but I can change up those things. After looking thru the app. there isn't enough my dog can learn from it so twelve bucks is just not worth it, for others it could be a lot of fun.", 'Homestly way better than the other apps. The free content is vast whereas other apps have you pay a lot just to use content that is otherwise free. The instructions and the videos are super simple and short. Honestly great great grear job to the developers.', "This ap is so amazing. I have a great pyrenees who is extremely hard to train. He's very low energy, and very independent so it's extremely hard to motivate him. He recently got sick, and threw all his potty training out the window. We got him as an adult, and this ap walked us through the RIGHT way to potty train a dog. Now he's back to his old self after some blunders. He's making amazing improvements. Thank you Puppr!!!"]

title: Boo - The World's Cutest Dog
description:
You’ve got a new pet – Boo, The World’s Cutest Dog! Play with Boo in the park and cuddle your new fuzzy friend to sleep. Take awesome selfies with Boo and upload them to your BOO-stagram!

Boo, The World’s Cutest Dog, is here, and he’s ready to hang out with you, his human! He needs lots of love and attention, and what’s more fun than loving this cute little fuzzball? Experience a day in the life of Boo – Give him a bath before it’s time to go to the vet. Dress him up in his favorite outfits. Play frisbee with him at the park and cheer him on while he’s racing against his puppy friends. Make sure he’s fed well before you tuck him into bed! 

Features:
> Dress Boo up in rockin’ outfits!
> Oh no! Boo’s not feeling well. Cure him with your special vet tools!
> Have a fun-filled day with Boo at the park!
> Boo’s hungry! Feed him yummy food to make his tail wag! 
> Ready, set go! Help Boo win the doggy race!
> Let Boo splash around in a bubble bath ‘til he’s squeaky clean!
> Play a lullaby for Boo and tuck him into his cozy bed!

To opt out of CrazyLabs sales of personal information as a California resident, please visit our Privacy Policy: https://crazylabs.com/privacy-policy/
